\id JHN  
\h JON 
\toc1 Jon 
\toc2 Jon 
\mt1 Jon  
\mt2 Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r R…ôha Iesu Kristo It…ôm Jon T…ôm…ôte  
\imt1 N…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r r…ôha naoa u Jon  
\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In pia Jemes, k…ôn ilau n…ôt…® Sepeti mil. In kit r…ôha net…ôm tuelef r…ôha Iesu, k…ôn Iesu tolkeike p…®k in. In t…ôm…ôte naoa m…®n u: Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r It…ôm Jon T…ôm…ôte, 1 Jon, 2 Jon, 3 Jon, ne Nol ∆èp…ôn.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô okot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu. In tolkeike m…ôm…ô otasitu elat mol nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhalat tuwa m…ôskas…®k, m…ôto-inu r…ôhalat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn t…ôs…ôskas…®k…ôn …ôh.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Jon in et…ôm-iasol kit r…ôha nim…ôfak, k…ôn net…ômim rafin r…ôha nim…ôfak koat…®siai-in. In tolkeike m…ôm…ô net…ômim rafin okot…®tun w…®r r…ôhan n…ôg…ôtun…ôn, k…ôn nian n…ôg…ôtun…ôn eiu…ô t…ôtan, m…ôto net…ômim kot…®tun nahtos…®g-in…ôn n…ôghat…ôn eiu…ô m…®n e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Jon e naoa u.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa u mat…ôn-iar…ôp w…®r m…ôm…ô Iesu in n…ôt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn net…ômim rafin it…ôm okotahat…ôt…ô lan, okotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n. K…ôn Jon tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp …ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô Iesu in n…ôt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn Iesu in Uhg…®n pahrien. K…ôn Jon tolkeike m…ôm…ô in ot…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn m…®n neen r…ôha Iesu it…ôm naoa m…®n r…ôha Matiu, ne Mak, ne Luk k…ôm…ôs…ôhal…ôn…ôn. K…ôn in tolkeike m…ôm…ô in ot…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…®n neen it…ôm net…ômim koat…ôn e Iesu.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ôghat…ôn R…ôha Uhg…®n T…ômuwa Et…ômim, in Iesu  
\m
\v 1 Aup…ôn ag…®n, e n…ôtuoun…ôn nian, N…ôghat…ôn t…®nat…®g r…ôk…®s.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Jen 1:1; 1 Jon 1:1; Jon 17:5; Nol ∆èp…ôn 19:13\f* N…ôghat…ôn u t…ôm…ôtat…®g ilau Uhg…®n, k…ôn N…ôghat…ôn u, in Uhg…®n.  
\v 2 E n…ôuk…ôt…® nian, in t…®n…ômat…®g r…ôk…®s ilau Uhg…®n,  
\v 3 k…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômol nat…®mnat rafin e N…ôghat…ôn u, k…ôn nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol, nat kiti…ôh ne t…®k…ô m…ôm…ô N…ôghat…ôn u t…ôsol…ôn.\f + \fr 1:3 \ft Kol 1:16; 1 Korin 8:6; Hip 1:2\f*  
\v 4 Inu, in N…ôuk…ôt…® N…ômeg…ôh…ôn,\f + \fr 1:4 \ft Jon 5:26; 11:25; 14:6\f* k…ôn N…ômeg…ôh…ôn u, in N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn r…ôha net…ômim rafin.  
\v 5 N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn …ôh, t…ôtasi…ôg…ôp…®n napin…ôp…ôn, k…ôn napin…ôp…ôn okol t…ôsapr…ôk…®s-in…ôn.\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Jon 9:5; 12:46\f*   
\p
\v 6 Et…ômim kit it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa tuwa, n…ôrg…®n u, Jon.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Aposol Jon in t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In tat…ôghat-in Jon Paptais e ves m…®n u.\f*  
\v 7 T…ôm…ôtul-ar…ôp m…ôm…ô otamnus-iar…ôp N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn …ôh k…ôm net…ômim, p…ôs ilat rafin kot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn lan.  
\v 8 S…ôn…ôm…ô Jon in N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn …ôh, m…ôto in t…ômuwa …ôm m…ôm…ô ot…ôtul-ar…ôp m…ôn-iar…ôp N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn …ôh k…ôm net…ômim rafin.  
\v 9 N…ôghat…ôn …ôh t…ômatuwa e n…ôtueint…ôn, k…ôn in N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn pahrien, it…ôm in t…ôtasi…ôg…ôp…®n net…ômim rafin.\f + \fr 1:9 \ft 1 Jon 2:8\f*   
\p
\v 10 Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômol n…ôtueint…ôn u e N…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ôn t…ôm…ôtat…®g e n…ôtueint…ôn u, m…ôto net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn kot…ôruru in.  
\v 11 T…ômuwa iman ik…®n, m…ôto natiman m…®n koat…ôuhlin m…ôntaalat k…ôm in, m…ôsotolkeike…ôn.  
\v 12 M…ôto net…ômim rafin it…ôm k…ômotos in n…®kilat tagien ron, k…ôn motahat…ôt…ô e n…ôrg…®n, k…ôn in t…ômeg…ôhan-in ilat koatuwa nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Kal 3:16\f*  
\v 13 Nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n …ôh, ilat k…ôsotaiir…ôn e nol…ôn it…ôm n…®sualk…ôl…ôh kotaiir mihin, k…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha et…ômim, o r…ôha tata m…®n, m…ôto ilat kotaiir wi m…®n e Uhg…®n, e r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn …ôm.\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Jon 3:5; 1 Pita 1:23\f*   
\p
\v 14 N…ôghat…ôn …ôh, in t…ômuwa et…ômim, m…ôtat…®g kitat min. K…ôn it…®mat emot…ôplan r…ôhan nep…ôt…ôn, k…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn asol ne n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn r…ôhan e n…®gan…ômt…®t…®mat. Inu, in n…ôsan…ôn…ôn asol ne n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn r…ôha Noan Kiti…ôh ∆èm, it…ôm in t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e Tata Uhg…®n. In t…ôrioah e n…ôw…®r…ôn it…ôm t…ôtawte-in k…ôm kitat, k…ôn m…ôrioah m…®n e n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft Fil 2:7; 1 Tim 3:16\f*   
\p
\v 15 Jon tat…ôtul-ar…ôp mat…ôn …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ômim u inu it…ôm io emat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIo etaup…ôn, k…ôn suah kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n tatuaris…®g-in io, m…ôto in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in io, m…ôto-inun, nian em…ôsaiir…ôn …ôh, in t…®n…ômat…®g lil…®n r…ôk…®s.‚Äô‚Äù   
\p
\v 16 K…ôn in t…ôrioah e n…ôw…®r…ôn it…ôm in t…ôtawte-in k…ôm kitat, k…ôn e n…ôw…®r…ôn …ôh r…ôhan, nian rafin in tatos-ipa, matos-ipa, matos-ipa, k…ôm kitat rafin.  
\v 17 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu Lou it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ipa aup…ôn, Moses in suat…®p ron, m…ôto Iesu Kristo in suat…®p r…ôha nawte-in…ôn n…ôw…®r…ôn …ôh ne n…®pahrien…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n k…ôm kitat.\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Rom 5:21\f*   
\p
\v 18 Suah kit t…ôsehm…ôn Uhg…®n nian kit ne.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft Eks 33:20\f* M…ôto Noan Kiti…ôh ∆èm, in Uhg…®n, it…ôm in iu…ôhk…®r o noanenau r…ôha Tata Uhg…®n, in t…ômol …ôp Uhg…®n k…ôm kitat k…ôn kot…®tun.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft 2 Korin 4:6; Kol 1:19; 2:9; Nol ∆èp…ôn 22:4\f*   
\s1 Jon t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa  
\r (Mat 3:11-12; Mak 1:7-8;  //  Luk 3:15-17)  
\p
\v 19 K…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n e noanol r…ôha Isrel it…ôm kotat…®g Jerusalem, k…ômotahl-ip…ôn pris m…®n neen ne Lifaet m…®n un, net…ôm kotasitu e pris m…®n e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, m…ôm…ô okotuwa motehm Jon mot…ôtap…ôh ron, m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik et…ômim pah un?‚Äù K…ôn o nat u, Jon t…ôm…ôtul-ar…ôp mat…ôn-iar…ôp in.   
\p
\v 20 Nian ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron, in t…ôm…ôs…ôhluaig-in…ôn, m…ôto t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn …ôtuat…®p …ôm in k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúS…ôn…ôm…ô io Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa.‚Äù   
\p
\v 21 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ok…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô ik Kristo, k…ôn ik pah? ?Ik Elaija?‚Äù\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Mal 3:1; 4:5-6; Mat 11:14; 17:10-13\f*  
\p M…ôto Jon t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôp…ô, s…ôn…ôm…ô io Elaija.‚Äù  
\p K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh m…®n ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ok…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô ik Elaija, k…ôn ik pah? ?Ik ien r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm k…ômat…ôn aup…ôn m…ôm…ô ot…ôpanuwa?‚Äù\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Dut 18:15\f*  
\p M…ôto Jon t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôp…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk on…ôk…ôike m…ôn-iar…ôp ik k…ôm it…®mat, p…ôs it…®mat ekotuw…®n mot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm k…ômotahl-ipa it…®mat ekotuwa.‚Äù   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u it…ôm ien r…ôha Uhg…®n Aesea t…®n…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s aup…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòSuah kit t…ôtag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, Otol-w…®r suat…®p r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \fr 1:23 \ft Aes 40:3\f*   
\p
\v 24 N…ôt…ômim it…ôm k…ômahl-ipa ilat, Farisi m…®n neen …ôh-ik…®n,  
\v 25 k…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh m…®n o Jon m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ok…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô ik Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, k…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô ik Elaija, k…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô ik ien it…ôm k…ômat…ôn-iar…ôp aup…ôn, k…ôn t…ôhrol nakatol baptais e net…ômim?‚Äù   
\p
\v 26 K…ôn tuhalp…®n mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo iatol baptais e net…ômim e n…ôhau, m…ôto suah kit u ik…®n ilug…®n et…ômat, it…ôm it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru in.  
\v 27 Io etaup…ôn, suah un in tatuaris…®g, m…ôto in il…®s, k…ôn io l…ôhau l…ôhau …ôm, k…ôn esahmen ag…®n-…ôh…ôn m…ôm…ô ekol w…ôk kit r…ôhan.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:27 \ft N…ôghat…ôn pahrien it…ôm Jon t…ôm…ôn, tol n…ôhlan, ‚ÄúIo esahmen ag…®n-…ôh…ôn m…ôm…ô ekos-ir…ôk…®s put r…ôhan.‚Äù Net…ômim aup…ôn kot…ôm…ô w…ôk r…ôha nos-ir…ôk…®s…ôn put r…ôha i…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, in w…ôk r…ôha slef it…ôm in l…ôhau l…ôhau ag…®n.\f*  
\v 28 Nat…®mnat m…®n u, k…ômol …ôp…ôh e latu…ônu kit, n…ôrg…®n u Petani, in t…ôtat…®g …ôp…ôh ent…ôn…®p…ôn e n…ôhau Jotan. Ik…®n …ôh Jon tatol baptais e net…ômim ik…®n.   
\s1 Iesu in tahmen e n…ôt…® sipsip r…ôha Uhg…®n  
\p
\v 29 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin, Jon t…ôm…ôplan Iesu taliw…ôk matuwa, k…ôn in t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! !Ot…ôplan-tu! Suah u inu, in N…ôt…® Sipsip r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 1:29 \ft Jen 22:8; Aes 53:7; 1 Pita 1:19; Nol ∆èp…ôn 5:6\f* K…ôn in ot…ôpanos-ir…ôk…®s nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u.\f + \fr 1:29 \ft Hiprus 9:22,26\f*  
\v 30 Et…ômim u inu, io emat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIo etaup…ôn, k…ôn suah kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n tatuaris…®g-in io, m…ôto in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in io, m…ôto-inu nian em…ôsaiir…ôn …ôh, in t…®n…ômat…®g lil…®n r…ôk…®s.‚Äô  
\v 31 Nian io emat…ôghat-in, k…ôn io m…®n em…ôruru m…ôm…ô in et…ômim pah; m…ôto emuwa matol baptais e net…ômim e n…ôhau m…ôm…ô ekol …ôp suah u k…ôm noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel.‚Äù   
\p
\v 32-33 Jon t…ômat…ôtul-ar…ôp mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa io m…ôm…ô io ekol baptais e net…ômim e n…ôhau, k…ôn nian emat…ôghat-in, io m…®n em…ôruru m…ôm…ô suah u inu. M…ôto Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-ipa k…ôm io m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòOn…ôk…ôplan Narm…®n R…ôhak oteiuaiu mat…®g e et…ômim kit. K…ônu suah u inun, in otol baptais e net…ômim e Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äô K…ôn …ômun, uaris…®g em…ôplan Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôr e neai tahmen e mak, muwa, meiuaiu m…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr lan.  
\v 34 Io …ôtuat…®p em…ôplan nat u, k…ôn emat…ôtul-ar…ôp mat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòSuah u inu, in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n pahrien.‚Äô‚Äù   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôtuoun m…ôtaun-in  //  r…ôhan net…ômim  
\p
\v 35 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin, Jon t…ôtat…®g …ôp…ôh ik…®n kiti…ôh …ôm il…ôhal r…ôhan k…ôiu et…ômim.  
\v 36 K…ôn nian n…®gan…ômt…® Jon t…ôm…ôtul e Iesu taliw…ôk matuwa k…ôn t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! !Ot…ôplan-tu! !Suah u inu, in N…ôt…® Sipsip r…ôha Uhg…®n!‚Äù   
\p
\v 37 K…ôn nian r…ôhan et…ômim mil k…ômu…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ômu…ôtul matiauaris…®g-in Iesu.  
\v 38 K…ôn Iesu teirair m…ôplan suah mil un katu…ôt…ôu-p…ôn-in, k…ôn in t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! !Suah mil! ?Natueg…ôs-in naka?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn ilau ku…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRapai. ?Ik n…ôtat…®g hi…ô?‚Äù (N…ôghat…ôn u ‚ÄúRapai,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n u ‚ÄúI…ôg…ôtun.‚Äù)   
\p
\v 39 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôs k…ôhaluw…®n naku…ôplan-tu.‚Äù K…ôn ilau k…ômiauaris…®g-in m…ôhaluw…®n ku…ôplan ik…®n in t…ôtat…®g ik…®n. Iu…ôhk…®r m…®tgar tiw…®g ehnaip…ôn, ilau k…ôm…ôtuan il…ôhal min m…ôtoarus tapin…ôp.   
\p
\v 40 Suah mil u kit it…ôm t…ôm…ôto Jon, n…ôrg…®n u Antru, pian u Saimon Pita.  
\v 41 K…ôn roiu ag…®n-…ôh m…®n, in t…ômuw…®n mehm pian Saimon mit muwa, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! !Enot…ôplan r…ôk…®s Mesaea!‚Äù (N…ôghat…ôn u, Mesaea, n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúKristo,‚Äù it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa.)  
\v 42 K…ôn t…ômit Saimon muwa o Iesu.  
\p K…ôn nian n…®gan…ômt…® Iesu t…ôm…ôtul lan, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk u inu Saimon, n…ôt…® Jon, m…ôto roiu okaun-in …ôt…ôgt…ôg ik m…ôm…ô ‚ÄòKefas.‚Äô‚Äù (In ‚ÄúPita‚Äù\f + \fr 1:42 \ft N…®p…ôt…® n…ôrg…®n u Pita, in ‚Äúk…ôpiel.‚Äù\f* e n…ôghat…ôn Kris).\f + \fr 1:42 \ft Mat 16:18\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ômaun-in Filip ne Nataniel  
\p
\v 43 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin m…®n, Iesu n…®kin t…®n…ôht m…ôm…ô otuw…®n-tu Kalili. K…ôn nian in t…ôm…ôplan Filip, k…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúWa-tu, m…ôt…ôu-pa io.‚Äù  
\v 44 Filip u, in et…ôm Petsaeta, ima Antru ne Pita.  
\v 45 K…ôn in t…ômehm Nataniel, k…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…®mat enot…ôplan suah ilouin, aup…ôn Moses t…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm tat…ôghat-in e naoa r…ôha Lou. K…ôn ien m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n aup…ôn ilat m…®n k…ômot…ôte r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm tat…ôghat-in. In et…ôm Nasaret, in n…ôt…® Josep, k…ôn n…ôrg…®n u, Iesu.‚Äù   
\p
\v 46 M…ôto Nataniel t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Naka lan? ?N…®kim t…ôht m…ôm…ô nat w…®r kit ot…®s…®-p…ôn e Nasaret? !K…ôp!‚Äù  
\p K…ôn Filip t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIta, t…ôw…®r …ôm, p…ôs-tu kian nak…ôplan-tu.‚Äù   
\p
\v 47 Nian Iesu t…ôm…ôplan Nataniel taliw…ôk matuwa, k…ôn t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Suah u, in noanol …ôtuat…®p r…ôha Isrel! !Neiueiu…ô…ôn t…®k…ô lan!‚Äù\f + \fr 1:47 \ft Jen 27:30-36; 31:26; 32:28\f*   
\p
\v 48 K…ôn …ômun Nataniel t…ôtap…ôh o Iesu m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…ômahro m…®tun m…ôm…ô io et…ôm tol nulan?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian ik n…ômat…ôp…ôl…ôh e n…ôuk…ôt n…®g fik, k…ôn Filip t…ôsaun-in…ôn …ôh ik, m…ôto io en…ôm…ôplan r…ôk…®s ik.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:48 \ft N…®g fik m…®n, ilat n…®g-k…®tun m…®n e nasum…ôn ik…®n Isrel. Net…ômim koatun noalat, k…ôn moat…ôp…ôl…ôh ahgin n…®mal…®lat. Koat…ôp…ôl…ôh ahgin p…®k n…®g fik iu…ôhk…®r o nim…ô r…ôhalat k…ôn moat…ôfak m…ôm…ô n…®kilat otat…ôht n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n. Nat it…ôm Iesu t…ôm…ôn e ves 47 ne 51 in tat…ôghat-in Nataniel m…ôm…ô ok…ôm-naka t…ômat…ôp…ôl…ôh ahgin r…ôhan n…®g fik, k…ôn n…®kin t…ômat…ôht n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Jekop.\f*   
\p
\v 49 K…ôn Nataniel t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!I…ôg…ôtun! !Ik N…ôt…® Uhg…®n! !Ik Kig r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel!‚Äù   
\p
\v 50 Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik n…ômatahat…ôt…ô lak m…ôto-inu io em…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô en…ôm…ôplan r…ôk…®s ik, nian n…ômat…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôn …ôh e n…ôuk…ôt…® n…®g fik? Ik on…ôpan…ôplan nat asol m…®n tapr…ôk…®s-in it…ôm u.‚Äù  
\v 51 K…ôn m…ôn m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, on…ôpanot…ôplan napu…ô oter…ôh, k…ôn nagelo m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n koat…ôr moatuw…®n e neai, k…ôn moteiuaiu moatuwa o N…ôt…® Et…ômim.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:51 \ft Jen 28:12\f*   
\c 2  
\s1 Marit kit …ôp…ôh Kena  
\m
\v 1 K…ôm…ôn ni…ôh in, katol mar…®t kit …ôp…ôh Kena, latu…ônu kit e Kalili. K…ôn mama r…ôha Iesu in …ôp…ôh ik…®n ilat min.  
\v 2 K…ôn ilat kotaun-in-p…ôn m…®n Iesu ne r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim, m…ôm…ô ilat m…®n okotuw…®n e mar…®t …ôh.  
\v 3 K…ôn e nian …ôh, k…ômot…ôn…®m rafin wain, k…ôn mama r…ôha Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúR…ôhalat wain t…ôm…®k…ô.‚Äù  
\v 4 M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?P…ôtan, t…ôhrol nakat…ôl…ôh…ôu-pa nat u k…ôm io? Nian r…ôhak t…ôsuwam…ôn …ôh.‚Äù  
\v 5 M…ôto r…ôhan mama t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm iolw…ôk m…®n r…ôha mar…®t m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat on…ôkot…ôk…ôike motol nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm in ot…ôn.‚Äù  
\v 6 Nuwig…® nat asol ilat sikis, k…ôm…ôl…®n …ôh-ik…®n …ôh o n…ôhau, m…ôm…ô net…ôm Isrel ilat kot…ôike motaikuas e nelm…®lat m…ôm…ô ilat okotaru…ôtu…ôh e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n. Nuwig…® nat m…®n un, k…ômol e k…ôpiel, k…ôn ok…ôm…ô naka kiti…ôh t…®tun nos…ôn wan-hanr…®t lita n…ôhau.\fig |alt="man pouring into jars" src="LB00135B.TIF" size="span" loc="Jhn 2:6-10" ref="Jon 2:6" \fig*  
\v 7 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm koatol w…ôk m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOt…ôtu-p…ôn n…ôhau e nuwig…® nat m…®n un.‚Äù K…ôn k…ômot…ôtu ilat kot…ôrioah w…®r.  
\v 8 K…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOt…ôtu r…ôk…®s n…ôhau neen motos motuw…®n k…ôm et…ôm t…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e mar…®t.‚Äù K…ôn ilat k…ômotol mihin.   
\p
\v 9 K…ôn nian suah un t…ôm…ôn…®m asg…ôw…®n, m…ôto n…ôhau t…®nol r…ôk…®s wain lan. M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm t…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e mar…®t u, in t…ôruru m…ôm…ô k…ômos hi…ô wain u. Net…ôm m…®n …ôm un it…ôm k…ômotos n…ôhau motuwa, ilat …ôm kot…®tun. K…ôn et…ôm t…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e mar…®t t…ômaun-in et…ôm t…ômol mar…®t,  
\v 10 m…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian rafin net…ômim kotaup…ôn motos-iar…ôp wain w…®r, k…ôn uaris…®g net…ômim kot…ôn…®m tep…ôt un, k…ônu k…ôpanos-iar…ôp it…ôm u t…ôs…ôw…®r p…®k…ôn. M…ôto ik natos …ôh it…ôm t…ôw…®r muwa m…ôtoarus-pa u-roiu.‚Äù  
\v 11 K…ôn inu n…ômt…ôtin it…ôm Iesu t…ôm…ôtuoun ag…®n-…ôh lan mol. K…ôn in t…ômol ik…®n Kena, latu…ônu kit e Kalili. N…ômt…ôtin …ôh, in t…ôm…ôg…ôtun nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n lan, k…ôn r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n, k…ômotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k lan.   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôhg-iar…ôp net…ômim it…ôm kotol maket e  //  Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n  
\r (Mat 21:12-13; Mak 11:15-18;  //  Luk 19:45-46)  
\p
\v 12 Uaris…®g e mar…®t …ôh, in t…ômeiuaiu muw…®n e taon …ôh Kapaneam ilat r…ôhan mama ne pian m…®n ne r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n. K…ôn k…ômotat…®g nian …ôku…ôk…®r …ôm …ôh-ik…®n …ôh.  
\v 13 K…ôn t…®nuwa iu…ôhk…®r o nian r…ôha lafet kit r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel it…ôm kat…ôn m…ôm…ô lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn.\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Eks 12; Dut 16:1-6\f* K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôr muw…®n …ôp…ôh Jerusalem.   
\p
\v 14 E Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, Iesu t…ôm…ôplan net…ômim it…ôm koatos m…ôni e kau, ne sipsip, ne iouen, m…ôm…ô net…ômim okotos-n…ômt…®n. K…ôn net…ômim neen …ôh-ik…®n, ilat koatol sen…®s e m…ôni r…ôha net…ôm ik p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.  
\v 15 K…ôn in tos t…ôul…ô neen, m…ôt…ôl o nalis-alis…ôn it…ôm. K…ôn in m…®t…ôp net…ôm m…®n un ilat r…ôhalat kau m…®n ne sipsip m…®n m…ôm…ô okotiet e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôht…ôg m…ôni r…ôha net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koatol sen…®s lan, k…ôn t…ômahwin-ahwin r…ôhalat tep…®l m…®n.  
\v 16 K…ôn m…ôhai ilat m…®n u it…ôm koatol-sal…®m-in iouen m…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ot…ôm…®k nat m…®n un motiet! !It…ômat sotol…ôn Nim…ô R…ôha Tata r…ôhak tuwa in nim…ô kit r…ôha nol…ôn mak…®t!‚Äù  
\v 17 K…ôn net…ômim r…ôhan, n…®kilat tu…ôh n…ôghat…ôn kit e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ekolkeike p…®k Nim…ô R…ôham e n…®kik, n…®kik tat…®m…®s-p…ôn lan.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:17 \ft Sam 69:9\f*   
\p
\v 18 K…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel kot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Pah t…ômol m…ôm…ô n…ôk…®tun nol…ôn nat u? !Ol n…ômt…ôtin m…ôm…ô ot…ôg…ôtun …ôtuat…®p k…ôm it…®mat!‚Äù   
\p
\v 19 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô it…ômat nakot…ôr…ôk…®n Nim…ô u R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn nian k…®s…®l …ôm, io ekil…ôk…®n m…®n t…ôtul.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:19 \ft Mat 26:60-61; 27:40; Mak 14:57-59; 15:29.\f*   
\p
\v 20 K…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n un kot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei, n…ôman! Net…ômim k…ômotol w…ôk p…®k e nup ilat rafin foti-sikis motil…ôk…®n Nim…ô u R…ôha Uhg…®n. ?Onakahrol nulan mil…ôk…®n e nian k…®s…®l …ôm?‚Äù   
\p
\v 21 M…ôto Nim…ô …ôh R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm Iesu tat…ôghat-in, in n…®p…ôt…®n.  
\v 22 K…ôn uaris…®g, nian in t…®n…®m…®s r…ôk…®s, k…ôn m…®n…ômeg…ôh m…®n, k…ôn r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n, n…®kilat tu…ôh n…ôghat…ôn …ôh r…ôhan it…ôm t…ôm…ôn. K…ôn ilat k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, ne n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Iesu t…ômat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat.   
\s1 Iesu t…®n…ôm…®tun r…ôk…®s n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…®n r…ôha net…ômim  
\p
\v 23 Nian …ôh Iesu t…ôm…ôtat…®g e Jerusalem e nian r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômot…ôplan n…ômt…ôtin m…®n it…ôm in t…ômol, k…ôn k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e n…ôrg…®n.  
\v 24 M…ôto Iesu in t…ôm…®tun nat it…ôm t…ôtat…®g e n…®kilat, k…ôn m…ôsatahat…ôt…ô…ôn elat.  
\v 25 Okol suah kit t…ôs…ôtul-ar…ôp…ôn m…ôghat r…ôha net…ômim lan, m…ôto-inu Iesu t…®tun rafin n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ômim.\f + \fr 2:25 \ft Jon 1:47; 6:61; 13:11\f*   
\c 3  
\s1 Nikotimas t…ômuw…®n m…ôplan Iesu  
\m
\v 1 Et…ôm-iasol kit e noanol r…ôha Isrel, n…ôrg…®n u, Nikotimas.\f + \fr 3:1 \ft Jon 7:50-51; 19:39-42\f* In Farisi kit.  
\v 2 K…ôn nian kit lap…®n, in t…ômuw…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôghat ilau Iesu. In t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôg…ôtun, it…®mat ekot…®tun m…ôm…ô ik i…ôg…ôtun kit it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa ik nakuwa, m…ôto-inu suah kit okol t…ôsol…ôn n…ômt…ôtin m…®n un ik nakatol ok…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôsat…®g…ôn ron.‚Äù   
\p
\v 3 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô, ok…ôm…ô et…ômim kit t…ôsaiir wi…ôn, okol in t…ôs…ôplan…ôn n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:3 \ft Jon 1:13; 1 Pita 1:23; Jem 1:18\f*   
\p
\v 4 K…ôn Nikotimas, narm…®n t…ômiw…®g p…®k, k…ôn m…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Et…ôm t…®nol iahgin r…ôk…®s, ot…ôhrol maiir m…ôtm…ôt…®g m…®n? !In okol t…ôsuw…®n m…®n…ôn e n…ôrp…® r…ôhan mama k…ôn maiir-pa m…®n!‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô, ok…ôm…ô et…ômim t…ôsaiir-wi…ôn e n…ôhau ne Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, okol t…ôsuw…®n…ôn mat…®g ahgin n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Esik 36:25-27; Efes 5:26; Taet 3:5\f*  
\v 6 N…®p…ôt…®t…ôm t…ôtaiir …ôm e n…®ta r…ôha et…ômim …ôm, m…ôto Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n …ôm un in tatol m…ôm…ô narm…®t…ôm t…ôtaiir wi m…®n.  
\v 7 T…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô narm…ôm otiw…®g m…ôto-inu em…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòOn…ôkot…ôk…ôike motaiir wi m…®n.‚Äô  
\v 8 Tahmen …ôm e n…®m…ôtag tat…®s…®-p…ô ik…®n kit, matelel nat matuw…®n ik…®n kit it…ôm in tolkeike m…ôm…ô otuw…®n-p…ôn ik…®n. Nat…ôto …ôm, m…ôto ik n…ôk…ôruru m…ôm…ô t…ôm…®s…®-p…ô hi…ô, k…ôn matuw…ô hi…ô. K…ôn e suat…®p kiti…ôh …ôm, kitat k…ôsot…ôplan…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, m…ôto koat…ôplan …ôm r…ôhan w…ôk e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha et…ômim it…ôm t…ômaiir wi m…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Esik 37:9\f*   
\p
\v 9 K…ôn …ômun, Nikotimas t…ôtap…ôh o Iesu m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Nat…®mnat m…®n un, ot…ôhrol nulan muwa?‚Äù   
\p
\v 10 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk i…ôg…ôtun asol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. ?T…ôhrol n…ôk…ôruru nat…®mnat m…®n u?‚Äù  
\v 11 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô, n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u it…ôm ekoat…ôn ilat, it…®mat ekot…®tun w…®r, k…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm ioat…ôn-iar…ôp, it…®mat enot…ôplan r…ôk…®s. M…ôto it…ômat n…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhat…®mat.  
\v 12 Io iat…ôn …ôm nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm katol e n…ôtueint…ôn …ôm u, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn e r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn. ?K…ôn ok…ôm…ô ek…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm katol e Nego e Neai, nakot…ôhrol nulan motahat…ôt…ô lan?  
\v 13 Suah kit t…ôsuw…®n…ôn …ôp…ôh il…®s e Nego e Neai, meiuaiu-pa, m…ôn-iar…ôp nian kit ne. M…ôto N…ôt…® Et…ômim …ôm, t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn iman ik…®n e Nego e Neai, meiuaiu-pa, t…®tun n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn.   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúAup…ôn, …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n, Moses t…ôm…®l…ôs narm…® s…®nek kit, m…ôtu-p…ôr il…®s e n…®g …ôf…ôm…ôh kit, k…ôn m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr.\f + \fr 3:14 \ft Nam 21:4-9; Jon 8:28; 12:32; 12:24\f* K…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, ok…ôike k…®l…ôs-ip…ôr mihin N…ôt…® Et…ômim,  
\v 15 m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm okotahat…ôt…ô lan, ilat okotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n.  
\v 16 Tol n…ôhlan, Uhg…®n t…ômolkeike p…®k net…ômim e n…ôtueint…ôn, tol-p…ôn in t…ômos-ipa N…ôt…®n Noan Kiti…ôh ∆èm, m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô lan, ilat okol k…ôsot…®m…®s…ôn, m…ôto okotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n.\f + \fr 3:16 \ft Esik 18:23,32; 37:9; 1 Tim 2:4; 4:10; 1 Jon 4:9-10\f*  
\v 17 Uhg…®n in t…ôm…ôsahl-ipam…ôn N…ôt…®n tuwa e n…ôtueint…ôn u m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, m…ôto in t…ômahl-ipa, m…ôm…ô otuwa mol suat…®p o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ômim e n…ôtueint…ôn.   
\p
\v 18 ‚ÄúEt…ômim it…ôm t…ôtahat…ôt…ô lan, Uhg…®n okol t…ôs…ôn…ôn nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhan, m…ôto et…ômim it…ôm t…ôsahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan, Uhg…®n t…®n…ôn r…ôk…®s nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhan, m…ôto-inu in t…ôsahat…ôt…ô…ôn e N…ôt…® Uhg…®n Noan Kiti…ôh ∆èm.  
\v 19 Uhg…®n t…ôtakil net…ômim e nol…ôn u m…ôm…ô, N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn t…®nuwa r…ôk…®s e n…ôtueint…ôn, m…ôto net…ômim k…ôsotolkeike…ôn N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn. Ilat k…ômoatolkeike Napin…ôp…ôn il…ô, m…ôto-inu nian rafin r…ôhalat nol…ôn, t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn.  
\v 20 Et…ômim it…ôm tatol nol…ôn it…ôm t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn, in tet…ôhau N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn. K…ôn in t…ôsuwam…ôn e N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn, m…ôto-inu in tap…ôs m…ôm…ô N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn …ôh otasi…ôg…ôp…®n r…ôhan nol…ôn m…®n.   
\p
\v 21 M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p r…ôha n…®pahrien…ôn in otuwa e N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn, m…ôm…ô N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn …ôh, in otasi…ôg…ôp…®n r…ôhan nol…ôn k…ôn mat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô in t…ômol ilat e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn …ôm r…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äù   
\s1 Jon T…ôm…ôghat-in M…®n Iesu  
\p
\v 22 Uaris…®g e nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh, Iesu ne r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim k…ômotuw…®n e n…®t…ôn Jutia. T…ômat…®g nuw…ôh m…ôs…®n ilat min ik…®n …ôh, k…ôn matol baptais e net…ômim.  
\v 23 M…ôto e nian …ôh, Jon m…®n, in tatol baptais e net…ômim …ôp…ôh ik…®n kit iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o Salim, n…ôrg…®n u, Aenon, m…ôto-inu, ik…®n …ôh, n…ôhau tep…ôt ik…®n. K…ôn net…ômim koatuw…®n ik…®n …ôh, m…ôm…ô Jon otol baptais elat.  
\v 24 E nian …ôh, k…ôm…ôs…®l…ôs-ip…ôn…ôn …ôh Jon e kalapus.   
\p
\v 25 K…ôn net…ômim neen r…ôha Jon, ilat k…ômot…ôrg…ôh…ôu ilat et…ôm Isrel kit, o nol…ôn …ôtuat…®p it…ôm et…ômim ot…ôk…ôike maikuas m…ôm…ô in otaru…ôtu…ôh e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n.  
\v 26 K…ôn ilat k…ômotuw…®n kehm Jon, mot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôg…ôtun, ik n…ôk…®tun et…ômim kit u aup…ôn it…ôlau min …ôp…ôh ent…ôn…®p…ôn-p…ôn ik…®n e n…ôhau Jotan, k…ôn ik n…ôm…ôtul-ar…ôp mat…ôghat-in k…ôm net…ômim. Roiu …ôh, in t…®natol baptais e net…ômim. K…ôn ilat rafin k…®noatuw…®n ron.‚Äù   
\p
\v 27 K…ôn Jon t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ômim t…ôruru nol…ôn nat kiti…ôh ne, ok…ôm…ô Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh e Nego e Neai t…ôsos-ip…ôn…ôn w…ôk …ôh k…ôm in.  
\v 28 It…ômat u noat…ôtul-pa ron io. It…ômat n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô iat…ôn nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòS…ôn…ôm…ô io Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa.‚Äô M…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa io m…ôm…ô iakaup…ôn muwa, k…ôn Kristo in ot…ôpanuaris…®g.  
\v 29 Eku…ôh nimaa n…ôghat…ôn kit k…ôm it…ômat. Et…ômim it…ôm in otol mar…®t e p…ôtan kit, p…ôtan …ôh tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm in. K…ôn et…ômim u, net…ômim koat…ôsahgin m…ôm…ô in otuwa e lafet r…ôha mar…®t, k…ôn n…®kilat kotagien lan k…ôn mot…ôto n…ôwian, ilat k…ôsotetet…ôn in. K…ôn io u, ekahmen e in kit it…ôm tat…ôsahgin …ôm mat…ôt…ôl…®g-in o n…ôto…ôn n…ôwian, k…ôn io m…®n eset…ôhak…ôn k…ôm in o net…ômim it…ôm koatuaris…®g-in, m…ôto n…®kik tagien m…ôrioah ron.  
\v 30 Kristo …ôh, in ot…ôk…ôike muwa m…ô in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in io, k…ônu io ek…ôike meiuaiu.‚Äù   
\p
\v 31 Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn il…®s e Nego e Neai, in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in net…ômim rafin. Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôtan …ôm e n…ôtueint…ôn, in et…ômim …ôm r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, k…ôn in t…®tun …ôm n…ôn…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u e n…ôtueint…ôn u. M…ôto, et…ômim it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn il…®s e neai in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s net…ômim rafin.  
\v 32 In tat…ôtul-ar…ôp o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm in t…ôm…ôplan k…ôn m…®n…ôto r…ôk…®s, m…ôto et…ômim kit ne t…ôsahat…ôt…ô…ôn e r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn.  
\v 33 M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm t…ômos r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn k…ôn m…ôtahat…ôt…ô lan, in tat…ôtul-ar…ôp m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn, in n…®pahrien…ôn.  
\v 34 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu et…ômim …ôh it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa tuwa, in tat…ôn-iar…ôp …ôm n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n. Kot…®tun m…ôm…ô in tat…ôn-iar…ôp …ôm n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn Narm…®n R…ôhan t…ôrioah lan, okol k…ôsol…ôn mak lan k…ôsehm…ôn namnun.  
\v 35 ∆èw…ôh, Tata Uhg…®n in tolkeike p…®k N…ôt…®n …ôh, k…ôn in t…®n…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat rafin e nelm…®n.  
\v 36 Et…ômim u it…ôm t…ôtahat…ôt…ô e N…ôt…® Uhg…®n u, in tatos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n u, namnun t…®k…ô. K…ôn m…ôto, et…ôm tat…ôht n…ôwia N…ôt…®n u, in okol t…ôsos…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n u nian kit ne, m…ôto-inu et…ômim it…ôm tol n…ôhlan, nem…ôha r…ôha Uhg…®n tatuw…®n ron namnun t…®k…ô.   
\c 4  
\s1 Iesu t…ômat…ôghat k…ôm p…ôtan Sameria  
\m
\v 1 Farisi m…®n k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn, m…ôm…ô Iesu in t…®natiuw-pa net…ômim tep…ôt k…®notuwa ron, k…ôn in tatol baptais elat tep…ôt. R…ôhalat nampa tapr…ôk…®s-in nampa r…ôha net…ômim r…ôha Jon.  
\v 2 (M…ôto n…®pahrien…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô Iesu in tatol baptais elat, net…ômim m…®n …ôm r…ôhan ilat kotol baptais e net…ômim.)  
\v 3 K…ôn nian Iesu t…®n…®tun m…ôm…ô Farisi m…®n k…®not…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ôn in t…ômiet e Jutia m…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn …ôp…ôh Kalili.   
\p
\v 4 K…ôn nian in t…ômatuw…®n ik…®n …ôh, t…ôm…ôn m…ô ot…ôk…ôike muw…®n-p…ôn Sameria ik…®n.\f + \fr 4:4 \ft E nian …ôh, ti…ôk…®s o net…ôm Isrel m…ôm…ô okotuw…®n ima net…ôm Sameria, m…ôto-inu e r…ôhalat nehm…ôn, net…ôm Sameria ilat kotamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n.\f*\fig |alt="Samaritan woman with Jesus at well" src="LB00302B.TIF" size="span" loc="Jhn 4:4-10" ref="Jon 4:4" \fig*  
\v 5 K…ôn in t…ômuw…®n-p…ôn e taon kit e Sameria, n…ôrg…®n un, Saeka. Taon …ôh, in iu…ôhk…®r o n…®m…ôpt…ôn kit it…ôm aup…ôn Jekop in t…ôm…ôtat…®p…ôn\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Jen 48:22; Jos 24:32\f* k…ôm n…ôt…®n u Josep.  
\v 6 K…ôn wel r…ôha Jekop …ôh-ik…®n. K…ôn Iesu t…®n…ôpou ag…®n, m…ôto-inu in t…ômaliw…ôk e suat…®p …ôf…ôm…ôh, k…ôn tuwa m…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr iu…ôhk…®r o wel, m…®tameg. E nian …ôh, in t…®nol tina.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft E nian …ôh, m…®tgar t…®n…ôtul …ôtuat…®p.\f*   
\p
\v 7-8 K…ôn r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n k…ômotuw…®n …ôp…ôh e taon, m…ôm…ô okotos-n…ômt…®n nagw…ôn…ôn. K…ôn p…ôtan Sameria kit, t…ômuwa m…ôm…ô ot…ôtu n…ôhau. K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEh. Os-ipa-tu n…ôhau noan m…ôs…®n k…ôm io. Ekolkeike m…ôm…ô ek…ôn…®m.‚Äù   
\p
\v 9 K…ôn p…ôtan Sameria u, t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! Ik et…ôm Isrel un, k…ôn io p…ôtan Sameria. ?T…ôhrol nakat…ôtap…ôh-in-pa n…ôhau k…ôm io?‚Äù T…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôhlan m…ôto-inun et…ôm Jutia ne et…ôm Sameria k…ôsu…ôn…®m k…ôl…ôh…ôn n…ôhau e pan…®k…®n kiti…ôh.   
\p
\v 10 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk n…ôk…ôruru nat naka it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike m…ôm…ô otos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik. K…ôn ik m…ôruru m…®n io, io u, iat…ôtap…ôh-in-p…®n…ô n…ôhau k…ôm ik. Ok…ôm…ô ik n…ôk…®tun, ik onak…ôtap…ôh-in-pa n…ôhau ron io. K…ôn io oekos-ip…®n…ô n…ôhau meg…ôh.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:10 \ft P…ôtan u t…ôm…ôs…®tun w…®r…ôn n…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn n…ôhau meg…ôh. N…ôghat…ôn …ôh, n…®p…ôt…®n …ôtuat…®p un n…ômt…® n…ôhau kit it…ôm talien m…®tapu…ôl-apu…ôl. M…ôto Iesu in tat…ôghat-in at…®p in, m…ôm…ô Narm…®n R…ôhan in tatos-ip…ôn n…ôhau lil…®n. Aes 44:3; 55:1; Jer 2:13; 17:13; Sek 14:8; Jon 7:37-38; Nol ∆èp…ôn 7:17; 21:6; 22:1,17.\f*   
\p
\v 11 K…ôn p…ôtan un, t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol, ik r…ôham p…ôk…®t t…®k…ô, k…ôn wel u, in …ôp…ôh l…ôhau is…ôu. ?N…ôhau meg…ôh un nakat…ôn m…ô onak…ôtu ahrol minu lan?  
\v 12 R…ôhatat pipi Jekop u aup…ôn, in t…ômos-ipa wel u k…ôm itat, k…ôn in t…ômat…ôtu n…ôhau ik…®n n…®m…®n, ilat nen…ôt…®n m…®n, ne r…ôhan m…®n kau m…®n. ?K…ôn t…ôhrol? ?Ik nakapr…ôk…®s-in Jekop, o?‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNet…ôm koat…ôn…®m n…ôhau e wel u, ilat ok…ôpanotoaoa m…®n.  
\v 14 M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm ot…ôn…®m n…ôhau it…ôm io ekos-ip…ôn k…ôm in, okol t…ôsoaoa m…®n…ôn nian kit ne.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Jon 6:35\f* N…ôhau it…ôm io oekos-ip…ôn k…ôm in, in tahmen e n…ômt…® n…ôhau kit it…ôm t…®tapu…ôl-apu…ôl m…ôtaiu …ôp…ôh im…ô e n…®kin nian rafin, matos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n k…ôm in, it…ôm ot…ôsol…ôn namnun.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Sam 42:1-2; 63:1, Aes 12:3; 41:17-18; 44:3; 49:10; 55:1; Jer 2:13; 17:13; Jon 7:38\f*   
\p
\v 15 K…ôn p…ôtan un t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Et…ôm-iasol, awi! Os-ipa-tu n…ôhau un kit k…ôm io, m…ôm…ô io ek…ôsoaoa m…®n…ôn nian kit, k…ôn m…ôsuwa m…®n…ôn u ik…®n-u, m…ôtu n…ôhau.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:15 \ft Jon 6:34\f*   
\p
\v 16 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUw…®n maun-in-p…ôn r…ôham iagu…®hl, k…ôn muea ik…®n-u.‚Äù  
\v 17 K…ôn p…ôtan un t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo r…ôhak iagu…®hl t…®k…ô.‚Äù M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNakat…ôn pahrien m…ôm…ô r…ôham iagu…®hl t…®k…ô.  
\v 18 M…ôto-inu ik, n…ôm…ôt…ôu-p…ôn r…ôk…®s n…ôman faif, k…ôn i…ôrman u it…ôm it…ômlau min nakatuat…®g u-roiu, s…ôn…ôm…ô r…ôham …ôtuat…®p iagu…®hl. N…ôghat…ôn r…ôham u-roiu, in n…®pahrien…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn p…ôtan u, t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol, iat…ôplan m…ôm…ô ik ien kit r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 20 T…®p…®t…®mat m…®n aup…ôn, ilat k…ômot…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s e n…®tot …ôp…ôh, m…ôto it…ômat net…ôm Isrel, nakoat…ôn m…ôm…ô Jerusalem …ôm un, ok…ôk…ôike kan ik…®n kat…ôfak.‚Äù   
\p
\v 21 M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôtan, ik onak…ôk…ôike m…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn. Nian …ôh-ik…®n tatuwa, m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôsot…ôfak m…®n…ôn k…ôm Tata Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh e n…®tot asol …ôh, ne Jerusalem m…®n.  
\v 22 It…ômat net…ôm Sameria, it…ômat noat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôto it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru in. M…ôto it…®mat ioat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n u, ekot…®tun in, m…ôto-inun suat…®p r…ôha Uhg…®n o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ômim in t…ôm…®s…®-pa et…®mat, net…ôm Isrel.\f + \fr 4:22 \ft Rom 3:1,2; 9:4,5; 15:8,9\f*  
\v 23 M…ôto ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô nian …ôh t…®nuwa r…ôk…®s, nian Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n in otasitu e i…ôfak pahrien m…®n, mol ilat m…ôm…ô ilat okot…®tun w…®r Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n u, in Uhg…®n pahrien, k…ôn mol ilat m…ôm…ô ilat okot…ôfak k…ôm in e n…®kilat pahrien. M…ôto-inu Tata Uhg…®n in tateg…ôs-in i…ôfak m…®n it…ôm koatol n…ôhlan.  
\v 24 Uhg…®n in s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ômim. K…ôp…ô. In narm…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôfak k…ôm in, ilat kot…ôk…ôike mot…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n u, in Uhg…®n pahrien, k…ôn ilat kot…ôk…ôike mot…ôfak k…ôm in e n…®kilat pahrien e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Narm…®n R…ôhan.‚Äù   
\p
\v 25 K…ôn p…ôtan u, t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo en…®tun m…ôm…ô Mesaea u, ot…ôk…ôike muwa. Inu, k…ôtaun-in m…ôm…ô Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa. K…ôn nian otuwa, k…ôn in t…®tun n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn nat…®mnat rafin k…ôm kitat.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:25 \ft Net…ôm Sameria k…ômot…®tun e naoa r…ôha Dut 18:15-19 m…ôm…ô Kristo in ot…ôn …ôp k…ôm ilat nalp…ôkau…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n k…ôm ilat.\f*   
\p
\v 26 Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u inu,\f + \fr 4:26 \ft E kopi oas m…®n neen r…ôha Niutesteman it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris aup…ôn, n…ôghat…ôn u r…ôha Iesu, ‚ÄúIo u inu,‚Äù t…ôm…ôn ik…®n-u ne ik…®n tep…ôt m…®n e naoa u, in tahmen ahmen …ôm e n…ôghat…ôn kit it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômat…ôn o n…ôn at…®p…ôn n…ôrg…®n k…ôm Moses, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo Etat…®g.‚Äù Onakehm e naoa r…ôha Eks 3:14-16. Iesu tat…ôn n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, matol …ôp in m…ôm…ô in Uhg…®n. Iesu in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in Uhg…®n, k…ôn mat…®g mat…ôn m…®n m…ôm…ô in Kristo it…ôm p…ôtan …ôh tat…ôn.\f* iat…ôghat k…ôm ik.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:26 \ft Jon 8:24; 9:35-37\f*   
\p
\v 27 K…ôn roiu ag…®n-…ôh, net…ômim r…ôha Iesu k…ômot…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n. K…ôn narm…®lat t…ômiw…®g p…®k nian k…ômot…ôplan in tat…ôghat ilau p…ôtan kit. M…ôto ilat kit t…ôm…ôs…ôtap…ôh…ôn ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik nakolkeike naka?‚Äù o ‚Äú?Ik nat…ôghat k…ôm p…ôtan …ôh o naka?‚Äù   
\p
\v 28 K…ôn p…ôtan u, t…ômap…ôs r…ôhan nuwig…® n…ôhau tat…ôp…ôl…ôh, m…®t…ôl…®g muw…®n …ôp…ôh e taon. T…ômuw…®n mat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ômim ik…®n …ôh m…ôm…ô,  
\v 29 ‚ÄúEh. Otuw…®n-tu mot…ôplan-tu suah kit …ôh-ik…®n …ôh, in t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp rafin nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm io ematol. ?Ok…ôm…ô naka in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa?‚Äù  
\v 30 K…ôn ilat k…ômotiet e taon …ôh, m…®noatuw…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan-tu Iesu.   
\s1 Iesu t…ômu…ôh nimaa n…ôghat…ôn e nagw…ôn…ôn  
\p
\v 31 K…ôn e nian …ôh, net…ômim r…ôha Iesu koatu…ôh n…®kin m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôg…ôtun, ik agw…ôn kit.‚Äù   
\p
\v 32 M…ôto in t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo n…®gak …ôp…ôh nagw…ôn…ôn it…ôm it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:32 \ft Job 23:12; Jon 6:27\f*   
\p
\v 33 Tol n…ôhlan, r…ôhan net…ômim k…®noat…ôtap…ôh-…ôtap…ôh olat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Tahro? ?Ok…ôm-naka suah kit t…ômos-ip…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn kit k…ôm in, o?‚Äù   
\p
\v 34 M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa io iakuwa, k…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn u n…®gak, m…ôm…ô iakatol nat…®mnat it…ôm in tolkeike m…ôm…ô oekol.\f + \fr 4:34 \ft Jon 5:30, 8:29\f* K…ônu iakol rafin w…ôk m…®n it…ôm in t…ômos-ipa m…ôm…ô oekol, o nol namnun…ôn r…ôhan w…ôk.   
\p
\v 35 ‚ÄúIt…ômat n…ôkot…®tun-tu n…ôghat…ôn kit u kat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòM…ôw…®g kuw…®t …ôh-ik…®n t…ôtat…®g m…ôm…ô okotoarus nian r…ôha n…ôul…ôk-in…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn e nasum…ôn.‚Äô M…ôto io iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat, ot…ôplan-tu nagw…ôn…ôn u e nasum…ôn. Roiu …ôh, n…®mal…®lat t…®nap…ô r…ôk…®s. Nian r…ôha n…ôul…ôk…ôn …ôh-roiu.\f + \fr 4:35 \ft Nian Iesu tat…ôghat-in nagw…ôn…ôn e nasum…ôn it…ôm n…®mal…®lat t…®nap…ô r…ôk…®s, in tat…ôn …ôtuat…®p …ôm m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ot…ôplan-tu! Net…ômim k…®not…ôtul mat…®p r…ôk…®s. Sotol…ôn k…ôm…®n motap…®l o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n tahmen-p…ôn …ôm e net…ôm koatol k…ôm…®n o n…ôul…ôk…ôn, k…ôn moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòM…ôw…®g kuw…®t …ôp…ôh ik…®n, k…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn t…ôpan…ôm…®t…ô.‚Äô K…ôp…ô, net…ômim k…®nat…ôtul mat…®p r…ôk…®s o nos…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äù\f*   
\p
\v 36 ‚ÄúEt…ômim r…ôha n…ôul…ôk…ôn t…®nuwa, m…®n…ôtuoun m…®natos r…ôk…®s r…ôhan n…ôtou…ôn. K…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn u, in t…ôm…ôul…ôk in o n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n. E nol…ôn u, et…ômim it…ôm t…ôtasum ne et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôul…ôk in mos matuwa, ilau k…ôr…ôn n…®kilau otagien.  
\v 37 N…ôghat…ôn kit u kat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòSuah kit tuw…®n m…ô otasum, m…ôto et…ôm p…®s…®n kit m…®n ot…ôul…ôk-in m…ôm…®k muwa.‚Äô N…ôghat…ôn u, in n…®pahrien…ôn.  
\v 38 Io emahl-ip…ôn it…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkotuw…®n mot…ôul…ôk e nasum…ôn it…ôm it…ômat n…ôm…ôsotasum-in…ôn. Net…ôm p…®s…®n m…®n, ilat k…ômotasum in. K…ôn it…ômat n…®noat…ôhl noa r…ôhalat w…ôk.‚Äù   
\s1 Net…ôm Sameria tep…ôt k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu  
\p
\v 39 K…ôn e taon u, net…ôm Sameria tep…ôt, ilat k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu m…ôto-inu p…ôtan …ôh t…ômat…ôtul-ar…ôp mat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIesu t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm io ematol.‚Äù   
\p
\v 40 K…ôn nian net…ôm Sameria k…ômotuw…®n motehm, k…ôn k…ômot…ôk…ôike k…ôm in m…ôm…ô otuw…®n motat…®g ilat min. K…ôn Iesu t…ômuw…®n moatat…®g o nian k…ôiu.  
\v 41 K…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt m…®n k…ômotahat…ôt…ô lan e r…ôhan m…®n n…ôghat…ôn.   
\p
\v 42 K…ôn moat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm p…ôtan u m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…®mat emotahat…ôt…ô lan o n…ôghat…ôn u it…ôm ik n…ôm…ôn-ipa, m…ôto roiu …ôh, ekoatahat…ôt…ô lan m…ôto-inu it…®mat …ôm emot…ôto r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn m…®n, k…ôn mot…®tun pahrien m…ôm…ô in Iosmeg…ôh r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:42 \ft 1 Jon 4:14\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ômol-w…®r n…ôt…®  //  et…ôm-iasol kit r…ôha kig  
\p
\v 43 Nian Iesu t…ômat…®g mos nian k…ôiu r…ôk…®s ik…®n …ôh, in t…ômiet muw…®n Kalili.  
\v 44 M…ôto-inu aup…ôn, in t…ômat…ôn m…ôm…ô ien m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n, natim…ôlat m…®n, ilat k…ôsot…®siai-in…ôn ilat.\f + \fr 4:44 \ft Nat …ôpnap…®n Iesu t…ômaiir latu…ônu Petlehem, e n…ôpt…ôn asol Jutia, net…ômim kot…ôplan m…ôm…ô in et…ôm Nasaret …ôp…ôh Kalili, m…ôto-inu t…ôm…ôtat…®g nuw…ôh ik…®n …ôh (Jon 7:41, 18:5, 19:19). Net…ôm Isrel e Jutia ne Kalili tep…ôt k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn pahrien lan, r…ôhalat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn t…®m…ôtm…ôt…®g …ôm lan, nian kot…ôplan in tatol nat p…®sp…®s neen (Jon 1:11; 2:18,23-25; 4:45,48; 6:2, 41, 66). M…ôto net…ôm Samaria it…ôm kotat…®g e taon u Saika, ilat k…ômotahat…ôt…ô pahrien lan, m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa (Jon 4:40-42).\f*  
\v 45 Net…ôm Kalili, aup…ôn ilat k…ômotuw…®n Jerusalem moatol lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, k…ôn e nian …ôh, ilat k…ômot…ôplan nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm in t…ômol ik…®n …ôh. K…ôn nian Iesu t…ômuw…®n Kalili, n…®kilat t…ômagien ron.   
\p
\v 46 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n e latu…ônu Kena, …ôp…ôh Kalili. Ik…®n …ôh aup…ôn, in t…ômol n…ôhau tuwa mol wain.\f + \fr 4:46 \ft Jon 2:1-11\f* K…ôn e Kapaneam, et…ôm-iasol r…ôha kig t…ôtat…®g ik…®n. K…ôn n…ôt…®n kit tat…®m…®s.  
\v 47 K…ôn nian suah u t…ôm…ôto m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn u Jutia m…®nuwa r…ôk…®s Kalili, k…ôn in t…ômuwa m…ôplan Iesu. K…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn ron m…ôm…ô oteiuaiu muw…®n …ôp…ôh Kapaneam k…ôn mol-w…®r n…ôt…®n. M…ôto-inu suak…ôku nol ot…®m…®s.   
\p
\v 48 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm suah un m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!N…ôman! It…ômat u, nakot…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôplan …ôm n…ômt…ôtin m…®n ne nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm narm…®t…ômat otiw…®g ron aup…ôn, k…ônu uaris…®g un, n…ôpanotahat…ôt…ô lak. M…ôto ok…ôm…ô n…ôsot…ôplan…ôn, okol n…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lak.‚Äù   
\p
\v 49 K…ôn suah un t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Et…ôm-iasol, awi! !P…ôs kian u…ôhai …ôm! !Ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn roiu n…ôt…®k t…®m…®s!‚Äù  
\v 50 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUw…®n; n…ôt…®m ot…ôpan…ômeg…ôh.‚Äù K…ôn suah un t…ômahat…ôt…ô e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Iesu k…ôn m…®t…ôl…®g.   
\p
\v 51 Nian in t…ômatuw…®n …ôh e suat…®p, t…ôm…ôplan r…ôhan iolw…ôk m…®n, k…ôn ilat kot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúR…ôham suak…ôku t…®n…ômeg…ôh r…ôk…®s.‚Äù  
\v 52 K…ôn in t…ôm…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôm…ôw…®r e nian naka?‚Äù K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôni…ôp ehnaip…ôn e wan klok r…ôhan n…ôg…ôpan…ôn t…ôm…®k…ô.‚Äù  
\v 53 K…ôn suah un, t…ôm…®tun m…ôm…ô, e nian …ôtuat…®p …ôh in…ôh, Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúR…ôham suak…ôku ot…ôpan…ômeg…ôh.‚Äù K…ôn in ne r…ôhan m…®n, k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu.  
\v 54 Inu nian tatol k…ôiu lan it…ôm Iesu t…ômiet Jutia, muwa Kalili k…ôn mol n…ômt…ôtin kit.   
\c 5  
\s1 Iesu t…ômol-w…®r suah kit …ôp…ôh iu…ôhk…®r e n…ôhau Petseta  
\m
\v 1 Uaris…®g e nian …ôh, Iesu t…ôm…ôr muw…®n e taon u Jerusalem, m…ôto-inu katol lafet kit r…ôha net…ôm Isrel …ôh-ik…®n …ôh.   
\p
\v 2 E Jerusalem, noan asol kit …ôp…ôh ik…®n, it…ôm k…ôtaig lan. E n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel kat…ôn n…ôrg…®n m…ôm…ô Petseta. K…ôn nim…ô kit tat…ôtul iu…ôhk…®r o noan …ôh. Nim…ô un, feranta lan, faif. In …ôh iu…ôhk…®r o ket u e fen…®s r…ôha taon u, n…ôrg…®n u, Ket r…ôha Sipsip.  
\v 3-4 K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, e feranta m…®n, net…ôm koat…®m…®s tep…ôt koatap…®l …ôh-ik…®n. Neen n…®gan…ômt…®lat t…ôp…®s, k…ôn neen nelk…®lat t…ôrat, neen m…®n n…®p…ôt…®lat n…ôwtain t…ôm…®m…®s.\f + \fr 5:3-4 \ft E kopi oas m…®n neen r…ôha Niutesteman it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris aup…ôn, k…ôm…ôtu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha ves 3-4 tol nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIlat koatap…®l ik…®n …ôh moat…ôsahgin noan …ôh m…ôm…ô ot…ôloal. 4 Meto-inun, nian neen, nagelo kit r…ôha Uhg…®n tuwa, muw…®n e noan …ôh, k…ôn mol tat…ôloal. K…ôn nian ok…ôm…ô n…ôhau …ôh t…ôloal un, et…ômim it…ôm taup…ôn meiuaiu matuw…®n e n…ôhau, nat …ôpnap…®n tatos n…®m…®s…ôn naka, m…ôto r…ôhan n…®m…®s…ôn ot…ôw…®r.‚Äù\f*  
\v 5 K…ôn suah kit …ôh-ik…®n …ôh t…ôtap…®l. In t…ômat…®m…®s m…®nos r…ôk…®s nup tate-eit.  
\v 6 K…ôn Iesu t…ôplan suah un t…ôtap…®l, k…ôn in m…®n…®tun m…ôm…ô suah u t…ôm…®m…®s nuw…ôh m…ôs…®n, k…ôn t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Tahro? ?Nakolkeike m…ôm…ô onak…ôw…®r?‚Äù   
\p
\v 7 Et…ôm tat…®m…®s un t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol, et…ômim t…®k…ô m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs io meiuaiu muw…®n e noan …ôh nian n…ôhau tat…ôloal. Nian rafin, io etalkut p…®k m…ôm…ô ekeiuaiu muw…®n e noan …ôh, m…ôto net…ômim neen ilat kotapr…ôk…®s-in io moteiuaiu motuw…®n. K…ôn ilat motaup…ôn motek n…ôhau.‚Äù   
\p
\v 8 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!∆ètul! Mos r…ôham n…®m…®tiw…®n maliw…ôk matuw…®n.‚Äù  
\v 9 K…ôn roiu ag…®n suah apon t…ôm…ôw…®r m…®n. K…ôn maiuaiu r…ôhan n…®m…®tiw…®n mos matuw…®n.  
\p Nat u k…ômol e nian r…ôha Sapat,\f + \fr 5:9 \ft Sapat: ∆èplan e tiksonari.\f*  
\v 10 k…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômot…ôhai suah un it…ôm t…®n…ômeg…ôh e r…ôhan n…®m…®s…ôn, mot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian u-roiu r…ôha Sapat; k…ôn t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn e Lou r…ôhatat m…ôm…ô onakos nulan r…ôham n…®m…®tiw…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 5:10 \ft Jer 17:21\f*  
\v 11 K…ôn in t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm m…®n u m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúM…ôto suah u t…ômol-w…®r io, in t…ôm…ôn-ipa m…ôm…ô ekos r…ôhak n…®m…®tiw…®n maliw…ôk matuw…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 12 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Suah pah apon t…ôm…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô on…ôkol nat un?‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 M…ôto suah un t…ôruru n…ôrg…® Iesu, m…ôto-inu net…ômim tep…ôt ik…®n …ôh, k…ôn Iesu t…ôm…®k…ô-p…ôn …ôm …ôh ilug…®n elat.   
\p
\v 14 K…ôn uaris…®g, Iesu t…ôm…ôplan suah un e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! !∆èplan-tu! !Ik n…®n…ôw…®r r…ôk…®s! M…ôto onat…ôto ik m…ôm…ô n…ôsol m…®n…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n. Ok…ôm…ô nakol, n…ôrat…ôn kit ot…®l…ôs m…®n ik, it…ôm t…ôrat t…ôhm…®n m…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 15 K…ôn suah apon t…ômuw…®n m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha Isrel m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah u it…ôm t…ômol-w…®r io, n…ôrg…®n un, Iesu.‚Äù   
\p
\v 16 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, ilat k…®noat…®t…ôp-…®t…ôp Iesu m…ôm…ô okotol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm in, m…ôto-inu ilat kot…ôplan in tatol nat…®mnat m…®n tol n…ôhlan e nian r…ôha Sapat.\f + \fr 5:16 \ft E kopi oas m…®n neen r…ôha Niutesteman it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris aup…ôn, k…ôm…ôtu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn tol nulan, ‚Äúk…ôn ilat k…ômoateg…ôs-in suat…®p o nohamnu…ôn in.‚Äù \f*  
\v 17 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian rafin r…ôhak Tata tatol …ôh w…ôk, k…ôn io m…®n oekatol w…ôk.‚Äù\f + \fr 5:17 \ft Jon 14:10\f*   
\p
\v 18 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, tol n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat t…ôskas…®k t…ôhm…®n m…®n, m…ôm…ô okotohamnu in t…®m…®s. M…ôto-inu roiu …ôh, s…ôn…ôm…ô m…ôm…ô tat…ôtg…ôhl …ôm Lou r…ôha Sapat, m…ôto nat in iahgin p…®k, in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô r…ôhan u Tata …ôtuat…®p Uhg…®n, k…ôn tol nulan, in matol m…ôm…ô in tahmen …ôtuat…®p e Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Jon 10:30,33; 19:7\f*   
\s1 Iesu in t…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô  //  m…ôto-inu in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n  
\p
\v 19 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n un iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat, N…ôt…® Uhg…®n t…ôruru nol…ôn nat kit e r…ôhan at…®p …ôm n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn. T…®tun …ôm nol…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n un it…ôm Tata Uhg…®n tatol, m…ôto-inu nat…®mnat rafin u it…ôm Tata Uhg…®n tatol, N…ôt…®n, in m…®n in tatol.\f + \fr 5:19 \ft Jon 14:10\f*  
\v 20 N…ôt…®n t…®tun nol…ôn n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu Tata Uhg…®n tolkeike p…®k N…ôt…®n, k…ôn in tat…ôg…ôtun k…ôm in nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm in tatol. K…ôn in ot…ôpan…ôg…ôtun m…®n nat…®mnat m…®n k…ôm in it…ôm iahgin m…®n kotapr…ôk…®s-in in m…®n u, m…ôm…ô otol it…ômat narm…®t…ômat tatiw…®g p…®k ron.   
\p
\v 21 ‚ÄúM…ôto-inu Tata Uhg…®n tatol net…ôm k…ômot…®m…®s ilat koat…ômeg…ôh m…®n, k…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, N…ôt…®n t…®tun nos-ip…ôn…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn k…ôm net…ômim it…ôm n…®kin tagien m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat.\f + \fr 5:21 \ft Rom 4:17; Jon 11:25\f*  
\v 22 M…ôto-inu s…ôn…ôm…ô Tata Uhg…®n it…ôm in otakil net…ômim, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn rafin nakil…ôn e nelm…® N…ôt…®n,\f + \fr 5:22 \ft Kitat kot…ôplan ves 21-22 k…ôn m…®tun m…ôm…ô Iesu in otakil kitat rafin, k…ôn in otos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn k…ôm net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm n…®kin tagien m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat. M…ôto Jon 3:17 tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôm…ôsuwam…ôn e n…ôtueint…ôn o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhatat, m…ôto t…ômuwa o nos-ip…ôn…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn k…ôm itat. \f* \f + \fr 5:22 \ft Jon 5:26-27; 9:39; W…ôk 10:42\f*  
\v 23 m…ôm…ô net…ômim ilat rafin okot…®siai-in N…ôt…®n, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inun koat…®siai-in mihin Tata Uhg…®n. Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôs…®siai-in…ôn N…ôt…®n, okol t…ôs…®siai-in…ôn Tata Uhg…®n u it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa N…ôt…®n.\f + \fr 5:23 \ft Luk 10:16; 1 Jon 2:23\f*   
\p
\v 24 ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôto r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn m…ôtahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io iakuwa, in t…®natos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n. In okol t…ôs…ôtul…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…ôk m…ôm…ô oek…ôn-iar…ôp nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhan. In t…®nag…®m r…ôk…®s e n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn m…®nuwa o n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.\f + \fr 5:24 \ft Jon 3:18\f*  
\v 25 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôm…ô o nian kit it…ôm tatuwa, k…ôn t…®nuwa r…ôk…®s, net…ôm m…®n u k…ômot…®m…®s, ilat okot…ôto n…ôwia N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn net…ôm m…®n u ilat kot…ôt…ôl…®g-in, ilat okotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.  
\v 26 Tata Uhg…®n in N…ôuk…ôt…® N…ômeg…ôh…ôn, k…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, in t…ômol m…ô N…ôt…®n in m…®n N…ôuk…ôt…® N…ômeg…ôh…ôn,\f + \fr 5:26 \ft Jen 2:7; Job 10:12; 33:4; Sam 36:9; 42:8; 66:9; Jon 1:1-4\f*  
\v 27 k…ôn in t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn ne nep…ôt…ôn e nelm…® N…ôt…®n m…ôm…ô in otakil nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha net…ômim, m…ôto-inu in N…ôt…® Et…ômim.   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúT…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô narm…®t…ômat otiw…®g p…®k o nat u, m…ôto-inu nian …ôh-ik…®n tatuwa it…ôm net…ôm k…ômot…®m…®s okot…ôto n…ôwia N…ôt…®n,  
\v 29 k…ôn ilat okot…ôtul e r…ôhalat m…®n suw…®t, ilat m…®n u aup…ôn k…ômoatol nol…ôn w…®r m…®n okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôtul m…®n motos m…®n n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, m…ôto it…ôm m…®n aup…ôn ilat k…ômoatol nol…ôn rat m…®n, ilat okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôtul m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn k…ôn mot…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…® Tata Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô N…ôt…®n ot…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôhalat nalp…®n…ôn.\f + \fr 5:29 \ft Net…ômim it…ôm kotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu, koatos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n. Net…ômim it…ôm k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan, ilat okotos nalp…®n…ôn lil…®n (Jon 3:36, 5:24, Mak 16:16, Efes 2:8-10). Nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm net…ômim koatol, okotol …ôp ok…ôm-naka ilat kotahat…ôt…ô pahrien e Iesu o k…ôp…ô (Mat 7:17-20; Kal 5:6, Jem 2:17,26). Uhg…®n tatos-ip…ôn nahat…ôt…ô…ôn k…ôm net…ômim …ôpnap…®n …ôm, k…ôn mat…®g masitu m…®n elat m…ôm…ô okoatol nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n.\f*   
\p
\v 30 ‚ÄúIo ek…ôruru nol…ôn nat kit e r…ôhak at…®p …ôm n…ôsan…ôn…ôn. Io iakatakil nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha net…ômim m…®n, m…ôto iatol …ôtuat…®p …ôm m…ôm…ô r…ôhak Tata tat…ôn mihin ne m…ôm…ô oekol. K…ôn nian iakakil nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim, ek…®tun m…ô ekol t…ôtuat…®p, m…ôto-inun oesalkut…ôn m…ôm…ô ekol …ôm e r…ôhak n…ôsan…ôn…ôn. M…ôto io, ek…ôike malkut m…ôm…ô iakol tahmen e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io ekuwa.‚Äù\f + \fr 5:30 \ft Jon 8:16\f*   
\s1 N…ôtul-ar…ôp…ôn o naru…ôsan…ôn Iesu  
\p
\v 31 Ok…ôm…ô io p…®s…®n …ôm iak…ôghat-in io, k…ôn r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn okol t…ôs…ôtul…ôn.\f + \fr 5:31 \ft Dut 17:6; 19:15\f*  
\v 32 M…ôto suah kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n in tat…ôtul-ar…ôp k…ôn matol n…ôf…®g…ôm…ôn ron io, k…ôn io ek…®tun m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u r…ôhan it…ôm tat…ôn lak in n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 5:32 \ft Jon 8:17-18\f*   
\p
\v 33 ‚ÄúAup…ôn, it…ômat n…ômotahl-ip…ôn r…ôhat…ômat m…®n net…ômim m…ôm…ô okotuw…®n mot…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Jon, k…ôn in t…ômat…ôtul-ar…ôp o n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 5:33 \ft Jon 1:19-28\f*  
\v 34 Iat…ôghat nulan, m…ôto esag…®le…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha et…ômim …ôm kit m…ôm…ô t…®tun nol…ôn n…ôf…®g…ôm…ôn ron io. K…ôp…ô. T…ôsol…ôn nulan.\f + \fr 5:34 \ft 1 Jon 5:9\f* Iat…ôghat-in n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Jon nulan m…ôto-inu ekolkeike m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otosmeg…ôh it…ômat.  
\v 35 Jon u, tahmen e lait kit. Tatu…ôp m…ôhag-…ôhag w…®r, k…ôn n…®kit…ômat t…ômagien ron o nian t…ôku…ôk…®r …ôm.   
\p
\v 36 ‚ÄúM…ôto r…ôhak w…ôk m…®n, ilat m…®n koatol n…ôf…®g…ôm…ôn ron io. K…ôn ilat kot…ôsan…ôn motapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôghat…ôn m…®n un Jon t…ômat…ôn. W…ôk m…®n un, r…ôhak Tata t…ômos-ipa k…ôm io m…ô oekol namnun elat. K…ôn w…ôk m…®n u r…ôhak, ilat koat…ôn-iar…ôp io, k…ôn ilat moatol …ôp io m…ôm…ô r…ôhak Tata in t…ômahl-ipa io.\f + \fr 5:36 \ft Jon 10:25; 14:11\f*  
\v 37 K…ôn Tata Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io, inun it…ôm t…®nat…ôtul-ar…ôp ron io. In tat…ôn-iar…ôp io pap, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôsot…ôto…ôn n…ôwian, k…ôn it…ômat n…ôsot…ôplan…ôn n…®gan…ômt…®n.  
\v 38 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan t…ôsat…®g w…®r…ôn e n…®kit…ômat, m…ôto-inun it…ômat n…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lak, io u, it…ôm in t…ômahl-ipa io iakuwa.   
\p
\v 39 ‚ÄúIt…ômat noatafin p…®k n…ôghat…ôn m…®n e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn motahat…ôt…ô e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn it…ôm namnun t…®k…ô. M…ôto ot…ôplan-tu. N…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, ilat koat…ôghat-in io, moat…ôn-iar…ôp io.  
\v 40 M…ôto it…ômat nakotap…ôs nuwam…ôn ron io m…ôm…ô nakotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn ron io.   
\p
\v 41 Esol…ôn nat ag…®n-…ôh e n…ônwiwi…ôn r…ôha net…ômim. K…ôp…ô.  
\v 42 M…ôto it…ômat u inun, io ek…®tun w…®r it…ômat, k…ôn io ek…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô nolkeike…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n t…®k…ô e n…®kit…ômat.  
\v 43 Io emuwa e n…ôrg…® Tata r…ôhak, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôsotos…ôn io e n…®kit…ômat, n…®kit…ômat t…ôsagien…ôn ron io; m…ôto ok…ôm…ô et…ômim kit tatuwa e n…ôrg…®n at…®p …ôm, k…ôn n…®kit…ômat tos, k…ôn motagien ron.  
\v 44 Nian rafin it…ômat nakotolkeike m…ôm…ô nakotos n…ônwiwi…ôn r…ôhat…ômat m…®n, m…ôto n…ôsotalkut ag…®n-…ôh…ôn m…ôm…ô on…ôkotol nat kit it…ôm Uhg…®n u, in p…®s…®n …ôm in Uhg…®n, ot…ônwiwi it…ômat ron. ?On…ôkotahat…ôt…ô ahro nulan lak e nol…ôn …ôh?   
\p
\v 45 ‚ÄúT…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat ot…ôht m…ôm…ô, io oek…ôn-iar…ôp nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhat…ômat e n…®gan…ômt…® Tata Uhg…®n. K…ôp…ô. M…ôto Moses il…ô, nian rafin it…ômat noatuag-p…ôn ron,\f + \fr 5:45 \ft Jon 9:28; Rom 2:17\f* in ot…ôn-iar…ôp nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhat…ômat.  
\v 46 M…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ômotahat…ôt…ô pahrien e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôha Moses, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôkotahat…ôt…ô m…®n e r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n. M…ôto-inun, n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm in t…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s, ilat koat…ôghat-in io.  
\v 47 M…ôto it…ômat n…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm in t…ôm…ôte, tol n…ôhlan, suat…®p t…®k…ô ag…®n m…ôm…ô on…ôkotahat…ôt…ô lak.   
\c 6  
\s1 Iesu t…ômagw…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt  
\r (Mat 14:13-21; Mak 6:30-44;  //  Luk 9:10-17)  
\m
\v 1 Uaris…®g e nat…®mnat m…®n u, Iesu t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh ent…ôn…®p…ôn e n…ôhau asol n…ôrg…®n un, Lek Kalili. K…ôn n…ôrg…®n kit m…®n un, Lek Taepirias.  
\v 2 K…ôn n…®manin net…ômim k…ômoatuaris…®g-in, m…ôto-inun koat…ôplan n…ômt…ôtin m…®n r…ôhan, it…ôm tatol net…ômim koat…®m…®s koat…ôto t…ôw…®r.  
\v 3 K…ôn Iesu t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s e n…®tot kit, k…ôn mat…ôp…ôl…ôh ik…®n …ôh ilat r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim.  
\v 4 E nian …ôh, lafet kit r…ôha net…ôm Isrel u, k…ôtaun-in m…ôm…ô lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn t…®natuwa iu…ôhk…®r.   
\p
\v 5 K…ôn nian Iesu tas…®p…ôn …ôp…ôh is…ôu, k…ôn m…ôplan n…®manin net…ômim tep…ôt ilat koatuwa, k…ôn in t…ôtap…ôh o Filip m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Okot…ôhrol motos p…®ret tep…ôt tahmen-in net…ôm m…®n u m…ôm…ô ilat okotun?‚Äù  
\v 6 In t…ôm…ôn asg…ôw…®n …ôm m…ôm…ô ot…ôplan nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôha Filip, m…ôto in t…®n…®tun r…ôk…®s nat naka it…ôm in ot…ôpanol.   
\p
\v 7 K…ôn Filip t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! Ok…ôm…ô okos-n…ômt…®n p…®ret m…ôni lan tahmen e tu-hanr…®t tenarius pap,\f + \fr 6:7 \ft Roiu, tu-hanr…®t tenarius tahmen e tu-hanr…®t-taosan vatu.\f* m…ôto okol t…ôsahmen…ôn. Net…ôm m…®n u rafin ilat okotun …ôm noan m…ôs…®n noan m…ôs…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 8 K…ôn et…ômim kit r…ôha Iesu, pian u Saimon Pita, n…ôrg…®n u Antru, in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Iesu m…ôm…ô,  
\v 9 ‚ÄúSuak…ôku kit …ôh-ik…®n …ôh, in tatos p…®ret faif k…ômol e pale, ne n…ôm k…ôiu. M…ôto okol t…ôsahmen-in ag…®n-…ôh…ôn net…ôm m…®n …ôh.‚Äù\f + \fr 6:9 \ft 2 King 4:42-44\f*   
\p
\v 10 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOt…ôn-ip…ôn-tu k…ôm net…ômim kot…ôp…ôl…ôh.‚Äù K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, manuw…®hl tep…ôt, k…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôp…ôl…ôh. K…ôn nampa r…ôha n…ôman …ôm, in nat kit tahmen e faif-taosan.\f + \fr 6:10 \ft N…®p…®tan ne n…®sualk…ôl…ôh ilat m…®n e n…®manin, m…ôto k…ômafin …ôm n…ôman. Nol…ôn r…ôhalat tol n…ôhlan. !Ok…ôm…ô naka, net…ômim ilat rafin tuente-taosan!\f*  
\v 11 K…ôn Iesu t…ômos p…®ret, m…ôn tagkiu k…ôm Uhg…®n ron, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn p…®ret un k…ôm ilat rafin u koat…ôp…ôl…ôh, k…ôn mat…®g mol m…®n nat kiti…ôh …ôm e n…ôm. K…ôn ilat k…ômotun tahmen-in n…ôrp…®lat.   
\p
\v 12 K…ôn nian k…®notagw…ôn r…ôk…®s, n…ôrp…®lat tasis, k…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOtuw…®n motuw…ôr n…®m…®sm…®s…® p…®ret m…®n …ôh koat…®s. T…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô okot…ôr…ôk…®n.‚Äù  
\v 13 K…ôn ilat k…ômotuw…®n motuw…ôr n…®m…®sm…®s…® p…®ret k…ôn motaii-p…ôn e k…ôt…®m asol m…®n ilat tuelef kot…ôrioah w…®r. P…®ret u, in n…®m…®sm…®s…® p…®ret ilat faif k…ômol e pale it…ôm net…ômim k…ômotun kap…ôs.   
\p
\v 14 K…ôn nian net…ômim k…ômot…ôplan n…ômt…ôtin …ôh it…ôm Iesu t…ômol, k…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn. !Ien pahrien u\f + \fr 6:14 \ft Net…ôm Isrel ilat k…ômot…ôsahgin ien kit m…ôm…ô in otuwa tahmen e Moses (Jon 1:21). E nian r…ôha Moses, Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn p…®ret t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôr e neai, n…ôrg…®n u mana. K…ôn ilat k…ômoat…ôplan …ôm Iesu t…ômol nat p…®sp…®s, magw…ôn ilat e p…®ret. R…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôm…ôtul-p…ôn o nagw…ôn…ôn (ves 26) ne n…ômki-r…ôk…®s…ôn ilat e net…ôm Rom (ves 15).\f* r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm aup…ôn k…ômat…ôn m…ôm…ô in otuwa e n…ôtueint…ôn!‚Äù\f + \fr 6:14 \ft Dut 18:15-19\f*  
\v 15 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…®tun m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u kot…ôm…ô okotuwa motos in motuw…®n mot…ôk…ôike k…ôm in m…ôm…ô in otuwa mol kig r…ôhalat. K…ôn in t…ômag…®m m…®n, map…ôs ilat muw…®n …ôp…ôh e n…®tot, m…ôtan in p…®s…®n …ôm.\f + \fr 6:15 \ft Mat 4:8-10; Jon 18:36-37\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ômaliw…ôk e  //  n…ôtuei n…ôhau  
\r (Mat 14:22-27; Mak 6:45-52)  
\p
\v 16 Nian m…®tgar t…ômeiuaiu, net…ômim r…ôha Iesu m…®n k…ômoteiuaiu motuw…®n e lek …ôh.\fig |alt="Boat in storm" src="LB00213B.TIF" size="col" loc="Jhn 6:16-21" ref="Jon 6:16" \fig*  
\v 17 K…ôn t…®napin…ôp, m…ôto Iesu t…®k…ô, t…ôsuwam…ôn …ôh. K…ôn …ômun, ilat k…ômotuw…®n mot…ôr e pot kit, k…ôn m…®notasu…ô lan motaulego m…®n e lek un, m…ôm…ô ilat okotuw…®n Kapaneam.  
\v 18 K…ôn n…®m…ôtag asol kit t…ôm…ôtul m…®nol n…ôhau t…®n…ôrat-n…ôrat.  
\v 19 K…ôn nian ilat k…ômotasu…ô motuw…®n, tahmen e faif o sikis kilomita, k…ôn ilat kot…ôplan Iesu taliw…ôk e n…ôtuei n…ôhau\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Job 9:8\f* matuwa iu…ôhk…®r o r…ôhalat pot. K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôg…®n p…®k,\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Mat 14:26; Mak 6:49; Luk 24:37\f*  
\v 20 m…ôto in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èsot…ôg…®n p…®k…ôn, io u inu.\f + \fr 6:20 \ft ‚ÄúIo u inu‚Äù - ∆èplan-tu futnot e Jon 4:26.\f*‚Äù  
\v 21 !K…ôn n…®kilat t…ômagien o n…®l…ôs…ôn in e pot, moatol …ômun, roiu ag…®n, m…ôto pot t…®nuw…®n e n…ôwtain n…ôhau ent…ôn…®p…ôn-p…ôn ik…®n-un k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô okotuw…®n ik…®n!   
\s1 Net…ômim k…ômoateg…ôs-in Iesu  
\p
\v 22 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin, net…ômim m…®n it…ôm kotat…®g …ôh ent…ôn…®p…ôn-pa ik…®n e lek asol u, ilat k…ômot…ôplan m…ôm…ô aup…ôn, pot kiti…ôh …ôm tat…ôtul uk…®n-u. K…ôn ilat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôsuw…®n…ôn e pot u ilat r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim, m…ôto-inun nian k…ômotiet, ilat p…®s…®n …ôm moatuw…®n.  
\v 23 K…ôn pot m…®n neen, k…ômot…®s…®-p…ôn e taon u Taepirias, ilat k…ômotuwa. Ilat k…ômotuwar iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o ik…®n-u it…ôm Ier…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôtul ik…®n m…ôfak mat…ôn tagkiu o p…®ret, k…ôn net…ômim k…ômotun.  
\v 24 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, nian ilat k…ômot…ôplan m…ôm…ô Iesu t…®n…®k…ô u ik…®n-u, k…ôn r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim kot…®k…ô, ilat m…®n k…ômotasu…ô m…®n e pot kit, motuw…®n e Kapaneam, moateg…ôs-in.   
\s1 Iesu in p…®ret r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn  
\p
\v 25 Nian net…ôm m…®n u k…ômot…ôplan Iesu …ôp…ôh ent…ôn…®p…ôn-p…ôn …ôp…ôh e lek u, kot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôg…ôtun, ik n…ômuwa ik…®n-u n…ôghan?‚Äù   
\p
\v 26 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, it…ômat noateg…ôs-in io, s…ôn…ôm…ô n…ômot…ôplan n…ômt…ôtin m…®n u it…ôm emol, m…ôto it…ômat n…ômotun …ôm p…®ret, n…ôrp…®t…ômat tasis.  
\v 27 M…ôto t…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat nahgit…ômat ot…®k…ô o nos…ôn p…®ret it…ôm ot…ôpan…ômn…ôm…®t m…®k…ô.\f + \fr 6:27 \ft Aes 55:2\f* It…ômat, nahgit…ômat ot…ôk…ôike m…®k…ô o nos…ôn p…®ret it…ôm t…ôtat…®g lil…®n u, r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn it…ôm namnun t…®k…ô.\f + \fr 6:27 \ft Jon 6:35, 48\f* P…®ret u, inu, N…ôt…® Et…ômim ot…ôpanos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat; m…ôto-inu Tata Uhg…®n, in t…ôm…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô n…®kin tagien o N…ôt…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 6:27 \ft Aes 55:2\f*   
\p
\v 28 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Nol…ôn naka m…®n un it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike m…ôm…ô it…®mat oekotol?‚Äù   
\p
\v 29 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motahat…ôt…ô lak, m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa io.\f + \fr 6:29 \ft Jon 6:35; 1 Tes 1:3; 1 Jon 3:23\f* Nat u inu Uhg…®n in tolkeike.‚Äù   
\p
\v 30 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh m…®n ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôto ik on…ôkol n…ômt…ôtin naka, m…ôm…ô it…®mat ekot…ôplan k…ôn ekotahat…ôt…ô lam? ?Ik on…ôkol nat naka?  
\v 31 Nian r…ôhatat pipi m…®n u aup…ôn, ilat k…ômotan ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n, ilat k…ômotun ‚Äòmana.‚Äô\f + \fr 6:31 \ft Nam 11:7-9\f* N…ôghat…ôn kit e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIn tatos-ip…ôn p…®ret it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn e Nego e Neai m…ôm…ô ilat okotun.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \fr 6:31 \ft Eks 16:4,15; Neham 9:15; Sam 78:24; Sam 105:40\f*   
\p
\v 32 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, s…ôn…ôm…ô Moses t…ômos-ip…ôn p…®ret u it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn e Nego e Neai m…ôm…ô nakotun. R…ôhak Tata il…ô in tatos-ip…®n…ô. K…ôn inun tatos-ip…ôn p…®ret pahrien it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn e Nego e Neai, m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotun.  
\v 33 M…ôto-inu p…®ret r…ôha Uhg…®n, inu in it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn e Nego e Neai, mateiuaiu-pa e n…ôtueint…ôn.\f + \fr 6:33 \ft Jon 3:13,31\f* K…ôn p…®ret u tatos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn k…ôm net…ômim e n…ôtueint…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 6:33 \ft Dut 8:3; Mat 4:4; Luk 4:4\f*   
\p
\v 34 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol, awi os-ipa-tu p…®ret u k…ôm it…®mat nian rafin.‚Äù\f + \fr 6:34 \ft Mat 6:11; Jon 4:15\f*   
\p
\v 35 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u, io\f + \fr 6:35 \ft Jon 8:12; 10:7,11; 11:25; 14:6; 15:1\f* P…®ret it…ôm tatos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. Et…ômim otuwa ron io, in n…ôum…®s ot…ôsus m…®n…ôn. K…ôn et…ômim it…ôm otahat…ôt…ô lak, in ot…ôsoaoa m…®n…ôn.\f + \fr 6:35 \ft Jon 4:14; 7:37-39\f*  
\v 36 M…ôto io em…ôn-ip…®n…ô r…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôm…ô nat …ôpnap…®n n…ôkot…ôplan io, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn …ôh lak.  
\v 37 Net…ômim it…ôm r…ôhak Tata tatos-ipa ilat k…ôm io, ilat okotuwa ron io. K…ôn et…ômim it…ôm otuwa ron io, okol iak…ôsahl-iar…ôp-…ôn.\f + \fr 6:37 \ft Jon 17:2\f*  
\v 38 M…ôto-inu io em…ôs…®s…®-p…ôn…ôn e Nego e Neai meiuaiu-pa e n…ôtueint…ôn m…ôm…ô iakol nat…®mnat m…®n u io …ôm ekolkeike. M…ôto emuwa m…ôm…ô ekol nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm r…ôhak Tata t…ômahl-ipa io ekuwa ron.  
\v 39 K…ôn in tolkeike m…ôm…ô io es…ômkar…ôp…ôn-in…ôn net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm in t…ôm…ômki-pa ilat k…ôm io. In tolkeike m…ôm…ô e namnun nian, io oekol net…ôm m…®n u ilat okot…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn.\f + \fr 6:39 \ft Jon 17:2,12; 18:9\f*  
\v 40 M…ôto-inu r…ôhak Tata in tolkeike m…ôm…ô net…ômim rafin it…ôm kotuag-p…ôn o Net…®n, k…ôn motahat…ôt…ô lan, ilat okotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn itul…®n. K…ôn e namnun nian, io oekol net…ôm m…®n u ilat okot…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 41 O nat u, net…ômim n…®kilat t…®n…ôtuoun m…ôtag…ôt, m…ôto-inu in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u, P…®ret it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn e Nego e Neai, meiuaiu-pa e n…ôtueint…ôn.‚Äù  
\v 42 Ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? Suah u in Iesu, n…ôt…® Josep, kitat kot…®tun …ôm r…ôhan tata ne mama. ?T…ôhrol in tat…ôn nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIo em…®s…®-p…ôn e Nego e Neai, matuwa e n…ôtueint…ôn‚Äô?‚Äù   
\p
\v 43 Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kit…ômat t…ôsag…ôt-ag…ôt…ôn nulan.  
\v 44 Ok…ôm…ô Tata Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io ekuwa, in t…ôsiuw-pam…ôn et…ômim kit tuwa ron io, k…ôn okol et…ômim un t…ôsuwa at…®p…ôn ron io m…ôm…ô io oekol in ot…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn e namnun nian.\f + \fr 6:44 \ft Hos 11:4; Jon 6:65; 12:32\f*  
\v 45 N…ôghat…ôn it…ôm ien kit t…ôm…ôte aup…ôn e Naoa r…ôha Uhg…®n, tat…ôn nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòUhg…®n in ot…ôg…ôtun net…ômim rafin.‚Äô Et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôg…ôtun…ôn r…ôha Tata Uhg…®n, in tatuwa ron io.\f + \fr 6:45 \ft Aes 54:13; Jer 31:34\f*  
\v 46 Et…ômim kiti…ôh ne t…®k…ô, it…ôm t…ôm…ôplan Tata Uhg…®n. In p…®s…®n …ôm un it…ôm t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn lan, t…ôm…ôplan in.\f + \fr 6:46 \ft Jon 1:18; 5:37; 7:29\f*  
\v 47 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, et…ômim it…ôm t…ôtahat…ôt…ô lak, in t…®nos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.  
\v 48 Io un, P…®ret r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.\f + \fr 6:48 \ft P…®ret …ôpnap…®n …ôm tasitu e n…®p…ôt…®tat m…ôm…ô kitat okot…ômeg…ôh k…ôn motat…®g, m…ôto Iesu, in P…®ret r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, k…ôn in n…ôuk…ôt…® n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n, it…ôm tat…ôtuoun u-roiu.\f*  
\v 49 Nat …ôpnap…®n t…®p…®t…ômat m…®n aup…ôn, ilat k…ômotun p…®ret u ‚Äòmana‚Äô …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n, m…ôto ilat k…®not…®m…®s r…ôk…®s.  
