\c 7  
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôghat ilat pian m…®n  
\m
\v 1 Uaris…®g e nat…®mnat m…®n u, Iesu t…ôsolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô otuw…®n latu…ônu m…®n e Jutia m…ôm…ô otol r…ôhan w…ôk …ôh-ik…®n …ôh, m…ôto-inun, net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Jutia k…ômoat…ôte noa anion kit ron. K…ôn t…®t…ôl…®g muw…®n latu…ônu m…®n e n…®t…ôn Kalili.  
\v 2 M…ôto nian t…®nu…ôk…®r e nian r…ôha nol…ôn lafet kit r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, n…ôrg…®n un, lafet r…ôha Nol…ôn Makeen.\f + \fr 7:2 \ft lafet r…ôha Nol…ôn Makeen: ∆èplan e tiksonari.\f*  
\v 3 K…ôn pia Iesu m…®n k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúT…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nakiet muw…®n …ôp…ôh Jutia, m…ô p…ôs net…ômim m…®n r…ôham …ôh-ik…®n …ôh, ilat kot…ôplan nat p…®sp…®s m…®n r…ôham it…ôm natol.  
