\v 11 K…ôn e lafet …ôh, net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Jerusalem, koateg…ôs-in in moat…ôtap…ôh-in …ôpnap…®n …ôm o net…ômim m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Suah …ôp…ôh in hi…ô?‚Äù   
