\v 23 M…ôto nian rafin, it…ômat noat…ôhg-ip…ôn n…®sualk…ôl…ôh e nian r…ôha Sapat moatol m…ôm…ô onasot…ôtg…ôhl…ôn Lou r…ôha Moses.\f + \fr 7:23 \ft Net…ôm Isrel, n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat tol n…ôhlan. Ok…ôm…ô lou k…ôiu, k…ôn kioal p…®s…®n elau m…®n, ok…ôm…ô natol kit mat…ôtg…ôhl kit, k…ôn onak…ôk…ôike m…®tun m…ôm…ô lou naka un in iahgin. Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô k…ôseg…ôhan-in…ôn nol…ôn w…ôk e nian r…ôha Sapat, m…ôto net…ôm Isrel ilat k…®not…ôn r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô n…ôhg-ip…ôn…ôn it…ôm, in iahgin e lou r…ôha Sapat. Tol n…ôhlan, ok…ôm…ô ok…ôhg-ip…ôn suak…ôku kit e nian r…ôha Sapat, k…ôn ok…ôk…ôike k…ôhg-ip…ôn e nian …ôh, k…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô nol…ôn rat. Iesu tat…ôn m…ôm…ô onas…ôkitun…ôn it…ôm, in m…®n un in n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn lou kit it…ôm in iahgin m…®n e lou r…ôha Sapat.\f* ?K…ôn t…ôhrol nem…ôha tatol it…ômat m…ôto-inu io emol-w…®r ag…®n n…®p…ôt…® et…ômim e nian r…ôha Sapat?\f + \fr 7:23 \ft Jon 5:2-9; Mak 3:5; Luk 13:12-14; Luk 14:4-6\f*  
\v 24 Otap…ôs nakil…ôn nol…ôn r…ôhak u it…ôm n…ômot…ôplan …ôm e n…®gan…ômt…®t…ômat, m…ôto it…ômat on…ôkot…ôk…ôike motakil r…ôhak nol…ôn e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:24 \ft Aes 11:1-3; Jon 8:15\f*   
\s1 Net…ômim k…ômoat…ôghat-in  //  Kristo  
\p
\v 25 K…ôn e nian …ôh, net…ôm Jerusalem neen kot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol …ôh? ?Suah u inu, net…ôm-iasol kot…ôm…ô okotohamnu?\f + \fr 7:25 \ft Jon 7:1\f*  
