\v 27 M…ôto kitat kot…®tun ik…®n suah u t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n. M…ôto nian Kristo in otuwa, okol suah kit t…ôs…®tun…ôn ik…®n in tat…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:27 \ft Net…ômim kot…®tun m…ôm…ô Iesu t…®nep…ôt …ôp…ôh e Nasaret, k…ôn in r…ôhan u mama ne tata u Josep ne Meri (Mat 2:23; Jon 1:45; 6:42; 18:5). Net…ôm Isrel neen ilat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô Kristo in ot…®s…®-p…ôn …ôp…ôh taon Petlehem (Maeka 5:2; Mat 2:4-6), m…ôto neen, n…®kilat t…ôht m…ôm…ô in otuwa …ôm, net…ômim ilat okot…ôruru ik…®n in t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n.\f*   
\p
\v 28 K…ôn e nian …ôh, Iesu in tat…ôg…ôtun net…ômim e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn in t…ômag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh mat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…®tun io, k…ôn mot…®tun m…®n ik…®n em…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru. Io, em…ôsuwam…ôn e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn …ôm r…ôhak. Uhg…®n t…ômahl-ipa io ekuwa. K…ôn Uhg…®n, in n…®pahrien…ôn. It…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru in,  
\v 29 m…ôto io ek…®tun,\f + \fr 7:29 \ft Mat 11:27\f* m…ôto-inu io em…®s…®-p…ôn lan. K…ôn in t…ômahl-ipa io ekuwa.‚Äù   
\p
\v 30 O nat u, ilat k…ômotolkeike m…ôm…ô mopael m…®n okotask…ôl…®m Iesu, m…ôto kit t…ôm…ôsea-p…ôn…ôn mek, m…ôto-inun t…ôsol…ôn …ôh nian r…ôhan.\f + \fr 7:30 \ft Mat 26:18\f*  
\v 31 M…ôto e n…®manin net…ômim ik…®n …ôh, ilat tep…ôt k…ômotahat…ôt…ô lan, k…ôn mot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô Kristo tuwa, k…ôn in okol t…ôsol…ôn n…ômt…ôtin tep…ôt tapr…ôk…®s-in it…ôm suah u Iesu tatol.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:31 \ft Jon 2:23; 4:48\f*   
\s1 Mopael m…®n r…ôha Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n k…ômotuwa m…ôm…ô okotask…ôl…®m Iesu  
\p
\v 32 K…ôn nian Farisi m…®n k…ômot…ôto n…®manin net…ômim kotasiw…®n-asiw…®n e Iesu nulan, ilat ne pris asol m…®n k…ômotahl-ip…ôn mopael m…®n it…ôm kot…ôtul o Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô okotask…ôl…®m Iesu.\f + \fr 7:32 \ft Jon 7:45-48\f*  
\v 33 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ek…ôtat…®g nian t…ôku…ôk…®r …ôm kitat min it…ômat, k…ôn uaris…®g, ek…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n o et…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io.  
\v 34 E nian u, it…ômat on…ôpanoteg…ôs-in io, m…ôto okol n…ôsotehm…ôn io; m…ôto-inu ik…®n …ôh, it…ôm oekuw…®n ik…®n, okol it…ômat n…ôsotuwam…ôn ik…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 35 K…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel k…®not…ôtap…ôh-…ôtap…ôh olat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?In otuw…®n hi…ô …ôh m…ôm…ô kitat ok…ôsot…ôplan…ôn in? ?Otuw…®n o noanol m…®n neen r…ôha net…ôm Isrel it…ôm kotat…®g e n…ôpt…ôn p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n ilat net…ôm Kris, m…ôm…ô ot…ôg…ôtun net…ôm Kris?  
\v 36 In tat…ôn m…ôm…ô e nian …ôh, kitat okoteg…ôs-in in, m…ôto k…ôsotehm…ôn in, m…ôto-inun ik…®n …ôh in tatuw…®n ik…®n, okol kitat k…ôsotuw…®n…ôn ik…®n. ?N…ôghat…ôn u, n…®p…ôt…®n tat…ôn naka?‚Äù   
\s1 N…ôhau it…ôm tatos-ipa n…ômeg…ôh…ôn pahrien  
\p
\v 37 Namnun nian r…ôha lafet …ôh, in iahgin tapr…ôk…®s-in nian m…®n neen r…ôha lafet. K…ôn e nian …ôh, Iesu t…ôm…ôtul …ôp…ôh e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim mag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Et…ômim it…ôm tatoaoa, p…ôs in otuwa ron io, m…ônim!\f + \fr 7:37 \ft ‚ÄúNoaoa…ôn‚Äù in nimaa n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm tat…ôpsen-p…ôn m…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôk…ôike motos Uhg…®n tahmen e et…ômim it…ôm tatoaoa t…ôike m…ôn…®m n…ôhau. ‚Äú!Otuwa ron io, m…ôn…®m!‚Äù in nimaa n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúAhat…ôt…ô lak.‚Äù\f* \f + \fr 7:37 \ft Aes 55:1; Jon 4:13-14; 6:35; Nol ∆èp…ôn 22:17\f*  
\v 38 Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôtahat…ôt…ô lak, in tahmen e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n u tat…ôn nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòN…ôhau it…ôm tatos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn pahrien, in ot…®s…®-p…ôn e n…®kin, tahmen e n…ômt…® n…ôhau it…ôm t…®tapu…ôl-apu…ôl mat…ôr m…ôtaiu e n…®kin.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \fr 7:38 \ft Jer 2:13; Aes 44:3; 55:1; 58:11; Sek 14:8-9; Jon 4:10-14; 6:35; Nol ∆èp…ôn 7:17\f*  
\v 39 Iesu t…ôm…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, mat…ôghat-in Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n u uaris…®g in ot…ôpanos-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm kotahat…ôt…ô lan.\f + \fr 7:39 \ft Jon 1:33; W…ôk 2:17,33\f* M…ôto e nian …ôh, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, t…ôsuwam…ôn …ôh e net…ômim, m…ôto-inu k…ôs…®l…ôs-ip…ôr…ôn …ôh Iesu.\f + \fr 7:39 \ft E naoa r…ôha Jon, n…®p…ôt…®n r…ôha n…®l…ôs-ip…ôr…ôn r…ôha Iesu, in nat k…ôiu. Kit u m…ôm…ô, k…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr Iesu e n…®g k…ôluau. K…ôn nat kit m…®n, kat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr Iesu m…ôto-inu t…ôm…®m…®s, m…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn, muw…®n mat…®g ilau Tata Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh e nego e neai. K…ôn ik…®n …ôh t…ômos nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag …ôtuat…®p r…ôhan.\f* \f + \fr 7:39 \ft Jon 12:23; 13:31,32\f*   
\s1 Net…ômim k…ômotoor ilat m…®n o Iesu  
\p
\v 40 Nian net…ômim …ôh-ik…®n k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn u, k…ôn neen kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah u, in ien r…ôha Uhg…®n u, aup…ôn k…ômat…ôghat-in.‚Äù   
\p
\v 41 M…ôto neen m…®n ilat kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah u, in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa.‚Äù  
\p M…ôto in p…®s…®n m…®n neen kot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa t…®tun n…®s…®-p…ôn…ôn e net…ôm Kalili?\f + \fr 7:41 \ft Jon 1:46\f*  
\v 42 Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa ot…ôk…ôike mas…®p…ôn e noanol r…ôha Tef…®t, e taon u Petlehem, im…ô Tef…®t aup…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:42 \ft 2 Saml 7:16; Sam 89:3-4; Maeka 5:2; Jer 23:5; Mat 2:1,22-23; Luk 2:4-7\f*  
\v 43 Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn n…®manin net…ômim m…®n u, k…ômotoor ilat m…®n o Iesu.  
\v 44 K…ôn neen kot…ôm…ô okotask…ôl…®m in, m…ôto et…ômim kit t…ôm…ôsea-p…ôn…ôn mek.   
