\v 47 K…ôn Farisi m…®n k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Tahro? ?In t…®neiu…ô-in m…®n it…ômat?  
\v 48 ?N…ômot…ôplan r…ôk…®s r…ôhatat kit et…ôm-iasol o Farisi kit t…ômatahat…ôt…ô lan?  
\v 49 M…ôto net…ôm …ôpnap…®n m…®n, ilat kot…ôruru ag…®n Lou r…ôha Moses, tol n…ôhlan, Uhg…®n ot…ôr…ôk…®n ilat.‚Äù   
\p
\v 50 K…ôn Nikotimas u in Farisi kit, in …ôh-ik…®n ilat min. Suah u inu aup…ôn t…ômuw…®n mat…ôghat k…ôm Iesu.\f + \fr 7:50 \ft Jon 3:1\f* K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô,  
\v 51 ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? ?T…ôtuat…®p e Lou r…ôhatat m…ôm…ô kitat okot…ôn-iar…ôp nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha et…ômim it…ôm kitat k…ôsotaup…ôn…ôn mot…®tun w…®r, k…ônu, m…ôsotehm …ôtuat…®p…ôn nat naka it…ôm in tatol?‚Äù   
\p
\v 52 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? ?Ik m…®n un ik et…ôm Kalili? Uw…®n-tu mafin m…®n Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n. Ik on…ôk…ôplan m…ôm…ô ien kit okol t…ôs…®s…®-p…ôn…ôn Kalili.‚Äù  
\b  
\m \bd [E kopi oas m…®n neen r…ôha Niutesteman it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris aup…ôn, n…ôghat…ôn u Jon 7:53‚Äî8:11 t…®k…ô.]\bd*   
\p
\v 53 K…ôn net…ômim k…®not…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n motuw…®n latu…ônu m…®n.   
\c 8  
\m
\v 1 M…ôto Iesu t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh e n…®tot u, n…ôrg…®n un, N…®tot R…ôha N…®g U Olif.   
\s1 P…ôtan it…ôm t…ômap…®l ilau i…ôrman p…®s…®n u s…ôn…ôm…ô r…ôhan i…ôrman  
\p
\v 2 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin, laulaug…®n ag…®n-…ôh, k…ôn Iesu t…ôm…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotuwa, motu…ôf…®m…®n ilat m…®n ron, k…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôp…ôl…ôh m…®n…ôtuoun mat…ôg…ôtun ilat.  
\v 3 K…ôn n…ôg…ôtun m…®n r…ôha Lou ne Farisi m…®n k…ômot…®l…ôs p…ôtan kit motuwa ron. K…ôn motol in t…ôtul aup…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…®lat. P…ôtan un, net…ômim k…ômot…ôplan m…ôm…ô in t…ôtap…®l ilau i…ôrman kit s…ôn…ôm…ô r…ôhan …ôtuat…®p i…ôrman.  
\v 4 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Iesu m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôg…ôtun, p…ôtan u net…ômim k…ômot…ôht…®m…®s in m…ôm…ô in t…ôtap…®l ilau i…ôrman kit u, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô r…ôhan i…ôrman …ôtuat…®p.  
\v 5 E Lou r…ôhatat, Moses t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn kit tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, p…ôtan tol nulan, kitat kot…ôk…ôike motaht e k…ôpiel ap…®n motaht…®mnu.\f + \fr 8:5 \ft E Lou r…ôha Moses p…ôtan ne i…ôrman ilau k…ôr…ôn ok…ôk…ôike kaht…®mnu ilau (Lev 20:10;  //  Dut 22:22-24).\f* ?M…ôto ik, r…ôham n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôhrol?‚Äù  
\v 6 Ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh n…ôhlan, m…ôm…ô okotol noa eko-eko, p…ôs ilat mot…ôplan-p…ôn nol…ôn rat neen lan, k…ôn ilat kot…®tun nakil…ôn nol…ôn r…ôhan ron. M…ôto Iesu t…ôpnap…®n …ôm, moeg-oeg mat…ôte nat e n…®s…®p e noanelm…®n.   
\p
\v 7 Ilat k…ômoat…ôtap…ôh-in n…ôghat…ôn u k…ôm in, moatuw…®n moatuw…®n, k…ôn in t…ôtul, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô it…ômat kit u ik…®n-u, in t…ôsol…ôn nol…ôn rat nian kit ne, p…ôs in otaup…ôn maht p…ôtan u.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:7 \ft Dut 17:7; Rom 2:1,22\f*  
\v 8 K…ôn in t…ômoeg-oeg m…®n, mat…ôte nat e n…®s…®p e noanelm…®n.  
\v 9 K…ôn nian ilat k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan, k…®notan kiti…ôh kiti…ôh, moatag…®m. Nagu…®hl-agu…®hl m…®n kotaup…ôn moatiet kiti…ôh kiti…ôh, motap…ôs …ôm Iesu ne p…ôtan un.   
\p
\v 10 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôg-…ôtuat…®p m…®n m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm p…ôtan un m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?P…ôtan, net…ôm m…®n u k…ômotahruw…®n? ?Kit t…ôsuwam…ôn m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôham nalp…®n…ôn?‚Äù   
\p
