\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo m…®n, okol es…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn r…ôham nalp…®n…ôn. M…ôto atuw…®n, mol namnun e nol…ôn rat m…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:11 \ft Jon 3:17; 5:14\f*   
\s1 Iesu in n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn r…ôha net…ômim e n…ôtueint…ôn  
\p
\v 12 K…ôn Iesu t…ômat…ôghat m…®n k…ôm ilat, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u, io N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn r…ôha net…ômim u e n…ôtueint…ôn.\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Esik 1:26-28; Jon 1:4-5; Hip 1:3\f* Et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôt…ôu-pa io, okol in t…ôsaliw…ôk…ôn e napin…ôp…ôn nian kit ne, m…ôto in otos n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhan.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Sam 27:1; 44:3; 119:105; Prov 6:23; Aes 49:6; 60:19-20; Mat 5:14; Nol ∆èp…ôn 21:23-24\f*   
\p
\v 13 K…ôn Farisi m…®n k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in mot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ik n…ôkat…ôn-iar…ôp ik nulan, m…ôto suah kit t…ôsol…ôn r…ôham n…ôf…®g…ôm…ôn, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, r…ôham n…ôghat…ôn okol t…ôs…ôtul…ôn!‚Äù\f + \fr 8:13 \ft Jon 5:31\f*   
\p
\v 14 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èw…ôh, n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô io at…®p …ôm iat…ôn-iar…ôp io. M…ôto r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn in tat…ôtul …ôh, m…ôto-inun, io ek…®tun ik…®n iat…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n, k…ôn m…®tun m…®n ik…®n iatuw…®n m…®n ik…®n,\f + \fr 8:14 \ft Jon 13:3; 16:28\f* m…ôto it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru ik…®n iatuw…®n ik…®n, k…ôn mot…ôruru ik…®n iat…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n.  
\v 15 It…ômat u, nakotakil nol…ôn r…ôha et…ômim e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha et…ômim …ôm. M…ôto io esakil…ôn nol…ôn r…ôha et…ômim n…ôhlan.  
\v 16 M…ôto ok…ôm…ô io, iakakil nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim, oekol e nol…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p, m…ôto-inu s…ôn…ôm…ô ekakil e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn …ôm r…ôhak, m…ôto it…®mlau Tata Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io, r…ôhat…®mlau nakil…ôn in kiti…ôh …ôm.  
\v 17 E Lou r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôm…ôte m…ôm…ô, ok…ôm…ô et…ômim k…ôiu, k…ôtioal n…ôf…®g…ôm…ôn o n…ôghat…ôn kit, k…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, in otat…ôtul.\f + \fr 8:17 \ft Dut 19:15\f*  
\v 18 K…ôn roiu …ôh, io iat…ôn-iar…ôp io, m…ôto r…ôhak Tata it…ôm in t…ômahl-ipa io iakuwa, in m…®n tatol n…ôf…®g…ôm…ôn ron io.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:18 \ft Mak 1:10-11; Jon 1:33-34\f*   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, ilat k…®not…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôto r…ôham Tata in hi…ô?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn in t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru io, k…ôn it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru m…®n r…ôhak Tata. Ok…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkot…®tun io un, k…ôn n…ôkot…®tun m…®n r…ôhak Tata.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:19 \ft 1 Jon 2:23\f*   
\p
\v 20 Iesu t…ôm…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, nian in t…ôm…ôg…ôtun net…ômim …ôp…ôh e ik…®n kit it…ôm kat…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn m…ôni ik…®n e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n. M…ôto suah kit t…ôm…ôsuw…®n…ôn mask…ôl…®m in, m…ôto-inun t…ôsol…ôn …ôh nian r…ôhan.   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn il…®s  
\p
\v 21 K…ôn Iesu t…ômat…ôn-ip…ôn m…®n k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ekag…®m t…ônin it…ômat, k…ôn it…ômat onakoateg…ôs-in io. M…ôto it…ômat on…ôkot…®m…®s, k…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat u r…ôhat…ômat\f + \fr 8:21 \ft Nian Iesu tat…ôn ‚Äút…ôfag…ô rat u,‚Äù ok…ôm-naka in tat…ôghat-in t…ôfag…ô rat it…ôm k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan (Jon 9:41).\f* otat…®g …ôh et…ômat. Ik…®n …ôh iakatuw…®n ik…®n, okol it…ômat n…ôsotuwam…ôn ik…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn net…ôm Isrel, ilat kot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…ôghat…ôn …ôh Iesu tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ik…®n …ôh in tatuw…®n ik…®n, okol kitat k…ôsotuw…®n…ôn ik…®n, n…®p…ôt…®n tat…ôn naka? ?Ok…ôm-naka in otohamnu at…®p in, o?‚Äù   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúImat…ômat u ik…®n-u, m…ôto io, io imak …ôh il…®s ik…®n …ôh, k…ôn em…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n, meiuaiu-pa. It…ômat net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u. M…ôto io, s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ôm r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u.\f + \fr 8:23 \ft Jon 3:31\f*  
