\p
\v 42 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô Uhg…®n pahrien in Tata r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôkotolkeike io, m…ôto-inu io em…®s…®-p…ôn lan, muwa ik…®n-u.\f + \fr 8:42 \ft 1 Jon 5:1\f* M…ôto in s…ôn…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat Tata. Io esuwam…ôn ik…®n-u e r…ôhak at…®p …ôm n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn, emuwa m…ôto-inu in t…ômahl-ipa io.  
