\v 53 ?Ik nakapr…ôk…®s-in Epraham u t…®p…®t…®mat t…®n…ôm…®m…®s r…ôk…®s? ?K…ôn ne ien m…®n u k…ômot…®m…®s? ?Ik nak…ôm…ô ik et…ômim naka?‚Äù\f + \fr 8:53 \ft Jon 4:12\f*   
