\p
\v 59 K…ôn …ômun, ilat k…ômot…ôm…®k k…ôpiel ap…®n, mot…ôm…ô okotaht Iesu lan;\f + \fr 8:59 \ft Lev 24:16\f* m…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ôhluaig, k…ôn miet e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, m…®natuw…®n.   
\c 9  
\s1 Iesu t…ômol-w…®r n…®gan…ômt…® suah kit  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn nian kit, Iesu t…ômaliw…ôk m…ôtan, k…ôn m…ôplan suah kit. Nian t…ômaiir, m…ôto n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôp…®s.  
\v 2 K…ôn net…ômim m…®n r…ôha Iesu k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôg…ôtun, suah u t…ômaiir m…ôto n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôp…®s. ?O naka? ?O nol…ôn rat r…ôhan, o nol…ôn rat r…ôha tata ne mama r…ôhan?‚Äù\f + \fr 9:2 \ft Luk 13:2-3\f*   
\p
\v 3 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®gan…ômt…® suah u t…ôm…ôrat, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô e nol…ôn rat r…ôhan, o e nol…ôn rat r…ôha tata ne mama r…ôhan. M…ôto, n…®gan…ômt…® suah u t…ôm…ôp…®s n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôg…ôtun r…ôhan w…ôk e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhan.\f + \fr 9:3 \ft Jon 11:4\f*  
\v 4 Nian tatian …ôh,\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Nian Iesu tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian tatian …ôh,‚Äù nag…ôhat…ôn u tat…ôpsen-p…ôn r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, m…ôto-inu in N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn (ves 5). M…ôto lap…®n tat…ôpsen-p…ôn r…ôhan n…®m…®s…ôn.\f* kitat kot…ôk…ôike kol w…ôk r…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io ekuwa. Nian lap…®n ot…ôpanuwa, k…ôn et…ômim in t…ôruru nol…ôn w…ôk.\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Jon 12:35-36\f*  
\v 5 Nian io etat…®g …ôh e n…ôtueint…ôn u, io N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn r…ôha net…ômim e n…ôtueint…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:5 \ft Jon 1:4\f*   
