\v 12 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôto suah un t…ôtat…®g hi…ô?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn in t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ek…ôruru.‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 K…ôn net…ômim k…ômot…®l…ôs suah u it…ôm n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôm…ôp…®s aup…ôn, motuw…®n k…ôm Farisi m…®n.  
\v 14 Nian u, it…ôm Iesu t…ômol-p…ôn n…ôm…®t e n…®gan…ômt…® suah kit lan t…ôw…®r, in nian r…ôha Sapat.  
\v 15 K…ôn Farisi m…®n k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…ômahrol n…®gan…ômt…®m t…ôw…®r?‚Äù K…ôn suah un t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIesu t…ômol-p…ôn n…ôm…®t e n…®gan…ômt…ôk, k…ôn ekuw…®n mau r…ôk…®s, k…ôn n…®gan…ômt…ôk t…ôw…®r, iat…ôplan nat.‚Äù  
\v 16 K…ôn Farisi m…®n neen k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah un t…ôs…®s…®-p…ôn…ôn o Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inun, in t…ôs…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn Lou r…ôha Sapat.‚Äù  
\p M…ôto Farisi m…®n neen m…®n kot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôto tahro? Suah …ôh s…ôn…ôm…ô in iol t…ôfag…ô rat. Iol t…ôfag…ô rat t…ôruru nol…ôn n…ômt…ôtin kit nulan.‚Äù K…ôn ilat k…ômotoor ilat m…®n o n…ôghat…ôn u.  
\v 17 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh m…®n ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Suah …ôh t…ômol-w…®r n…®gan…ômt…®m, k…ôn n…®kim t…ôht m…ôm…ô in et…ômim naka?‚Äù K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIn ien kit.‚Äù  
\v 18 M…ôto net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel k…ôsot…ôn…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn lan m…ôm…ô suah u aup…ôn n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôm…ôp…®s, m…ôto roiu …ôh, t…®n…ôtaiir. Tol n…ôhlan, ilat k…ômotaun-in-p…ôn r…ôhan tata ne mama kueia,  
\v 19 k…ôn k…ômot…ôtap…ôh olau m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? ?N…ôt…®t…ômlau u suah u? ?It…ômlau onaku…ôn-tu m…ôm…ô nian in t…ômaiir-pa, k…ôn n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôp…®s? ?Ok…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn, k…ôn n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ômahrol m…ôw…®r?‚Äù   
\p
\v 20 K…ôn r…ôhan mama ne tata ku…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…®mlau ekiatun m…ôm…ô n…ôt…®t…®mlau …ôh, k…ôn it…®mlau ekiatun m…ôm…ô t…ômaiir-pa, n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôp…®s.  
\v 21 M…ôto it…®mlau eku…ôruru m…ôm…ô, roiu …ôh, k…ômahrol n…®gan…ômt…®n taiir. K…ôn it…®mlau eku…ôruru m…®n m…ôm…ô et…ômim pah t…ômol n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôw…®r. T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô it…ômat nakot…ôtap…ôh ron. In t…®nep…ôt r…ôk…®s, in t…®tun n…ôn…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n rafin k…ôm it…ômat.‚Äù  
\v 22 R…ôhan tata ne mama, k…ômu…ôn n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu ilau katu…ôgin net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha Isrel, m…ôto-inu ilat k…®not…ôl…ôh…ôu r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn kit m…ôm…ô, et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, k…ôn ilat okotahl-iar…ôp in e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn.   
\p
\v 23 Tol n…ôhlan, r…ôhan tata ne mama, ilau k…ômu…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIn t…®nep…ôt r…ôk…®s, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô it…ômat nakot…ôtap…ôh ron, p…ôs in t…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 24 O nat u, ilat k…ômotaun-in-p…ôn m…®n suah un it…ôm n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôm…ôp…®s aup…ôn, m…ôm…ô otuwa m…ôtul aup…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…®lat. K…ôn k…ômot…ôhai mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èn n…®pahrien…ôn k…ôn l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® Uhg…®n. It…®mat ekot…®tun m…ôm…ô suah u, in iol t…ôfag…ô rat.‚Äù   
\p
\v 25 M…ôto suah u t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ek…ôruru m…ôm…ô suah u in iol t…ôfag…ô rat, o k…ôp. Nat kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm io ek…®tun. Aup…ôn n…®gan…ômt…ôk t…ôm…ôp…®s, m…ôto roiu enataiir.‚Äù   
\p
\v 26 K…ôn ilat k…®not…ôtap…ôh m…®n ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ômahrol ik? ?T…ômahrol mol-w…®r ik, k…ôn n…®gan…ômt…®m t…ôw…®r?‚Äù   
\p
\v 27 M…ôto in t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEn…ôm…ôn-ip…®n…ô r…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn io. ?T…ôhrol nakot…ôm…ô iak…ôn m…®n? ?It…ômat m…®n nakot…ôm…ô r…ôhan u it…ômat?‚Äù   
\p
\v 28 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôhai in mot…ôn rat, mot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ah! !Ik u r…ôhan et…ômim! !M…ôto it…®mat u, net…ômim r…ôha Moses!\f + \fr 9:28 \ft Jon 5:45\f*  
\v 29 It…®mat ekot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômat…ôghat k…ôm Moses, m…ôto suah un, ekot…ôruru m…ôm…ô t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn hi…ô.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:29 \ft Net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, t…ôm…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô ilat okot…®tun m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn o Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n …ôm t…®tun nol-w…®r…ôn n…®gan…ômt…®n …ôp…®s. M…ôs…®n m…®n un, Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô nian Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa tuwa, k…ôn in otol-w…®r n…®gan…ômt…®n …ôp…®s m…®n okot…ôw…®r (Aes 29:18, 35:5, 42:7). M…ôto, net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, n…®gan…ômt…®lat t…ôp…®s o nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn kotap…ôs n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn Iesu.\f*   
\p
\v 30 K…ôn suah apon t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!N…ôman! !Narm…ôk t…ômiw…®g p…®k! !Suah u in t…ômol-w…®r n…®gan…ômt…ôk, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru ik…®n t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn ik…®n!  
\v 31 Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôs…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn net…ôm koatol nol…ôn rat. !M…ôto et…ôm tat…®siai-in Uhg…®n, k…ôn matol n…ôwian, Uhg…®n tat…ôt…ôl…®g-in!\f + \fr 9:31 \ft Sam 66:16-20; Prov 15:29; Aes 1:15; 59:2\f*  
\v 32 E n…ôtuoun…ôn nian, m…ôtoarus-pa u-roiu, k…ôs…ôto…ôn …ôh suah kit m…ôm…ô t…ômol-w…®r igan…ômt…®n …ôp…®s kit it…ôm t…ômaiir-pa tol mihin, m…ôto n…®gan…ômt…®n t…®n…ôw…®r.  
\v 33 Ok…ôm…ô suah u t…ôm…ôs…®s…®-p…ôn…ôn o Uhg…®n, okol t…ôsol ag…®n-…ôh nat kit. M…ôto t…ôtuat…®p …ôm m…ôm…ô in tat…®s…®-p…ôn o Uhg…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:33 \ft Jon 3:2\f*   
\p
\v 34 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôhai m…®n mot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!N…ôman! Ik et…ômim r…ôha nol…ôn rat nian rafin …ôm, t…ôtuoun e nian n…ômaiir-pa m…ôtoarus-pa u-roiu. ?Nakahrol m…ôm…ô nak…ôg…ôtun it…®mat?‚Äù K…ôn ilat k…ômotahl-iar…ôp in e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn.\f + \fr 9:34 \ft Jon 9:2; Aes 66:5\f*   
\s1 N…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha Farisi m…®n, tahmen e et…ôm n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôp…®s  
\p
\v 35 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôto n…ôghat…ôn m…ôm…ô k…ômahl-iar…ôp suah u e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn, k…ôn in t…ômuw…®n m…ôplan, k…ôn t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? ?Ik n…ôkatahat…ôt…ô e N…ôt…® Et…ômim?‚Äù   
\p
\v 36 K…ôn suah un t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Et…ôm-iasol, et…ômim un in pah? !Awi! ∆èn-ipa-tu k…ôm io, p…ôs io ekahat…ôt…ô lan.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:36 \ft Rom 10:14\f*   
\p
\v 37 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRoiu …ôh, ik n…®nehm r…ôk…®s in. Suah u, m…ô inu io, iat…ôghat k…ôm ik u-roiu.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:37 \ft Jon 4:26\f*   
\p
\v 38 K…ôn suah un t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Iesu m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, io enatahat…ôt…ô lam.‚Äù K…ôn in t…ôm…®sin-p…ôn nul…®n ron, k…ôn mat…ôfak k…ôm in.\f + \fr 9:38 \ft Mat 28:9\f*   
\p
\v 39 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo emuwa e n…ôtueint…ôn u m…ôm…ô ekakil net…ômim motoor ilat, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, net…ôm n…®gan…ômt…®lat t…ôm…ôp…®s, okotehm nat, k…ôn net…ôm m…®n u koatehm nat, n…®gan…ômt…®lat ot…ôp…®s.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:39 \ft Aes 6:10; Mak 4:12; Luk 4:18\f*   
\p
\v 40 K…ôn Farisi m…®n neen …ôh-ik…®n, k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn lan, k…ôn kot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? ?Ik nakat…ôn m…ôm…ô n…®gan…ômt…®t…®mat m…®n t…ôp…®s?‚Äù\f + \fr 9:40 \ft Rom 2:19\f*   
\p
\v 41 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô n…®gan…ômt…®t…ômat t…ôp…®s, oes…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motos nalp…®n…ôn o t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n r…ôhat…ômat. M…ôto it…ômat nakot…ôm…ô n…®gan…ômt…®t…ômat t…ôw…®r, nakotehm nat, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n r…ôhat…ômat t…ôtat…®g …ôh et…ômat.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:41 \ft Jon 15:22,24; Hip 10:28-31\f*   
\c 10  
\s1 Iesu t…ômu…ôh nimaa n…ôghat…ôn e et…ômim r…ôha nehm…ôn sipsip  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, et…ômim it…ôm tatuw…®n im…ô e noan…®kulu r…ôha sipsip, t…ôsuw…®n-p…ôn…ôn e ket, m…ôto in t…ôtaiu …ôm lan k…ôn matiw…®gego in m…ôm…ô otuw…®n im…ô e noan…®kulu r…ôha sipsip,\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Noan…®kulu r…ôha sipsip un, tahmen e ik…®n kit it…ôm kat…ôhg-ip…ôn sipsip m…®n ik…®n nian rafin lap…®n, m…ôm…ô ilat okotat…®g w…®r o kuri iarup…®n m…®n ne laion m…®n.\f* in iakl…ôh ne iohamnu it…ôm kit.\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Jon 10:8,10\f*\fig |alt="sheep in sheepfold with shepherd" src="LB00014B.TIF" size="span" loc="Jhn 10:1-10" ref="Jon 10:1" \fig*  
\v 2 M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm tatuw…®n-p…ôn e ket, in et…ôm tatehm sipsip.\f + \fr 10:2 \ft E ves m…®n u 1-5, ket ne et…ôm tatehm sipsip, ilau k…ôr…ôn katu…ôpsen-p…ôn Iesu, k…ônu iakl…ôh m…®n koat…ôpsen-p…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. K…ônu sipsip m…®n koat…ôpsen-p…ôn net…ômim m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f*  
\v 3 Et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôtul e ket, nian rafin in tater…ôh e ket o suah u, k…ôn sipsip m…®n kot…®tun n…ôwian. Nian rafin in t…ôtaun-in n…ôrg…® sipsip m…®n kiti…ôh kiti…ôh, k…ôn in matit ilat moatiet.  
\v 4 Nian in tatit r…ôhan m…®n rafin sipsip moatiet e noan…®kulu, in t…ôtaup…ôn-in ilat, k…ôn sipsip m…®n koatuaris…®g-in, m…ôto-inu kot…®tun n…ôwian.  
\v 5 M…ôto ilat k…ôsot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn suah kit u it…ôm kot…ôruru, ilat okot…ôk…ôike kag…®m kap…ôs, m…ôto-inu ilat kot…ôruru n…ôwian.‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 Iesu t…ômu…ôh nimaa n…ôghat…ôn u, m…ôto ilat kot…ôruru n…®p…ôt…®n m…ôm…ô tat…ôn naka.   
\s1 Iesu in et…ômim …ôtuat…®p r…ôha nehm…ôn sipsip  
\p
\v 7 Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn m…®n k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, io u, io Ket r…ôha sipsip m…®n it…ôm koatuw…®n-p…ôn ik…®n.\f + \fr 10:7 \ft Jon 1:51; 14:6\f*  
\v 8 Net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm kotaup…ôn-in io, ilat rafin net…ômim r…ôha nakl…ôh…ôn …ôm ne nohamnu…ôn it…ôm.\f + \fr 10:8 \ft Jer 12:1; Esik 34:2\f* M…ôto sipsip m…®n kol k…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn ilat.  
\v 9 Io un, io Ket u. Et…ôm tatuwa-pa io ik…®n, m…ôm…ô otuw…®n im…ô, in otos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. In otuwa im…ô, miet muw…®n ihlu…ô e io, k…ôn mos manuw…®hl w…®r it…ôm tami…ôm…®t…ô lan.\f + \fr 10:9 \ft Sam 118:20,22-24\f*  
\v 10 M…ôto iakl…ôh, in tatuwa …ôm o nat kiti…ôh …ôm. In tatuwa m…ôm…ô otakl…ôh k…ôn mohamnu it…ôm, k…ôn m…ôr…ôk…®n-…ôr…ôk…®n nat…®mnat rafin. M…ôto io, emuwa m…ôm…ô iakol suat…®p o nos…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn,\f + \fr 10:10 \ft Jon 1:4; 3:15-16; 5:40; 20:31\f* k…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn u, in t…ôrioah w…®r e n…ôw…®r…ôn rafin.   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúIo u, Et…ômim r…ôha Nehm W…®r…ôn Sipsip M…®n.\f + \fr 10:11 \ft Sam 23:1; Aes 40:11; Esik 34; Maeka 5:2,4; Mat 2:6; Mak 6:34; 1 Pita 2:25; 5:2-4; Nol ∆èp…ôn 7:17; Jon 15:13; 1 Jon 3:16\f* Et…ôm w…®r un, it…ôm tatehm w…®r sipsip m…®n, in n…®kin tagien …ôm m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhan o sipsip m…®n.\f + \fr 10:11 \ft Hip 13:20\f*  
\v 12 M…ôto et…ômim un it…ôm kat…ôtou m…ôm…ô in otatehm sipsip m…®n, in s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ôm …ôtuat…®p r…ôha nehm…ôn sipsip. S…ôn…ôm…ô in r…ôhan …ôh sipsip m…®n. K…ôn ok…ôm…ô tar…ôplan kuri iarup…®n kit tatuwa m…ôm…ô otus ilat, k…ôn in otaiu map…ôs ilat. K…ôn kuri iarup…®n u, tuw…®n mus sipsip m…®n neen, k…ôn m…ôhgatit ilat kotag…®m kiti…ôh kiti…ôh.  
\v 13 Et…ôm n…ôhlan, in otag…®m m…ôto-inun kat…ôtou …ôm in o nehm…ôn sipsip m…®n, m…ôto e n…®kin, in t…ôsol…ôn nat ag…®n e sipsip m…®n.   
\p
\v 14-15 ‚ÄúIo u inu, io Et…ômim r…ôha Nehm W…®r…ôn Sipsip M…®n. Tata Uhg…®n in t…®tun io, k…ôn io ek…®tun in,\f + \fr 10:14-15 \ft Mat 11:27\f* k…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, io ek…®tun r…ôhak sipsip m…®n, k…ôn r…ôhak sipsip m…®n ilat kot…®tun io. Io n…®kik tagien …ôm, m…ôm…ô oek…®m…®s o nosmeg…ôh…ôn ilat.  
\v 16 K…ônu r…ôhak m…®n neen …ôp…ôh ik…®n sipsip m…®n, it…ôm k…ôsotat…®g…ôn e noan…®kulu u, m…ôto io ek…ôk…ôike mit m…®n ilat kotuwa. Ilat m…®n, ok…ôpanot…®tun n…ôto…ôn n…ôwiak. K…ônu sipsip m…®n u ilat rafin u, okotuwa motu…ôf…®m…®n …ôm ilat m…®n motol kiti…ôh. K…ôn et…ômim kiti…ôh …ôm, in otatehm ilat.\f + \fr 10:16 \ft Ves 16 u, in tat…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn e ves m…®n 1-5. Ik…®n …ôh, noan…®kulu r…ôha sipsip tat…ôg…ôtun net…ôm Isrel. Iesu t…ôtaun-in ilat m…ôm…ô r…ôhan m…®n. Sipsip m…®n it…ôm kotat…®g …ôh e noan…®kulu …ôh, ilat u, net…ôm Isrel it…ôm k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Iesu. Sipsip m…®n it…ôm Iesu tat…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat k…ôsotat…®g…ôn e noan…®kulu u, ilat Iaihlu…ô m…®n. Nian in otaun-in ilat, k…ôn ilat m…®n okot…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôwian, k…ôn ilat rafin okotuwa kol kiti…ôh, k…ôn et…ômim kiti…ôh …ôm, inu Iesu, in otatehm w…®r ilat.\f* \f + \fr 10:16 \ft Aes 56:8; Jon 11:52; W…ôk 10:34,35; Rom 1:16; Efes 3:6\f*   
\p
\v 17 ‚ÄúR…ôhak Tata in tolkeike p…®k io, m…ôto-inu n…®kik tagien …ôm m…ôm…ô oekos-ip…ôn r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn o net…ômim, m…ôm…ô uaris…®g lan, io ekos m…®n n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak.\f + \fr 10:17 \ft Aes 53:12\f*  
\v 18 Et…ômim kit t…®k…ô m…ôm…ô otos-ir…ôk…®s n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak, m…ôto io at…®p …ôm ekos-ip…ôn r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn m…ôto-inun io …ôm iakolkeike mihin. Io at…®p …ôm iatos nep…ôt…ôn m…ôm…ô ek…ôhlman r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, k…ôn io at…®p …ôm matos m…®n nep…ôt…ôn m…ôm…ô ekask…ôl…®m m…®n r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. Nat u inu, it…ôm r…ôhak Tata t…ôm…ôn-ipa k…ôm io m…ôm…ô ek…ôk…ôike mol mihin.‚Äù\f + \fr 10:18 \ft Mat 26:53-54; Fil 2:8; Hip 5:8\f*   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn net…ôm Isrel u, ilat k…ômotoor m…®n ilat m…®n o n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u.  
\v 20 Ilat tep…ôt kot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Suah u narm…®n rat kit t…ôtat…®g lan! !R…ôhn-kap…ô t…ôtalm…ôl! ?T…ôhrol it…ômat nakoat…ôt…ôl…®g-in?‚Äù   
\p
\v 21 M…ôto neen m…®n, ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôghat…ôn u, s…ôn…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha et…ôm narm…®n rat t…ôtat…®g lan. ?N…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô, narm…®n rat t…®tun nol-w…®r…ôn igan…ômt…®n …ôp…®s, t…ôw…®r m…®n?‚Äù\f + \fr 10:21 \ft Eks 4:11\f*   
\s1 Net…ômim k…ômoatet…ôhau Iesu, m…ôto-inu in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n  
\p
\v 22 T…®nuwa e nian r…ôha net…ôm Isrel it…ôm koatol lafet kit lan Jerusalem. N…ôrg…® lafet u, in lafet r…ôha Nol-W…®r…ôn M…®n Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 10:22 \ft Lafet …ôh koatol n…®kilat tatu…ôh nian kit aup…ôn. T…®p…®lat m…®n k…ômotaf…ôl w…®r Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, t…ôpi…ô, k…ôn m…ôw…®r, masim. Lafet …ôh, in kat…ôn m…®n m…ôm…ô lafet r…ôha Laet M…®n, m…ôto-inu net…ômim k…ômotasi…ôp…ôn e lait m…®n tep…ôt e r…ôhalat latu…ônu m…®n.\f*  
\v 23 In …ôh e nian r…ôha n…ôt…ôp…ôn. K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôtaliw…ôk e feranta e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, n…ôrg…®n u, Feranta R…ôha Kig Solomon.  
