\v 42 K…ôn ek…®tun m…ôm…ô e nian rafin, nat…ôto io. M…ôto iat…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, o net…ôm m…®n u, it…ôm koat…ôtul t…®t…ôlau-in io, m…ôm…ô ilat okotahat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô ik n…ômahl-ipa io.‚Äù\f + \fr 11:42 \ft Jon 3:17\f*  
\v 43 K…ôn …ômun, nian Iesu t…®n…ôn r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn u, in t…ômaun …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Lasaros, …ôtul miet!‚Äù  
\v 44 K…ôn Lasaros t…ôm…ôtul miet, mat…ôm…®k m…ôtm…ôt…®g …ôm n…®m…ôhan m…®n u it…ôm k…ôm…ôlis …ôtain nelm…®n ne nelk…®n ne n…®gan…ômt…®n ne lan. K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOt…®k…®s r…ôk…®s n…®m…ôhan m…®n …ôh, p…ôs in taliw…ôk.‚Äù   
\s1 Net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômoteg…ôs-in suat…®p m…ôm…ô okotoh Iesu  
\r (Mat 26:1-5; Mak 14:1-2;  //  Luk 22:1-2)  
\p
\v 45 Net…ôm Isrel it…ôm k…ômotuwa o Meri k…ôn motehm nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm Iesu t…ômol, ilat tep…ôt k…ômotahat…ôt…ô lan.  
\v 46 M…ôto ilat m…®n neen k…ômotuw…®n o Farisi m…®n, k…ôn mot…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm ilat rafin nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm Iesu t…ômol.  
\v 47 K…ôn o nat u, Farisi m…®n u ne pris asol m…®n ilat k…ômotask…ôl…®m nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn asol kit r…ôhalat, k…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn k…ôm ilat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Okot…ôhrol nulan? Suah …ôh t…®natol n…ômt…ôtin tep…ôt.  
\v 48 Ok…ôm…ô okotap…ôs …ôm, tatol n…ôhlan, k…ôn net…ômim rafin okotahat…ôt…ô lan, k…ôn net…ôm Rom ilat okotuwa mot…ôr…ôk…®n Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n ne kantri r…ôhatat k…ôn motos-ir…ôk…®s ilau e nelm…®tat.‚Äù   
\p
\v 49 K…ôn ilat kit u, n…ôrg…®n u Kaeafas, in pris asol ag…®n e nup …ôh. Tol nulan, in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru ag…®n-…ôh nat u.  
\v 50 ?T…ôhrol it…ômat n…ôsot…®tun…ôn? ?It…ômat n…ôsot…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô t…ôw…®r m…ôs…®n ot…ômat m…ôm…ô et…ômim kiti…ôh …ôm ot…®m…®s o net…ômim, tapr…ôk…®s-in m…ôm…ô kantri api…ôpi…ô ot…®m…®s?‚Äù\f + \fr 11:50 \ft Jon 18:14\f*   
\p
\v 51 Nian in t…®n…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, in t…ôm…ôs…ôn at…®p…ôn e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn …ôm r…ôhan. In pris asol ag…®n e nup …ôh, k…ôn in t…ômaup…ôn m…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn k…ôm in. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô Iesu in ot…®m…®s o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ôm Isrel.\f + \fr 11:51 \ft Kai…ôf…ôs tolkeike m…ôm…ô okohamnu Iesu m…ôto-inu t…ôsolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ôm Rom okot…ôr…ôk…®n kantri r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. M…ôto, in t…ômat…ôn aup…ôn nat kit it…ôm otuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn lan, m…ôto in t…ôruru nat …ôh in tat…ôn. R…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn, n…®p…ôt…®n tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô Iesu ot…ôk…ôike m…®m…®s m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôsol…ôn nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm r…ôhan net…ômim o r…ôhalat t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n.\f*   
\p
\v 52 K…ôn m…ôto r…ôhan n…®m…®s…ôn, s…ôn…ôm…ô o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ôm Isrel …ôm, m…ôto o nosm…ôg…ôh m…®n…ôn nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n it…ôm kotan atit e n…ôtueint…ôn, k…ôn mol ilat kotuwa motol kiti…ôh …ôm.\f + \fr 11:52 \ft Aes 49:6; Jon 10:16\f*  
\v 53 Tol n…ôhlan, e nian …ôh, ilat k…ômoteg…ôhan-in m…ôm…ô okot…ôk…ôike keg…ôs-in suat…®p kit o nohamnu…ôn Iesu.  
\v 54 K…ôn o nat u, Iesu t…ôsaliw…ôk-ar…ôp m…®n…ôn ik…®n m…®n e Jutia, in t…ômag…®m ik…®n-u, muw…®n …ôp…ôh e taon kit, n…ôrg…®n u Efraim. Taon u, in iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n. K…ôn in m…ôtat…®g ik…®n …ôh, ilat r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim.   
\s1 Net…ômim k…ômoatol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô o nol…ôn lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn  
\p
\v 55 T…®natuwa iu…ôhk…®r o nian r…ôha lafet kit r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, n…ôrg…®n u, lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn.\f + \fr 11:55 \ft Eks 12:13,23,27\f* K…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt k…®noatiet ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n m…®noatuwa Jerusalem m…ôm…ô okotol nat…®mnat m…®n m…ôm…ô ilat okotaru…ôtu…ôh\f + \fr 11:55 \ft Okotaru…ôtu…ôh, n…®p…ôt…®n un, m…ôm…ô ilat okotaf…ôl w…®r ilat m…®n, m…ôto-inu ilat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô ilat kotamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n.\f* e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, paup…ôn un, m…ôpanotuw…®n e lafet …ôh.  
\v 56 K…ôn net…ôm m…®n …ôh k…®noateg…ôs-in Iesu. K…ôn nian k…ômotu…ôf…®m…®n e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…®noat…ôtap…ôh-…ôtap…ôh olat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?K…ôruru m…ô Iesu otuwa e lafet u, o k…ôp?‚Äù   
\p
\v 57 M…ôto e nian …ôh, pris asol m…®n ne Farisi m…®n k…ômot…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn kit, m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô et…ômim kit t…®tun ik…®n Iesu t…ôtat…®g ik…®n, in ot…ôk…ôike muwa m…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn k…ôm ilat, p…ôs mopael m…®n kotuw…®n motask…ôl…®m.   
\c 12  
\s1 Meri t…ômau nelk…® Iesu e senta  
\r (Mat 26:6-13; Mak 14:3-9)  
\m
\v 1 Nian sikis …ôh-ik…®n t…ôtat…®g …ôh k…ôp…ônan e nian r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, k…ôn Iesu t…®n…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n Petani, im…ô Lasaros ik…®n. Suah u inu, Iesu in t…ômol in t…ômeg…ôh m…®n.  
\v 2 K…ôn net…ômim ik…®n-u, k…ômotol nagw…ôn…ôn kit r…ôha Iesu. K…ôn Mata in tos nagw…ôn…ôn, muwa.\f + \fr 12:2 \ft Luk 10:38-42\f* K…ôn Lasaros m…®n …ôh-ik…®n e nagw…ôn…ôn …ôh, ilat Iesu ne, koat…ôm…ôhl-p…ôn, moatagw…ôn.\f + \fr 12:2 \ft N…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat k…ôsot…ôp…ôl…ôh…ôn motagw…ôn. M…ôto e nol…ôn r…ôhalat e nian …ôh, ilat kotap…®l mot…®sin-p…ôn nuwl…ôlm…®lat e tep…®l, k…ôtagw…ôn.\f*  
\v 3 K…ôn Meri t…ômos senta kit tat…ôr e nuwig…® nat, muwa. Senta u, k…ômol e nok…® nato.\f + \fr 12:3 \ft Nato in nat kit n…ômi…ôw…®n tat…ôpien w…®r, tahmen e n…®gp…®s.\f* Senta …ôh, n…ômi…ôw…®n t…ôw…®r, k…ôn n…ômt…®n ti…ôk…®s. K…ôn in t…ômau nelk…® Iesu e senta u, k…ôn maf…ôl e noanun. N…ômi…ôw…® senta u, t…ôm…®r…ôfin n…®p…ôgnoa nim…ô.\f + \fr 12:3 \ft Mak 14:3\f*  
\v 4 M…ôto et…ômim kit r…ôha Iesu, n…ôrg…®n u Jutas Iskariot, suah un uaris…®g ot…ôpaneg…ôhan-in-p…ôn Iesu e nelm…® r…ôhan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n, in t…ôm…ôhai ron. In t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\v 5 ‚Äú?Ik n…ôk…ôruru nol-sal…®m-in senta u, mos m…ôni lan, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn k…ôm ian-rat m…®n? Senta u, in tahmen e tri-hanr…®t tenarius.\f + \fr 12:5 \ft Roiu, tri-hanr…®t tenarius tahmen e tri-hanr…®t-taosan vatu.‚Äù\f*  
\v 6 In t…ôm…ôn n…ôhlan, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô in tatol nat ag…®n e ian-rat m…®n, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôn …ôm, m…ôto-inu in iakl…ôh. In tatos k…ôt…®m r…ôha m…ôni r…ôhalat, k…ôn nian neen, in t…ôtakl…ôh-in.   
\p
\v 7 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èp…ôs-tu p…ôtan u. S…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn. In t…ômat…ôl…ôh…ôu w…®r senta u, m…ôm…ô otau n…®p…ôt…®k, o nian …ôh it…ôm ok…®t…ôn…®m io lan.  
\v 8 Ian rat m…®n, nian rafin it…ômat min ilat n…ôkotat…®g.\f + \fr 12:8 \ft Dut 15:11\f* M…ôto io, okol esat…®g…ôn nian rafin kitat min it…ômat.‚Äù   
\s1 Pris asol m…®n k…ômoteg…ôs-in m…®n suat…®p o nohamnu…ôn Lasaros  
\p
\v 9 K…ôn nian n…®manin net…ôm Jutia k…ômot…ôto m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôtat…®g latu…ônu Petani, k…ôn ilat k…®noatuwa ik…®n. K…ôsotuwa …ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô okotehm Iesu, m…ôto ilat kotuwa m…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan-tu Lasaros u t…ôm…®m…®s, k…ôn Iesu tol m…®n t…ômeg…ôh.\f + \fr 12:9 \ft Jon 11:43,44\f*  
\v 10 K…ôn …ômun, pris asol m…®n, k…ômoteg…ôhan-in m…®n m…ôm…ô ok…ôk…ôike kohamnu m…®n Lasaros,  
\v 11 m…ôto-inun nian net…ôm Isrel tep…ôt k…ômot…ôplan Lasaros t…ôm…ômeg…ôh m…®n, k…ôn ilat k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu, k…ôn m…®notap…ôs r…ôhalat net…ôm-iasol m…®n.   
\s1 Iesu t…ômuwa Jerusalem matol …ôp in m…ôm…ô in kig  
\r (Mat 21:1-11; Mak 11:1-11; Luk 19:28-40)  
\p
\v 12 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin, n…®manin net…ômim it…ôm k…ômoatuwa Jerusalem m…ôm…ô okotol lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, k…ômot…ôto m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôtaliw…ôk m…®natuwa e taon.  
\v 13 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, ilat k…ômotiet e taon u, moat…ôm…®k nat kit tahmen e n…®mal…® n…ôm…®l\f + \fr 12:13 \ft N…®mal…® n…ôm…®l u in n…ômt…ôtin r…ôha n…ôpt…ôn r…ôhalat ne nol win…ôn e t…®k…®m…®r m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. Ok…ôm-naka ilat k…ômoturin-urin n…®mal…® n…ôm…®l m…ôto-inu n…®kilat tat…ôht m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo, k…ôn in t…®nuwa m…ôm…ô ot…ômki-r…ôk…®s ilat e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Rom.\f* moatuw…®n m…ô okot…ôplan Iesu. K…ôn moatag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh moat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚Äú!Hosana!\f + \fr 12:13 \ft N…ôghat…ôn u, ‚ÄúHosana,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n …ôtuat…®p in ‚ÄúAsitu, Uhg…®n, osmeg…ôh it…®mat,‚Äù m…ôto e nian r…ôha Iesu, n…ôghat…ôn u, ilat k…ômot…ôuhlin …ôm n…®p…ôt…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!∆ènwiwi Uhg…®n!‚Äù Ves u ilat koat…ôn, in t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e Sam 118:25-26.\f*  
\q1 !I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g ilau suah u it…ôm tatuwa e n…ôrg…®n!  
\q1 !I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g ilau Kig u r…ôha net…ôm Isrel!‚Äù\f + \fr 12:13 \ft Jon 1:49\f*   
\p
\v 14 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôplan n…ôt…® togki kit, k…ôn tasu…ô lan maliw…ôk matuw…®n. Nat…®mnat m…®n u, Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n t…®n…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô,\fig |alt="tied donkey" src="HK00033B.TIF" size="col" loc="Jhn 12:14-15" ref="Jon 12:14" \fig*   
\q1
\v 15 ‚ÄúNet…ôm Saeon,\f + \fr 12:15 \ft Jerusalem u, k…ômotaun-in m…®n m…ôm…ô Saeon, m…ôto-inun n…ôrg…®n …ôh r…ôha n…®tot kit it…ôm k…ômil…ôk…®n-p…ôr taon lan. Saeon u, in n…ôrg…® Jerusalem kit m…®n.\f* it…ômat sot…ôg…®n…ôn.  
\q1 !Ot…ôplan-tu! !Kig r…ôhat…ômat tatuwa,  
\q1 in t…®tasu…ô e n…ôt…® togki maliw…ôk matuwa!‚Äù\f + \fr 12:15 \ft Sek 9:9\f*   
\p
\v 16 E nian …ôh, net…ômim r…ôha Iesu ilat kot…ôruru n…®p…ôt…® nat u. M…ôto uaris…®g, nian Iesu t…®n…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn Uhg…®n t…®nol …ôp r…ôk…®s nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha Iesu, k…ôn n…®kilat t…ôpan…ôht m…ôm…ô aup…ôn, k…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn lan e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ônu net…ômim k…®notol n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh t…®nuwa m…®nol n…®pahrien…ôn lan.   
\p
\v 17 E nian Iesu t…ômaun-in Lasaros, k…ôn Lasaros tiet e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel m…ômeg…ôh m…®n, n…®manin net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotat…®g ilat …ôh-ik…®n. K…ôn ilat …ôh k…ômot…ôtul-ar…ôp m…®not…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat m…®n u in t…ômol.  
\v 18 Tol n…ôhlan, net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotuwa m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan Iesu, m…ôto-inu koat…ôto m…ôm…ô in t…ômol n…ômt…ôtin …ôh.  
\v 19 K…ôn Farisi m…®n k…®noat…ôn-…ôn k…ôm ilat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ot…ôplan-tu, okol kitat k…ôsotol ag…®n-…ôh…ôn nat kit. Roiu …ôh, net…ômim rafin e n…ôtuoun…ôn k…®noatuaris…®g-in!‚Äù   
\s1 Net…ôm Kris neen k…ômotolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan Iesu  
\p
\v 20 K…ôn nian net…ômim k…ômotuw…®n Jerusalem m…ôm…ô okot…ôfak e nian r…ôha lafet u, k…ôn net…ôm Kris neen m…®n …ôh-ik…®n ilat min, k…ômoat…ôfak.  
\v 21 Net…ôm Kris m…®n u k…ômotuwa motehm Filip. Filip in et…ôm Petsaeta …ôp…ôh Kalili. K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol, iakotolkeike m…ôm…ô ekot…ôplan Iesu.‚Äù  
\v 22 K…ôn Filip t…ôtul muw…®n m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Antru, k…ôn ilau k…ômian mu…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Iesu.   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRoiu …ôh, N…ôt…® Et…ômim, r…ôhan nian t…®nuwa r…ôk…®s, m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otol …ôp r…ôhan nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag.  
\v 24 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, et…ômim ot…ôk…ôike m…®t…ôn…®m n…®kuti nat e n…®s…®p k…ôn ot…®m…®s. Ok…ôm…ô t…ôs…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn okol t…ôs…ôwi…ô…ôn k…ôn m…ôsoe…ôn. M…ôto ok…ôm…ô ot…®m…®s, k…ôn otoe-in noan tep…ôt, tep…ôt.\f + \fr 12:24 \ft 1 Korin 15:36\f*  
\v 25 Et…ôm n…®kin tat…ôht p…®k r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn e n…ôtueint…ôn u, in ot…ômkar…ôp…ôn-in. M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm n…®kin t…ôs…ôht p…®k…ôn n…ôhlan r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn e n…ôtueint…ôn u, in otask…ôl…®m w…®r n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhan o n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.\f + \fr 12:25 \ft Mat 10:39; 16:25; Mak 8:34-38; Luk 14:26; 17:33; 2 Korin 5:14-15\f*  
\v 26 Et…ôm tolkeike m…ôm…ô otol w…ôk r…ôhak, in ot…ôk…ôike muaris…®g-in io,\f + \fr 12:26 \ft Mat 10:38; Luk 14:27\f* k…ôn ok…ôm…ô ik…®n p…ôhru…ôn io ekat…®g ik…®n, k…ôn in m…®n, in otat…®g ik…®n-u.\f + \fr 12:26 \ft Jon 14:3; 17:24\f* K…ôn et…ôm tatol w…ôk r…ôhak, Tata Uhg…®n ot…®siai-in.‚Äù   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôghat-in n…®m…®s…ôn r…ôhan  
\p
\v 27 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRoiu …ôh, n…®kik t…®tahm…ô p…®k.\f + \fr 12:27 \ft Mat 26:38,39; Jon 11:33,38; 13:21\f* ?Oekahrol min-nulan? Okol es…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòTata, ohr…ôk…®s nahm…ô…ôn it…ôm tatuwa ron io.‚Äô Nat…®mnat u inu, io emuwa ron.  
\v 28 Tata, ik os-ip…ôr at…®p n…ôrg…ôm.‚Äù  
\p K…ôn …ômun, roiu ag…®n-…ôh, ilat k…ômot…ôto n…ôwian kit t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e neai tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo en…®l…ôs-ip…ôr r…ôk…®s n…ôrg…ôk, k…ôn roiu …ôh, oek…®l…ôs-ip…ôr m…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 29 K…ôn net…ômim it…ôm k…ômot…ôtul iu…ôhk…®r ron k…ômot…ôto n…ôwian …ôh, k…ôn ilat neen kot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Net…ômim! ?Naka u? ?Kalu…ôlu…ô kit, o?‚Äù M…ôto neen kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNagelo kit …ôh tat…ôghat k…ôm in.‚Äù   
\p
\v 30 M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôwian u, t…ôm…ôsuwam…ôn m…ôm…ô io ek…ôto. M…ôto t…ômuwa m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkot…ôto.\f + \fr 12:30 \ft Eks 19:9; Jon 11:42\f*  
\v 31 Roiu …ôh t…®nol nian it…ôm Uhg…®n otakil nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim e n…ôtueint…ôn. Roiu …ôh, in otoh-i…ôhau n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Setan,\f + \fr 12:31 \ft Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô n…®m…®s…ôn r…ôha Iesu t…ômol m…ôm…ô ok…ôm-naka Setan t…ômol win, m…ôto n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô in t…ôsol win…ôn. ∆èplan-tu Luk 10:18; Hip 2:14-15; 1 Jon 4:4; Nol ∆èp…ôn 12:8-9.\f* i…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u.\f + \fr 12:31 \ft Mat 4:8-9; Jon 14:30; 16:11; 2 Korin 4:4; Efes 2:2, 6:12\f*  
