\p
\v 34 K…ôn net…ômim k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…®mat enot…ôto r…ôk…®s e Lou r…ôhatat, m…ôm…ô nian Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa tuwa, in ot…ôtat…®g lil…®n …ôm, matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô.\f + \fr 12:34 \ft Net…ômim n…®kilat tat…ôht ves m…®n …ôh, tahmen e 2 Saml 7:16, Sam 72:17; 89:4,35-37; 110:1,4, Aes 9:7; Esik 37:25; Dan 7:14. N…®kilat t…ôs…ôht…ôn ves m…®n it…ôm koat…ôn m…ôm…ô Kristo in otaup…ôn m…®m…®s.\f* ?T…ôhrol ik nakat…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôk…ôike mot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr N…ôt…® Et…ômim? ?M…ôto N…ôt…® Et…ômim u, in pah?‚Äù   
\p
