\v 38 Ien r…ôha Uhg…®n u Aesea, t…ômaup…ôn mat…ôghat-in r…ôhalat nol…ôn. K…ôn nat u t…ômuwa m…ôm…ô otol n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan tuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn lan. In t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, pah otahat…ôt…ô e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhat…®mat?  
