\p
\v 41 Ien r…ôha Uhg…®n, Aesea u aup…ôn, t…ôm…ôn nulan m…ôto-inun in t…ôm…ôplan nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag r…ôha Iesu, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, in tat…ôghat-in.\f + \fr 12:41 \ft Aes 6:1-4\f*   
