\v 47 Et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôto r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn, m…ôsol…ôn, okol es…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn r…ôhan nalp…®n…ôn, m…ôto-inun em…ôsuwam…ôn e n…ôtueint…ôn u m…ôm…ô ek…ôn-iar…ôp nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ômim. M…ôto emuwa m…ôm…ô ekosmeg…ôh ilat.\f + \fr 12:47 \ft Jon 3:17\f*  
\v 48 M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôuhlin-pa m…ôntaan k…ôm io, m…ôsos…ôn r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn, nat kit …ôh-ik…®n t…ôtat…®g m…ôm…ô in ot…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôhan nalp…®n…ôn. O Namnun Nian, n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u r…ôhak, ilat okot…ôn-iar…ôp nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhan.\f + \fr 12:48 \ft Jon 5:45\f*  
