\c 13  
\s1 Iesu t…ômau nelk…® r…ôhan net…ômim  
\m
\v 1 T…®nuwa m…ôtoarus nian net…ôm Isrel kotol lafet lan, lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, k…ôn Iesu t…®n…®tun m…ôm…ô r…ôhan nian t…®nuwa r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otiet e n…ôtueint…ôn u, muw…®n mehm Tata Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 13:1 \ft Jon 16:28\f* Nian rafin in t…ômatolkeike p…®k r…ôhan net…ômim u kotat…®g e n…ôtueint…ôn, k…ôn m…ôto roiu in tat…ôg…ôtun …ôsas r…ôhan nolkeike…ôn rafin k…ôm ilat.  
\v 2 T…®nehnaip…ôn, Iesu ne r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n k…ômoatagw…ôn, k…ôn Setan t…®natos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn r…ôk…®s k…ôm Jutas Iskariot, n…ôt…® Saimon, m…ôm…ô in otosal…®m-in Iesu tuw…®n e nelm…® t…®k…®m…®r m…®n r…ôhan.  
\v 3 Iesu t…ôm…®tun m…ôm…ô Tata Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat rafin u e nelm…®n,\f + \fr 13:3 \ft Mat 28:18\f* k…ôn t…®n…®tun m…®n m…ôm…ô in t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn o Uhg…®n, k…ôn in ot…ôpan…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n o Uhg…®n.  
\v 4 Tol n…ôhlan, in t…ôm…ôtul, k…ôn mapeg r…ôk…®s r…ôhan sot asol, k…ôn m…ôt…ôut-in taw…®l kit.  
\v 5 K…ôn m…®l…ôs pes…®n kit, m…ôtu-p…ôn n…ôhau lan, k…ôn …ômun m…ôtuoun m…ôtau nelk…® r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim, k…ôn m…ôtaf…ôl e taw…®l, taw…®l u it…ôm in tat…ôt…ôut-in.   
\p
\v 6 T…ômol mihin, muw…®n e Saimon Pita, k…ôn Pita t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, t…ôhrol? T…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô ik onakau nelk…ôk.‚Äù   
\p
\v 7 M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRoiu ik n…ôk…ôruru n…®p…ôt…® nat u io iatol, m…ôto uaris…®g un, on…ôpan…®tun n…®p…ôt…®n.‚Äù   
