\p M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô ek…ôsau…ôn nelk…ôm, k…ôn okol ik n…ôk…ôsuwam…ôn mol r…ôhak et…ômim.‚Äù   
\p
\v 9 K…ôn Saimon Pita t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ok…ôm…ô tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn onasau…ôn …ôm nelk…ôk, m…ôto onakau m…®n nelm…ôk ne r…ôhk-kap…ô!‚Äù   
\p
\v 10 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!K…ôp! Et…ôm un t…®naig r…ôk…®s, in t…®n…ôru…ôn r…ôk…®s, t…®nahmen. T…ôw…®r …ôm m…ôm…ô ok…ôsau m…®n…ôn n…®p…ôt…®n; m…ôto io oek…ôike mau m…®n …ôm nelk…®n. It…ômat n…®not…ôru…ôn r…ôk…®s. M…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô it…ômat rafin ag…®n-…ôh.‚Äù\f + \fr 13:10 \ft Jon 13:18\f*  
\v 11 Iesu t…®n…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô ilat pah un oteg…ôhan-in-p…ôn in e nelm…® r…ôhan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn in t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúS…ôn…ôm…ô it…ômat rafin ag…®n-…ôh.‚Äù   
\p
\v 12 Nian Iesu t…®nau r…ôk…®s nelk…® r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n, k…ôn muw…®n m…®n e r…ôhan nap…ôn, k…ôn muw…®n m…®n m…ôp…ôl…ôh e n…ômeen e tep…®l. K…ôn …ômun m…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?It…ômat n…ôkot…®tun n…®p…ôt…® nat u emol roiu ag…®n et…ômat?\fig |alt="Jesus eating last supper with disciples" src="LB00320B.TIF" size="span" loc="Jhn 13:12-30" ref="Jon 13:12" \fig*  
\v 13 It…ômat nakotaun-in io m…ôm…ô I…ôg…ôtun ne I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ôn t…ôtuat…®p …ôm nulan, m…ôto-inun n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô io u, r…ôhat…ômat I…ôg…ôtun ne r…ôhat…ômat I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúM…ôto-inu io, io u r…ôhat…ômat I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô ne io I…ôg…ôtun r…ôhat…ômat, k…ônu io ekau nelk…®t…ômat, k…ônu it…ômat m…®n, on…ôkotau nelk…®t…ômat m…®n.\f + \fr 13:14 \ft 1 Pita 5:5\f*  
\v 15 Io emol m…ôg…ôtun it…ômat lan, m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotol nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, m…ôm…ô inu, emol mihin et…ômat.  
\v 16 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, iolw…ôk kit, in t…ôsapr…ôk…®s-in…ôn r…ôhan et…ôm-iasol, k…ônu iahl-ip…ôn in t…ôsapr…ôk…®s-in…ôn et…ôm t…®tahl…ôpis.\f + \fr 13:16 \ft Luk 6:40\f*  
\v 17 Roiu …ôh, it…ômat n…ôkot…®tun w…®r nat…®mnat m…®n u. K…ôn o nat u, ok…ôm…ô n…ôkoatol nulan, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôkotos n…ôw…®r…ôn o Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 13:17 \ft Mat 7:24,25; Luk 11:28; Jem 1:25\f*   
\p
\v 18 ‚ÄúIo es…ôn…ôn it…ômat rafin.\f + \fr 13:18 \ft Jon 13:10\f* Io ek…®tun w…®r it…ômat m…®n un it…ôm io em…®t…ôpun it…ômat.\f + \fr 13:18 \ft Jon 15:16\f* M…ôto n…ôghat…ôn u r…ôha Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, ot…ôk…ôike muwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn lan. N…ôghat…ôn u tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòEt…ômim u, aup…ôn it…®mlau ematuagw…ôn k…ôl…ôh e plet kiti…ôh, m…ôto roiu, in t…®n…ôuhlin r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn, m…®natol noa k…ôm io.‚Äô\f + \fr 13:18 \ft Sam 41:9\f*  
\v 19 Io iat…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat u-roiu, nian ok…ôsol…ôn …ôh. M…ôto nian okatol, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôkotahat…ôt…ô lak, m…ôm…ô Io u inu.\f + \fr 13:19 \ft ‚ÄúIo u inu‚Äù - ∆èplan-tu futnot e Jon 4:26.\f*  
\v 20 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, et…ômim pah it…ôm tatos r…ôhak iahl…ôpis k…ôn n…®kin tagien ron, tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô in tatos m…®n io, k…ôn n…®kin tagien ron io. K…ônu et…ômim it…ôm tatos w…®r io, k…ôn n…®kin tagien ron io, tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô in tatos w…®r m…®n r…ôhak Tata, k…ôn n…®kin tagien ron.‚Äù\f + \fr 13:20 \ft Mat 10:40; Jon 17:18\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô Jutas in oteg…ôhan-in-p…ôn in e nelm…® t…®k…®m…®r m…®n  
\r (Mat 26:20-25; Mak 14:17-21;  //  Luk 22:21-23)  
\p
\v 21 Nian Iesu t…®n…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ôn n…®kin t…ôm…ôf…®g…ôm p…®k, k…ôn in t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, it…ômat kit u ik…®n-u, oteg…ôhan-in-p…ôn io e nelm…® t…®k…®m…®r m…®n r…ôhak.‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n k…ômot…ôtag-p…ôn mot…ôplan ilat m…®n. N…®kilat nat…ôht m…ôm…ô k…ôruru m…ôm…ô in tat…ôn pah.  
\v 23 K…ôn ilat kit u it…ôm Iesu in tolkeike p…®k,\f + \fr 13:23 \ft Et…ômim it…ôm naoa u tat…ôn, in Jon u it…ôm t…ôtap…®l iu…ôhk…®r o Iesu. In u, it…ôm Iesu tolkeike p…®k, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôte naoa u, k…ôn m…ôs…ôn…ôn n…ôrg…®n.\f* in tatam…ôhl\f + \fr 13:23 \ft E nol…ôn r…ôhalat e nian …ôh, ilat kot…ôm…ôhl n…ôhlan moatagw…ôn.\f* iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o Iesu.  
\v 24 K…ôn Saimon Pita, in t…ômasg…ôw…®n-p…ôn anion k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ètap…ôh-tu ron, m…ôm…ô et…ômim pah …ôh in tat…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 25 K…ôn suah …ôh t…ômi…ôu-i…ôu muwa iu…ôhk…®r o Iesu, k…ôn m…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, pah un nakat…ôn?‚Äù  
\v 26 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ek…ômkas p…®ret m…ôs…®n, k…ônu meer-p…ôn e sup, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn k…ôm in, k…ônu suah u, inun.‚Äù K…ôn …ômun, in t…ôm…ômkas p…®ret kit, meer-p…ôn e sup, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn k…ôm Jutas, n…ôt…® Saimon Iskariot.  
\v 27 K…ôn Jutas t…ômos p…®ret un. K…ôn Setan t…®nalpin r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn.  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNat u nak…ôm…ô nakol, uw…®n u…ôhai …ôm mol.‚Äù\f + \fr 13:27 \ft Luk 22:3\f*\f + \fr 13:27 \ft Setan: ∆èplan e tiksonari.\f*  
\v 28 Net…ômim m…®n un r…ôha Iesu it…ôm kot…ôm…ôhl t…®t…ôlau e tep…®l moatagw…ôn, ilat k…ôsot…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u k…ôm in o naka.  
\v 29 Jutas in t…®tahtu k…ôt…®m r…ôha m…ôni r…ôhalat, k…ôn ilat neen n…®kilat t…ôht m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô otuw…®n mos-n…ômt…®n nagw…ôn…ôn neen n…®g…®lat o lafet, o ok…ôm-naka tatuw…®n otos-ip…ôn m…ôni neen k…ôm ian-rat m…®n.\f + \fr 13:29 \ft Jon 12:5-6\f*  
\v 30 K…ôn nian Jutas t…ômos r…ôk…®s p…®ret u, t…ôm…ôtul miet u…ôhai …ôm. K…ôn t…®napin…ôp r…ôk…®s.\f + \fr 13:30 \ft Luk 22:53\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôn n…ôghat…ôn wi kit m…ôm…ô okotol  
\p
\v 31 Nian Jutas t…®niet r…ôk…®s, k…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRoiu …ôh, Uhg…®n t…®nat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® N…ôt…® Et…ômim,\f + \fr 13:31 \ft Jon 12:23\f* k…ôn N…ôt…® Et…ômim t…®nat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® Uhg…®n.  
\v 32 M…ôto nian N…ôt…® Et…ômim t…®nol …ôp r…ôk…®s nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn Uhg…®n at…®p …ôm in otol …ôp m…®n nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha N…ôt…® Et…ômim. K…ôn in otol …ôm hu…ô roiu …ôm.\f + \fr 13:32 \ft Jon 17:1-5\f*   
\p
\v 33 ‚ÄúNen…ôt…®k m…®n, okol esat…®g…ôn tuw…ôh kitat min it…ômat. K…ôn it…ômat on…ôpanoteg…ôs-in io, m…ôto io iakat…ôn m…®n …ôm n…ôghat…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm k…ôm it…ômat u-roiu, it…ôm emat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha Isrel aup…ôn. Emat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIk…®n …ôh ekatuw…®n ik…®n, it…ômat n…ôkot…ôruru nuw…®n…ôn ik…®n.‚Äô\f + \fr 13:33 \ft Jon 7:33-34\f*   
\p
\v 34 ‚ÄúIo iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn wi kit k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…ôk…ôike moatol.\f + \fr 13:34 \ft Jon 15:12; 1 Jon 2:7-11; 3:11\f* It…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motolkeike it…ômat m…®n.\f + \fr 13:34 \ft Lev 19:18; 1 Tes 4:9; 1 Pita 1:22\f* Tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô io emolkeike mihin it…ômat, k…ônu e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, it…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motolkeike it…ômat m…®n.\f + \fr 13:34 \ft Efes 5:1-2; 1 Jon 4:10-11\f*  
\v 35 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô nakolkeike nulan it…ômat m…®n, k…ôn net…ômim rafin okot…®tun m…ôm…ô it…ômat r…ôhak m…®n net…ômim.‚Äù\f + \fr 13:35 \ft 1 Jon 3:14; 4:20\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô Pita ot…ôpan…ôn m…ôm…ô in  //  t…ôruru Iesu  
\r (Mat 26:31-35; Mak 14:27-31;  //  Luk 22:31-34)  
\p
\v 36 K…ôn Saimon Pita t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ik on…ôkuw…®n hi…ô?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk…®n …ôh io ekatuw…®n ik…®n, ik n…ôk…ôruru n…ôt…ôu-pa-m…ôn io roiu, m…ôto uaris…®g un, on…ôpanuwa.‚Äù\f + \fr 13:36 \ft Jon 14:2\f*  
\v 37 K…ôn Pita t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, oek…ôs…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn ik u-roiu o naka? Io, n…®kik tagien …ôm m…ôm…ô ek…®m…®s ron ik.‚Äù  
\v 38 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik nak…ôm…ô n…®kim tagien …ôm m…ôm…ô onak…®m…®s ron io? N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô, m…ôn…®g ot…ôs…®mn…ôn…ôn …ôh, k…ôn ik onak…ôn mau k…®s…®l m…ôm…ô n…ôk…ôruru io.‚Äù\f + \fr 13:38 \ft Jon 18:27\f*   
\c 14  
\s1 Iesu in Suat…®p o nuw…®n…ôn o Tata Uhg…®n  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kit…ômat t…ôsahm…ô…ôn. It…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 14:1 \ft Sam 4:5\f* k…ôn motahat…ôt…ô m…®n lak.  
\v 2 E nim…ô r…ôha Tata r…ôhak, noan tep…ôt …ôh-ik…®n. N…ôghat…ôn u in n…®pahrien…ôn. Ok…ôm…ô t…ôsol mihin…ôn, okol en…ôn-ip…®n…ô r…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat. Roiu …ôh, io ekatuw…®n, ekol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô r…ôhat…ômat.\f + \fr 14:2 \ft Hip 11:16\f*  
\v 3 K…ôn m…ôto-inu ekuw…®n mol apen-pena ot…ômat, k…ôn io oepan…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n mos it…ômat nakotuwa moatat…®g kitat min io,\f + \fr 14:3 \ft 1 Tes 4:16-17; 2 Korin 5:8, Fil 1:23\f* m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotat…®g ik…®n-u it…ôm io m…®n iak…ôtat…®g ik…®n.\f + \fr 14:3 \ft Jon 12:26\f*  
\v 4 Ik…®n …ôh iakatuw…®n ik…®n, it…ômat n…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s suat…®p r…ôhan.‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 M…ôto Tomas t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, it…®mat ekot…ôruru ik…®n-un nakatuw…®n ik…®n. ?Ekot…ôhrol nulan mot…®tun suat…®p tatuw…®n ik…®n …ôh?‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u,\f + \fr 14:6 \ft Jon 6:35\f* suat…®p ron.\f + \fr 14:6 \ft Jon 10:9; Hip 10:20\f* K…ôn io un, n…ôuk…ôt…® n…®pahrien…ôn,\f + \fr 14:6 \ft Jon 1:14\f* k…ônu io un, n…ôuk…ôt…® n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.\f + \fr 14:6 \ft Jon 1:4\f* Et…ômim kit okol t…ôsuwam…ôn o r…ôhak Tata ok…ôm…ô io ek…ôsos…ôn in muw…®n.\f + \fr 14:6 \ft W…ôk 4:12\f*  
\v 7 Ok…ôm…ô n…ômot…®tun io, k…ôn n…ômot…®tun m…®n r…ôhak Tata.\f + \fr 14:7 \ft Jon 1:18; 1 Jon 2:23\f* K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, t…ôtuoun roiu, n…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s in, k…ôn m…®not…ôplan.‚Äù   
\p
\v 8 K…ôn Filip t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, awi …ôg…ôtun-tu Tata Uhg…®n k…ôm it…®mat. Nat …ôm u inu, it…®mat ekotolkeike.‚Äù\f + \fr 14:8 \ft Eks 33:18\f*   
\p
\v 9 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúFilip, io em…ôtat…®g t…ôf…ôm…ôh kitat min it…ômat. M…ôto ik n…ôk…ôruru …ôh io. Et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôplan io, in tat…ôplan Tata Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 14:9 \ft Aes 9:6; Jon 1:14; 12:45; 2 Korin 4:4; Fil 2:6; Kol 1:15; Hip 1:3\f* ?T…ôhrol ik nakat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòAwi, …ôg…ôtun Tata Uhg…®n k…ôm it…®mat‚Äô?\f + \fr 14:9 \ft Jon 1:18; 10:30; 12:44-45; 13:20\f*  
\v 10 ?Ik n…ôsahat…ôt…ô…ôn m…ôm…ô iakat…®g e Tata Uhg…®n, k…ônu Tata Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g lak?\f + \fr 14:10 \ft Jon 14:20; 10:38; 17:21\f* N…ôghat…ôn m…®n u iakat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat, s…ôn…ôm…ô r…ôhak …ôm. Tata Uhg…®n u, nian rafin, t…ôtat…®g lak, inun in tatol r…ôhan m…®n u w…ôk.  
\v 11 It…ômat on…ôkot…ôike motahat…ôt…ô lak nian io iat…ôn m…ôm…ô iak…ôtat…®g e Tata Uhg…®n, k…ônu Tata Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g lak. M…ôto ok…ôm…ô k…ôp…ô, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nakotahat…ôt…ô lak o n…ôf…®g…ôm…ôn r…ôha n…ômt…ôtin m…®n it…ôm ematol.\f + \fr 14:11 \ft Jon 5:36; 10:38\f*  
\v 12 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, et…ômim it…ôm t…ôtahat…ôt…ô lak, in otol nol…ôn w…ôk m…®n un it…ôm io ematol.\f + \fr 14:12 \ft Luk 10:17\f* ∆èw…ôh, in otol nol…ôn w…ôk t…ôr t…ôhm…®n m…®n tapr…ôk…®s-in w…ôk m…®n un it…ôm io emol, m…ôto-inun io oekatuw…®n o Tata Uhg…®n.  
\v 13 Io N…ôt…®n, k…ôn ok…ôm…ô nakoteasi…ô-in nat kit e n…ôrg…ôk, nat …ôpnap…®n ok…ôm…ô nakoteasi…ô-in nat naka, io epanol,\f + \fr 14:13 \ft Mat 7:7\f* m…ôm…ô w…ôk u r…ôha N…ôt…®n ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® Tata Uhg…®n.  
\v 14 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô on…ôkoteasi…ô-in nat kit ron io, e n…ôrg…ôk, k…ôn io ekol.‚Äù   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n otuwa  
\p
\v 15 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôghat …ôh matuw…®n, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô it…ômat nakotolkeike io, k…ônu it…ômat on…ôkotol n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhak.\f + \fr 14:15 \ft Dut 11:13; Jon 13:34, 1 Jon 2:3-5,24; 5:3; 2 Jon 6\f*  
\v 16 K…ôn io, oekeasi…ô o Tata Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô in otahl-ipa Iasitu\f + \fr 14:16 \ft Jon 14:26; 15:26; 16:7\f* kit m…®n ot…ômat. K…ôn in ot…ôtat…®g lil…®n it…ômat min.  
\v 17 Suah un inun, in Narm…®n r…ôha N…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 14:17 \ft Jon 15:26; 16:13; 1 Jon 4:6; 5:6\f* Net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, okol k…ôsotos…ôn in e n…®kilat,\f + \fr 14:17 \ft 1 Korin 2:14\f* m…ôto-inu ilat k…ôsot…ôplan…ôn in, mot…ôruru in. M…ôto it…ômat, n…ôkot…®tun in, m…ôto-inun in t…ôtat…®g it…ômat min. K…ôn in ot…ôpanat…®g e n…®kit…ômat.   
\p
\v 18 ‚ÄúNian io ekiet et…ômat, okol esap…ôs…ôn it…ômat n…ôkotat…®g p…®s…®n …ôm, tahmen e suak…ôlh. Io epan…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n ot…ômat.  
\v 19 Ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u ilat ok…ôsot…ôplan…ôn io. M…ôto it…ômat on…ôpanot…ôplan io.\f + \fr 14:19 \ft Jon 16:16\f* K…ôn m…ôto-inun io epan…ômeg…ôh, it…ômat m…®n on…ôpanot…ômeg…ôh.\f + \fr 14:19 \ft Jon 6:57\f*  
\v 20 O nian r…ôha nat…®mnat m…®n u, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô iak…ôtat…®g e r…ôhak Tata.\f + \fr 14:20 \ft Jon 10:38; 17:21\f* K…ôn it…ômat n…ôkotat…®g lak, k…ônu io ek…ôtat…®g et…ômat.   
\p
\v 21 ‚ÄúEt…ômim it…ôm t…ômos w…®r n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhak, k…ôn matol, et…ômim u inun in tolkeike io. K…ôn et…ômim it…ôm tolkeike io, r…ôhak Tata in otolkeike m…®n in.\f + \fr 14:21 \ft Jon 16:27; 1 Jon 2:5\f* K…ôn io m…®n oekolkeike in. K…ôn io oekol …ôp io k…ôm in, m…ôm…ô in ot…®tun …ôsas io.‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn Jutas u, (s…ôn…ôm…ô Jutas Iskariot, m…ôto iahunin kit), in t…ôm…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ik onakahrol nulan k…ôn mol …ôp ik k…ôm it…®mat …ôm, m…ôto on…ôsol …ôp…ôn ik k…ôm net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn?‚Äù\f + \fr 14:22 \ft W…ôk 10:41\f*   
\p
\v 23 M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ômim it…ôm tolkeike io, in otatol n…ôwiak, k…ônu r…ôhak Tata in otolkeike in. K…ônu io ne r…ôhak Tata, it…®mlau ekueia m…ôtuat…®g it…®m…ôhal min. K…ôn it…®mlau ekioal imat…®mlau …ôh-ik…®n.\f + \fr 14:23 \ft Esik 37:27-28; Sek 2:10; Efes 3:17; 1 Jon 4:12,16; Nol ∆èp…ôn 21:3\f*  
\v 24 Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôsolkeike…ôn io, in t…ôsol…ôn n…ôwiak. N…ôghat…ôn m…®n u it…ôm n…ômot…ôto emat…ôn, em…ôs…ôn at…®p…ôn ilat. M…ôto emos ilat o r…ôhak Tata it…ôm in t…ômahl-ipa io ekuwa.\f + \fr 14:24 \ft Jon 5:19; 7:16; 8:28; 12:49-50\f*   
\p
\v 25 ‚ÄúIo iat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat nian etat…®g …ôh kitat min it…ômat.  
\v 26 M…ôto Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n u, in Iasitu, it…ôm Tata Uhg…®n otahl-ipa e n…ôrg…ôk, in ot…ôg…ôtun it…ômat e nat…®mnat m…®n rafin. K…ôn in otatol it…ômat m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat otat…ôht nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôsotaluin…ôn.\f + \fr 14:26 \ft Jon 15:26; 16:7,13; 1 Jon 2:27\f*   
\p
\v 27 ‚ÄúRoiu …ôh t…®nu…ôk…®r m…ôm…ô io oekap…ôs it…ômat. Io iat…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn r…ôhak t…ôtat…®g ot…ômat.\f + \fr 14:27 \ft Aes 9:6-7; Luk 2:14; 24:36; Jon 16:33; Rom 5:1; Fil 4:7\f* K…ônu n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn u, it…ôm iakatos-ip…®n…ô, t…ôsahmen…ôn e n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn it…ôm n…ôtueint…ôn u tatos-ip…®n…ô. It…ômat, n…®kit…ômat t…ôsahm…ô…ôn k…ôn m…ôsot…ôg…®n…ôn.  
\v 28 It…ômat n…®n…ômot…ôto r…ôk…®s r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn, em…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIo oepanap…ôs it…ômat, m…ôto uaris…®g, oepan…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n ot…ômat.‚Äô Ok…ôm…ô nakotolkeike pahrien io, k…ôn n…®kit…ômat otagien …ôm m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…ôplan io iakatuw…®n o r…ôhak Tata, m…ôto-inu in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in io.  
\v 29 Io iat…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s …ôm nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat u-roiu, nian ilat k…ôsotol…ôn …ôh, m…ôm…ô nian ilat k…®notuwa moatol n…®pahrien lan, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôkotahat…ôt…ô lak.  
\v 30 Roiu …ôh, okol es…ôghat…ôn t…ôf…ôm…ôh m…®n k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôto-inun Setan u i…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u,\f + \fr 14:30 \ft Jon 12:31\f* in t…®natuwa. In t…ôsos…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô otol win lak.  
\v 31 M…ôto io iatol …ôtuat…®p …ôm n…ôwia Tata Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn okot…®tun m…ôm…ô io ekolkeike in.\f + \fr 14:31 \ft Jon 10:18; 12:49\f*  
\p ‚ÄúIt…ôla, p…ôs kot…ôtul motag…®m ik…®n-u, moatuw…®n.‚Äù   
\c 15  
\s1 Iesu in tahmen e n…ôuk…ôt n…®g pahrien  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn Iesu tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo un,\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Jon 6:35\f* io ekahmen e nok…ôt n…®g pahrien. K…ôn r…ôhak Tata in tahmen e et…ômim it…ôm tat…®tas…®l…®n n…®g u.\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Aes 5:1-7\f*\fig |alt="Grape vine with supports" src="LB00107B.TIF" size="span" loc="Jhn 15:1-10" ref="Jon 15:1" \fig*  
\v 2 Nelm…® n…®g m…®n rafin it…ôm k…ôsotoe…ôn, in tat…ôte r…ôk…®s ilat, k…ôn nelm…® n…®g m…®n rafin u it…ôm koatoe, in t…ôtaf…ôl w…®r ilat,\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Hip 12:5-11\f* m…ôm…ô ilat okotoe-in noalat tep…ôt.\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Mat 7:20; Kal 5:22-23; Efes 5:8-9; Fil 1:11\f*  
\v 3 It…ômat n…ôkotahmen e nelm…® n…®g u. K…ôn io enaf…ôl w…®r r…ôk…®s it…ômat e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat.\f + \fr 15:3 \ft Jon 1:29; 13:10; Efes 5:26\f*  
\v 4 Ot…ôper-ipa lak,\f + \fr 15:4 \ft Jon 6:56\f* k…ôn io oek…ôper-ip…ôn et…ômat. Nelm…® n…®g ot…ôsoe…ôn ok…ôm…ô in t…ôs…ôper-ip…ôn…ôn e n…ôuk…ôt…®n. E nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, it…ômat okol n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat t…ôsoe-in…ôn noan ok…ôm…ô n…ôsot…ôper-ipam…ôn lak.\f + \fr 15:4 \ft ∆èplan-tu futnot …ôp…ôh Jon 6:56.\f*   
\p
\v 5 ‚ÄúIo u, io nok…ôt n…®g. K…ôn it…ômat nelm…® n…®g m…®n, nelm…® n…®g m…®n it…ôm koat…ôtul-p…ôn w…®r lak, moat…ôper-ipa. N…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôper-ipa lak k…ôn iat…ôper-ip…ôn lan, in otoe-in noan tep…ôt. M…ôto it…ômat u, ok…ôm…ô n…ôsot…ôper-ipam…ôn lak, okol n…ôsotol…ôn nat kit.\f + \fr 15:5 \ft Fil 4:13\f*  
\v 6 Ok…ôm…ô et…ômim t…ôs…ôper-ipam…ôn lak, in tahmen e nelm…® n…®g kit, it…ôm k…®n…ôrakin k…ôn t…®nap…ô r…ôk…®s. Nelm…® n…®g m…®n tol n…ôhlan, k…®tun n…ôm…®k…ôn k…ôrakin-p…ôn e n…®g…ôm, kuwaan …ôt…®p.\f + \fr 15:6 \ft Mat 3:10\f*  
\v 7 Ok…ôm…ô it…ômat nakot…ôper-ipa lak, k…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhak kot…ôper-ip…ôn et…ômat, nat naka it…ômat nakotolkeike, n…ôkot…®tun neasi…ô-in…ôn. K…ôn Uhg…®n otol k…ôm ik.\f + \fr 15:7 \ft Mat 7:7\f*  
\v 8 Nian n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat otoe-in noan tep…ôt,\f + \fr 15:8 \ft Kal 5:22-23\f* nat …ôh in tat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® r…ôhak Tata, k…ôn e nol…ôn u, tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô it…ômat r…ôhak m…®n net…ômim.\f + \fr 15:8 \ft Jon 8:31\f*   
\p
\v 9 ‚ÄúTata Uhg…®n in tolkeike p…®k io. E nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, io ekolkeike mihin it…ômat. Ot…ôper-ip…ôn e r…ôhak nolkeike…ôn.  
\v 10 Ok…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkoatol r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn,\f + \fr 15:10 \ft Jon 14:15\f* k…ôn on…ôkot…ôper-ipa e r…ôhak nolkeike…ôn, tahmen …ôtuat…®p …ôm m…ô inun io emol n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôha Tata Uhg…®n, k…ôn iat…ôper-ip…ôn e r…ôhan nolkeike…ôn.  
\v 11 Io emat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat ot…ôtagien, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô io n…®kik t…ôtagien. K…ônu n…®kit…ômat otagien otagien m…ôrioah.\f + \fr 15:11 \ft 1 Jon 1:4\f*  
\v 12 It…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike moatol n…ôghat…ôn u r…ôhak. Tat…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotolkeike it…ômat m…®n, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô io ekolkeike mihin it…ômat.\f + \fr 15:12 \ft Jon 13:34\f*  
\v 13 Suah kit t…®k…ô it…ôm tolkeike p…®k in kit tapr…ôk…®s-in et…ômim un it…ôm tateg…ôhan-in r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn m…ôm…ô otosmeg…ôh in m…®n neen.\f + \fr 15:13 \ft Jon 10:11; Rom 5:7,8; 1 Jon 3:16\f*  
\v 14 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkotol nat…®mnat m…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat, tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô it…ômat un, io m…®n neen.  
\v 15 Io oesaun-in m…®n…ôn it…ômat m…ôm…ô iolw…ôk m…®n r…ôhak, m…ôto-inun et…ôm tatol w…ôk, in t…ôruru nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm r…ôhan et…ôm-iasol tatol. M…ôto roiu …ôh, io ekaun-in it…ômat, m…ôm…ô io m…®n neen, m…ôto-inun nat…®mnat m…®n rafin u it…ôm em…ôto o r…ôhak Tata, en…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat.\f + \fr 15:15 \ft Jon 8:26\f*  
\v 16 It…ômat n…ôm…ôsot…®t…ôpun…ôn io, m…ôto io em…®t…ôpun it…ômat.\f + \fr 15:16 \ft Jon 13:18\f* K…ôn io em…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn it…ômat m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotuw…®n motol w…ôk, k…ôn w…ôk r…ôhat…ômat otoe-in noan.\f + \fr 15:16 \ft Jon 15:5\f* K…ôn noan un, in ot…ôtat…®g. Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn ok…ôm…ô nakoteasi…ô-in nat…®mnat m…®n k…ôm Tata Uhg…®n e n…ôrg…ôk, k…ôn in otos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat.  
\v 17 Iatos-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn kit k…ôm it…ômat in tol nulan. It…ômat on…ôkot…ôike motolkeike it…ômat m…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:17 \ft Jon 15:12\f*   
\s1 Net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, ilat koatet…ôhau net…ômim r…ôha Iesu  
\p
\v 18 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u koatet…ôhau it…ômat, n…®kit…ômat ot…ôk…ôike muw…ôh m…ôm…ô aup…ôn, ilat k…ômotet…ôhau mihin io.\f + \fr 15:18 \ft Aes 66:5; 1 Jon 3:13\f*  
\v 19 Ok…ôm…ô it…ômat net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, k…ôn net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn okotolkeike it…ômat, m…ôto-inu r…ôhalat u it…ômat. M…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô it…ômat net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u. Io en…®m…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s it…ômat, k…ôn mos-ir…ôk…®s it…ômat o n…ôtueint…ôn. K…ôn o nat u inu, net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, kotet…ôhau it…ômat.\f + \fr 15:19 \ft Jon 13:16; 17:14\f*  
\v 20 N…®kit…ômat ot…ôk…ôike mat…ôht n…ôghat…ôn u em…ôn-ip…®n…ô r…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIolw…ôk …ôm kit, t…ôsapr…ôk…®s-in…ôn r…ôhan et…ôm-iasol.‚Äô\f + \fr 15:20 \ft Jon 13:16\f* K…ôn m…ôto-inu net…ôm r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, ilat koatol t…ôrat ag…®n ron io, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, ilat okotol nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm et…ômat.\f + \fr 15:20 \ft 2 Tim 3:12\f* Ok…ôm…ô ilat k…ômotol r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn ilat okotol r…ôhat…ômat n…ôghat…ôn. M…ôto ilat k…ôm…ôsotol ag…®n-…ôh…ôn r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n.  
\v 21 Ilat okotol nat…®mnat m…®n nulan et…ômat, m…ôto-inun it…ômat r…ôhak m…®n net…ômim.\f + \fr 15:21 \ft Aes 66:5; Mat 5:10-12; 10:22; Luk 6:22-23; W…ôk 5:41; 1 Pita 4:14; Nol ∆èp…ôn 2:3\f* Ilat okotol n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu ilat kot…ôruru Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io.\f + \fr 15:21 \ft Jon 16:1-3\f*   
\p
\v 22 ‚ÄúEmuwa k…ôn m…ôghat k…ôm ilat. Tol n…ôhlan e noa n…ôghat…ôn u, ilat k…ômot…ôplan …ôsas r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat m…®n. M…ôto k…ômoat…ôuhlin m…ôntalat ron io moatap…ôs r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn. K…ôn roiu, kol k…ôsot…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat t…®k…ô.\f + \fr 15:22 \ft Jon 9:41; Rom 1:20; 2:1; Luk 11:31-32\f*\f + \fr 15:22 \ft Iesu t…®nuwa k…ôn mol …ôp r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat, k…ôn mol suat…®p o n…®k…®s…ôn ilat e t…ôfag…ô rat. M…ôto net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn kotet…ôhau m…ôm…ô Iesu tatol …ôp nol…ôn rat r…ôhalat. Tol n…ôhlan, ilat kotap…ôs in k…ôn moat…®t…ôpun napin…ôp…ôn mapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn (3:19-21; 9:39-41).\f*  
\v 23 Et…ômim it…ôm tet…ôhau io, in tet…ôhau m…®n r…ôhak Tata.  
\v 24 Emuwa mol w…ôk m…®n u e n…®gan…ômt…®lat it…ôm kol et…ôm p…®s…®n kit t…ôm…ôsol…ôn. Tol n…ôhlan, ilat k…ômot…®tun m…ôm…ô pah u io. K…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n k…ômot…®tun io, m…ôto koatet…ôhau io, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô koatet…ôhau m…®n r…ôhak Tata. K…ôn roiu, kol k…ôsot…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat t…®k…ô.\f + \fr 15:24 \ft Jon 5:36; Mat 11:20-24\f*  
\v 25 M…ôto nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh ot…ôk…ôike mol n…ôhlan, k…ôn mol m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn u otuwa pahrien it…ôm net…ôm aup…ôn k…ômot…ôte r…ôk…®s e naoa r…ôha Lou. R…ôhalat u Lou tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIo esol…ôn nat kit elat, m…ôto ilat kotet…ôhau ag…®n-…ôh io, moatol t…®m…ôht k…ôm io.‚Äô\f + \fr 15:25 \ft Sam 35:19; 69:4\f*   
\p
\v 26 ‚ÄúM…ôto nian Iasitu otuwa, in otat…ôn-iar…ôp io. Narm…®n r…ôha N…®pahrien…ôn u, tat…®s…®-p…ôn o Tata Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 15:26 \ft Jon 14:26\f* Io ekahl-ipa in tuwa ot…ômat.  
\v 27 K…ônu it…ômat m…®n, on…ôkot…ôk…ôike mot…ôn-iar…ôp io,\f + \fr 15:27 \ft Luk 24:48; Jon 21:24; 1 Jon 1:2; 4:14\f* m…ôto-inu it…ômat noatat…®g kitat min io e n…ôtuoun…ôn e w…ôk r…ôhak muwa m…ôtoarus-pa u-roiu.   
\c 16  
\m
\v 1 ‚ÄúIo enat…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn ot…ôseiuaiu…ôn.  
\v 2 Ilat ok…ôpanot…ôhg-iar…ôp it…ômat e nim…ô m…®n r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôhalat;\f + \fr 16:2 \ft Jon 9:22; 12:42\f* k…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n, nian …ôh-ik…®n tatuwa it…ôm net…ôm okotohamnu it…ômat, k…ôn n…®kilat t…ôht m…ôm…ô ilat koatol w…ôk w…®r kit r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 16:2 \ft W…ôk 26:9-10\f*  
\v 3 Ilat okotol nat…®mnat m…®n u, m…ôto-inun ilat kot…ôruru Tata Uhg…®n, k…ôn mot…ôruru m…®n io.\f + \fr 16:3 \ft Jon 15:21; 1 Jon 3:1\f*  
\v 4 M…ôto io ekaup…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat. K…ôn nian ilat k…®not…ôtuoun m…®natol et…ômat, k…ôn n…®kit…ômat otu…ôh m…ôm…ô io en…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat.‚Äù  
\s1 W…ôk m…®n it…ôm Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ôpanol  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôghat …ôh matuw…®n, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo em…ôs…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat aup…ôn, m…ôto-inu em…ôtat…®g kitat min it…ômat.  
\v 5 M…ôto roiu ek…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n o r…ôhak Tata it…ôm t…ômahl-ipa io, m…ôto it…ômat kit t…ôs…ôtap…ôh…ôn ron io m…ôm…ô, ‚Äò?Ik on…ôkuw…®n hi…ô?‚Äô  
\v 6 M…ôto roiu, tol nulan m…ôm…ô em…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat, k…ôn n…®kit…ômat t…ômahm…ô.  
\v 7 M…ôto io iat…ôn pahrien k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, ot…ôw…®r p…®k ot…ômat m…ôm…ô io ekag…®m t…ônin it…ômat. M…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô esag…®m t…ônin…ôn it…ômat, k…ôn Iasitu\f + \fr 16:7 \ft Jon 14:16\f* okol t…ôsuwam…ôn mat…®g it…ômat min. M…ôto ok…ôm…ô io ekag…®m, muw…®n, k…ôn io ekahl-ipa in tuwa m…ôtat…®g ot…ômat.\f + \fr 16:7 \ft Jon 7:39\f*  
\v 8 K…ôn nian in otuwa, k…ôn ot…ôg…ôtun net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat iol t…ôfag…ô rat, k…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat t…ôsahmen…ôn o nol…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat t…ôsahmen…ôn o nakil…ôn nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim.  
\v 9 Narm…®n u ot…ôg…ôtun ilat m…ôm…ô ilat iol t…ôfag…ô rat,\f + \fr 16:9 \ft Jon 15:22\f* m…ôto-inu k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lak.  
\v 10 Narm…®n u ot…ôg…ôtun k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat in t…ôsahmen…ôn o r…ôhalat n…ôtuat…®p…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 16:10 \ft Aes 64:5; Mat 5:20; Rom 1:17; 3:21,22; 10:3; Fil 3:6-9; Taet 3:5; 1 Pita 3:18\f* m…ôto-inu io ek…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n o r…ôhak Tata, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôsotehm…ôn io.  
\v 11 Narm…®n u ot…ôg…ôtun k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat in t…ôsahmen…ôn o nakil…ôn nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim, m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n in t…®nakil r…ôk…®s i…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, Setan.\f + \fr 16:11 \ft Jon 12:31\f*   
\p
\v 12 ‚ÄúIo iatos nat…®mnat tep…ôt m…®n …ôh-ik…®n m…ôm…ô epan…ôn k…ôm it…ômat. M…ôto roiu …ôh, okol n…ôsotos rafin…ôn ilat. Ilat koti…ôk…®s p…®k …ôh ot…ômat.\f + \fr 16:12 \ft Mak 4:33\f*  
\v 13 M…ôto nian Narm…®n r…ôha N…®pahrien…ôn otuwa,\f + \fr 16:13 \ft Jon 14:17\f* in otit it…ômat, tol m…ô it…ômat n…ôkot…®tun n…®pahrien…ôn rafin. In okol t…ôs…ôn at…®p…ôn r…ôhan …ôm n…ôghat…ôn. In ot…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn …ôm nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm in tat…ôto e Tata Uhg…®n. K…ôn in ot…ôn-iar…ôp…®n…ô m…®n k…ôm it…ômat nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm nian kit ok…ôpanotuwa.  
\v 14 In ot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn pahrien ron io k…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm it…ômat. E nol…ôn u, in ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr io.  
\v 15 Nat…®mnat m…®n rafin r…ôha Tata Uhg…®n, in r…ôhak.\f + \fr 16:15 \ft Jon 17:10\f* Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn io ekat…ôn m…ôm…ô, Narm…®n u, in ot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn pahrien ron io k…ôn matol …ôp n…®p…ôt…®n k…ôm it…ômat.‚Äù   
\s1 Ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn okot…ôplan m…®n Iesu  
\p
\v 16 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOt…ôsuw…ôh…ôn on…ôsot…ôplan…ôn io, m…ôto uaris…®g un, t…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, k…ôn on…ôpanot…ôplan m…®n io.‚Äù\f + \fr 16:16 \ft Jon 14:18\f*   
\p
\v 17 K…ôn net…ômim m…®n neen r…ôhan, ilat koat…ôtap…ôh-…ôtap…ôh k…ôm ilat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…ôghat…ôn u, n…®p…ôt…®n naka? In tat…ôn k…ôm itat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòOt…ôsuw…ôh…ôn on…ôsot…ôplan…ôn io, m…ôto uaris…®g, ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, n…ôpanot…ôplan m…®n io.‚Äô K…ôn in t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòM…ôto-inu io iakatuw…®n o Tata Uhg…®n.‚Äô  
\v 18 ?N…ôghat…ôn u, ‚Äòot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn‚Äô n…®p…ôt…®n naka? Kitat kot…ôruru n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh in tat…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn Iesu t…®n…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô ilat kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…ôtap…ôh-in nat kit ron, k…ôn in t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Tahro? Io em…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòOt…ôsuw…ôh…ôn it…ômat n…ôsot…ôplan…ôn io. M…ôto uaris…®g, t…ôsuw…ôh…ôn on…ôpanot…ôplan m…®n io.‚Äô ?K…ôn roiu nakot…ôtap…ôh ot…ômat m…®n o n…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn u?  
\v 20 N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, it…ômat n…®kit…ômat otahm…ô, it…ômat on…ôkotas…ôk p…®k,\f + \fr 16:20 \ft Mak 16:10\f* m…ôto n…ôtueint…ôn, n…®kin otagien. It…ômat on…ôkot…ôto t…ôrat p…®k ag…®n, m…ôto nahm…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat ot…ôuhlin-pa e nagien…ôn.\f + \fr 16:20 \ft Jon 20:20\f*  
\v 21 Nian ok…ôm…ô t…®nu…ôhk…®r m…ôm…ô p…ôtan kit otem…ôk, k…ôn in tat…ôto t…ôrat, m…ôto-inun t…®nol nian r…ôhan m…ôm…ô ot…ôto nahm…ô…ôn e n…®p…ôt…®n. M…ôto uaris…®g, ok…ôm…ô n…ôt…®n t…®naiir r…ôk…®s, k…ôn in n…®kin t…ôs…ôht m…®n…ôn nahm…ô…ôn …ôh. In n…®kin t…ôtagien p…®k m…ôto-inu n…ôt…®n t…®naiir-pa e n…ôtueint…ôn.  
\v 22 E nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, roiu …ôh it…ômat nakot…ôto t…ôrat. M…ôto uaris…®g, k…ônu io ek…ôplan m…®n it…ômat. K…ônu n…®kit…ômat otagien otagien, okol et…ômim kit t…ôsol m…®n…ôn it…ômat n…®kit…ômat tahm…ô m…®n.  
\v 23 O nian …ôh, it…ômat on…ôsot…ôtap…ôh-in m…®n…ôn nat kit ron io. N…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, ok…ôm…ô it…ômat nakot…ôtap…ôh-in nat kit o Tata Uhg…®n e n…ôrg…ôk, k…ôn in otos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat.\f + \fr 16:23 \ft Mat 7:7\f*  
\v 24 M…ôtoarus-pa u-roiu, it…ômat n…ôsot…ôtap…ôh-in…ôn …ôh nat kit ron e n…ôrg…ôk. Ot…ôtap…ôh-in e n…ôrg…ôk, k…ôn on…ôkotos, m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat otagien otagien m…ôrioah.‚Äù\f + \fr 16:24 \ft Jon 15:7-8\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…®nol win r…ôk…®s e nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn  
\p
\v 25 K…ôn Iesu tat…ôghat …ôh matuw…®n mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ematu…ôh nimaa n…ôghat…ôn e nat…®mnat m…®n u, mat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat.\f + \fr 16:25 \ft Mat 13:34; Mak 4:33,34; Jon 10:6\f* M…ôto nian …ôh-ik…®n tatuwa, it…ôm io ek…ôsu…ôh m…®n…ôn nimaa n…ôghat…ôn lan, m…ôto oek…ôghat-in r…ôhak Tata k…ôm it…ômat e nol…ôn kit it…ôm it…ômat on…ôkot…®tun w…®r in.  
\v 26 E nian …ôh, it…ômat on…ôkoteasi…ô-in nat…®mnat k…ôm r…ôhak Tata e n…ôrg…ôk, m…ôto io es…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô io ekuw…®n e n…ôrg…®t…ômat measi…ô-in nat…®mnat ron\f + \fr 16:26 \ft Kitat kot…®tun nuw…®n…ôn o Uhg…®n e n…ôfak…ôn, tahmen …ôm e n…®sualk…ôl…ôh koatuw…®n o r…ôhalat tata m…®n it…ôm kotolkeike ilat. Iesu in tat…ôfak o nat kiti…ôh …ôm, inun, m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôplan kitat m…ôm…ô kot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…®n (Rom 8:34, Hip 7:24-25; 1 Jon 2:1-2). K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, kitat kot…®tun nuw…®n…ôn measi…ô-in nat…®mnat o Uhg…®n.\f*  
\v 27 m…ôto-inu Tata Uhg…®n, in …ômun tolkeike p…®k it…ômat. In tolkeike it…ômat m…ôto-inu it…ômat nakotolkeike io, k…ôn it…ômat n…ômotahat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô io em…®s…®-p…ôn lan.  
\v 28 Io em…®s…®-p…ôn o Tata Uhg…®n, muwa e n…ôtueint…ôn u. K…ônu roiu ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn k…ôn ekiet m…®n e n…ôtueint…ôn u, m…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n o Tata Uhg…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 29 K…ôn net…ômim r…ôhan m…®n koat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!In un! !Roiu …ôh ik n…ôsu…ôh m…®n…ôn nimaa n…ôghat…ôn! Ik nakat…ôn …ôtuat…®p …ôm k…ôm it…®mat.  
\v 30 Roiu …ôh enot…®tun m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô suah kit t…ôs…ôtap…ôh-in…ôn …ôh nat kit ron ik, m…ôto ik n…ôk…®tun nuhalp…®n…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n rafin it…ôm k…ôs…ôtap…ôhin…ôn …ôh. O nat u, tol k…ôn it…®mat ekot…®tun m…ôm…ô ik n…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn o Uhg…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 31 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…®pahrien…ôn, it…ômat nakotahat…ôt…ô lak u-roiu?\f + \fr 16:31 \ft Jon 4:23\f*  
\v 32 It…ômat ot…ôt…ôl…®g-in-tu, nian …ôh-ik…®n tatuwa, n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô nian …ôh t…®niet-ar…ôpa r…ôk…®s, it…ôm net…ômim okot…®t…ôp it…ômat rafin, nakotaiu atit, motuw…®n imat…ômat m…®n ik…®n, motap…ôs io, io p…®s…®n …ôm.\f + \fr 16:32 \ft Sek 13:7; Mat 26:56; Mak 14:27\f* M…ôto okol io esan p…®s…®n …ôm…ôn, m…ôto-inu nian rafin r…ôhak Tata t…ôtat…®g it…®mlau min.\f + \fr 16:32 \ft Jon 8:29\f*  
\v 33 Io en…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn oteiuaiu m…ôto-inu n…ôkotat…®g lak.\f + \fr 16:33 \ft Jon 14:27\f* E n…ôtueint…ôn u, nahm…ô…ôn otep…ôt ot…ômat,\f + \fr 16:33 \ft Jon 15:18-21\f* m…ôto sot…ôg…®n…ôn, mot…ôtul m…ôha-m…ôha,\f + \fr 16:33 \ft Mak 13:9\f* m…ôto-inu io enol win r…ôk…®s e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 16:33 \ft Rom 8:37; 1 Jon 4:4; 5:4; Nol ∆èp…ôn 2:7,11,17,26; 3:5,12,21; 21:7\f*   
\c 17  
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôfak at…®p ron  
\m
\v 1 Nian Iesu t…ôm…ôghat r…ôk…®s, k…ôn m…ôtag-p…ôr il…®s e neai, k…ôn mat…ôfak mat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\p ‚ÄúTata, r…ôhak nian t…®nuwa r…ôk…®s. Io iakolkeike m…ôm…ô ik onak…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® N…ôt…®m, m…ôm…ô in m…®n ot…ôpan…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…ôm,\f + \fr 17:1 \ft Jon 12:23; 13:31,32\f*  
\v 2 m…ôto-inu ik n…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn ne nep…ôt…ôn k…ôm in, m…ôm…ô in ot…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e net…ômim rafin,\f + \fr 17:2 \ft Dan 7:14; Mat 28:18; 1 Korin 15:27-28\f* k…ôn m…®tun m…®n nos-ip…ôn…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n k…ôm ilat m…®n u, it…ôm ik n…ômos-ip…ôn ilat m…®n k…ôm in.\f + \fr 17:2 \ft 17:24; Jon 6:37,39\f*  
\v 3 K…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n u, n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…®tun ik, it…ôm ik …ôm un ik Uhg…®n pahrien,\f + \fr 17:3 \ft Jon 17:25,26\f* k…ôn mot…®tun m…®n Iesu Kristo u, ik n…ômahl-ipa.\f + \fr 17:3 \ft Fil 3:8\f*  
\v 4 Io emat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…ôm e n…ôtueint…ôn u,\f + \fr 17:4 \ft Jon 13:31\f* k…ôn enol rafin r…ôk…®s w…ôk it…ôm ik n…ômos-ipa k…ôm io m…ôm…ô iakol.\f + \fr 17:4 \ft Jon 19:30\f*  
\v 5 Tata, roiu …ôh, t…®nol nian r…ôham m…ôm…ô onakos io ek…®mn…ô m…ôtat…®g kilau min ik. L…ôs-ip…ôr io mos-ipa nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag k…ôm io, tahmen …ôm m…ô inun, emos aup…ôn kilau min ik e nian n…ôtueint…ôn u t…ômat…®k…ô …ôh.\f + \fr 17:5 \ft Jon 1:1-2; 8:58; 16:28; Fil 2:6-11\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôfak o r…ôhan m…®n  
\p
\v 6 ‚ÄúNet…ôm m…®n u it…ôm ik n…ômos-ir…ôk…®s ilat o n…ôtueint…ôn mos-ipa ilat k…ôm io, io ematol …ôp n…ôrg…ôm k…ôm ilat, m…ôm…ô ilat okot…®tun ik.\f + \fr 17:6 \ft Jon 1:18\f* Aup…ôn, ilat r…ôham m…®n net…ômim, m…ôto roiu ik n…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn ilat e nelm…ôk, m…ôm…ô ilat r…ôhak m…®n net…ômim. Ilat k…ômoat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn r…ôham n…ôghat…ôn,  
\v 7 k…ôn roiu …ôh, ilat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô, nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm ik n…ômos-ipa k…ôm io, ilat koat…®s…®-p…ôn …ôm ron ik.  
\v 8 Ilat kot…®tun nat…®mnat m…®n u, m…ôto-inu ik n…®n…ôm…ôn-ipa r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm io, k…ôn io em…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat, k…ôn ilat koatos e n…®kilat. K…ôn ilat mot…®tun m…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n m…ôm…ô io em…®s…®-p…®n…ô ron ik, k…ôn moatahat…ôt…ô lak m…ôm…ô ik n…ômahl-ipa io.   
\p
\v 9 ‚ÄúIo iat…ôfak olat m…®n u. Io es…ôfak…ôn o net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, iat…ôfak …ôm o net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm ik n…ômos-ipa ilat k…ôm io, m…ôto-inun ilat u r…ôham m…®n.  
\v 10 Net…ôm m…®n u iatos, ilat rafin r…ôham, k…ônu ilat rafin u it…ôm ik natos, ilat r…ôhak.\f + \fr 17:10 \ft Jon 16:15\f* K…ôn net…ôm m…®n u, ik n…ômol ilat m…ôm…ô n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat tat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…ôk.  
\v 11 Roiu …ôh iakatuwa ron ik, k…ôn ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn io esat…®g…ôn u e n…ôtueint…ôn u. M…ôto net…ôm m…®n u, ilat okotat…®g …ôh e n…ôtueint…ôn u. Tata, ik nak…ôtuat…®p ag…®n. Awi, nakask…ôl…®m net…ôm m…®n u kotat…®g w…®r e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha n…ôrg…ôm u it…ôm ik n…ômos-ipa k…ôm io, m…ôm…ô ilat okotat…®g kiti…ôh …ôm, tahmen m…ôm…ô inu, kilau min ik kiti…ôh.\f + \fr 17:11 \ft Jon 17:21-23; Sam 133:1; Jon 10:30\f*  
\v 12 Nian io em…ôtat…®g it…®mat min ilat, k…ôn emat…®pal w…®r\f + \fr 17:12 \ft ‚ÄúEmat…®pal w…®r,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n u, ematehm w…®r m…ôm…ô nat kit t…ôs…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn, mol protektem elat.\f* olat, e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha n…ôrg…ôm …ôm it…ôm ik n…ômos-ipa k…ôm io. Io ematehm w…®r ilat, esaiiroauin…ôn kit.\f + \fr 17:12 \ft Jon 6:39\f* Kiti…ôh …ôm u it…ôm t…ôm…ôlue, inun it…ôm Uhg…®n ot…ôk…ôike m…ôr…ôk…®n,\f + \fr 17:12 \ft Inu Jutas. Jon 6:70,71\f* k…ônu nat …ôh otol n…ôhlan, m…ôm…ô otol n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n otuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn.   
\p
\v 13 ‚ÄúRoiu …ôh, iatuwa ron ik, m…ôto iat…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u nian etat…®g …ôh e n…ôtueint…ôn, m…ôm…ô ilat m…®n, n…®kilat otagien otagien, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô io n…®kik t…ôtagien.  
\v 14 Io em…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôham n…ôghat…ôn m…®n k…ôm ilat. K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, k…ôsotolkeike…ôn ilat, koatet…ôhau ilat,\f + \fr 17:14 \ft Jon 8:23; 15:19\f* m…ôto-inun ilat s…ôn…ôm…ô net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn,\f + \fr 17:14 \ft 1 Pita 2:11\f* tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô io s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn.  
\v 15 Io es…ôtap…ôh…ôn ron ik m…ôm…ô onakos-ir…ôk…®s ilat e n…ôtueint…ôn u. M…ôto ekolkeike m…ôm…ô ik onakahtos…®g-in et…ôm rat u, Setan, m…ôm…ô in ot…ôsuwam…ôn m…ôr…ôk…®n ilat. Ik onak…®pal w…®r\f + \fr 17:15 \ft ‚ÄúOnak…®pal w…®r,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n u, otehm w…®r m…ôm…ô nat kit t…ôs…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn, mol protektem elat.\f* olat.\f + \fr 17:15 \ft Mat 24:24; Jon 8:44; 1 Pita 5:8\f*  
\v 16 Io, s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u. K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, ilat m…®n s…ôn…ôm…ô net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn.  
\v 17 R…ôham n…ôghat…ôn in n…®pahrien…ôn rafin. On…ôkol r…ôham n…ôghat…ôn m…ôm…ô in otol w…ôk e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat m…ôm…ô ilat net…ômim pahrien r…ôham motasim mot…ôtuat…®p.\f + \fr 17:17 \ft Lev 11:44-45; Jon 15:3; 1 Pita 1:16\f*  
\v 18 Ik n…ômahl-ipa io, ekuwa e n…ôtueint…ôn u,\f + \fr 17:18 \ft Jon 3:17\f* k…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, io enatahl-iar…ôp m…®n ilat, kotuw…®n e n…ôtueint…ôn.\f + \fr 17:18 \ft Jon 20:21; Mat 28:18-20\f*  
\v 19 K…ôn io iatos-ip…®n…ô at…®p io m…ôm…ô iakatasim o nol…ôn nalp…ôkau…ôn r…ôham,\f + \fr 17:19 \ft Mak 14:24; Luk 22:19; Jon 6:51; 1 Kor 11:24; Dut 15:19,21; Taetas 2:14; Hip 9:14\f* m…ôm…ô ekasitu e net…ôm m…®n u, m…ôm…ô ilat m…®n okotasim mot…ôtuat…®p, k…ôn ilat net…ômim pahrien r…ôham.\f + \fr 17:19 \ft Hip 10:10\f*   
\s1 Iesu t…ôm…ôfak o net…ôm ok…ôpanotahat…ôt…ô lan  
\p
\v 20 ‚ÄúIo es…ôfak…ôn …ôm o net…ôm m…®n u, m…ôto iat…ôfak m…®n o net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm ok…ôpanotahat…ôt…ô lak e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm m…®n u.  
\v 21 Tata, io iat…ôfak olat, m…ôm…ô ilat rafin okotuwa kiti…ôh …ôm, tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô inun kilau kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn iak…ôtat…®g-p…®n…ô lam, k…ôn ik n…ôk…ôtat…®g lak. Iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô ilat okotuwa kiti…ôh …ôm kitat min ik, m…ôm…ô net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn okotahat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô ik n…ômahl-ipa io.\f + \fr 17:21 \ft Jon 3:17\f*  
\v 22 Ik n…®n…ômos-ipa r…ôk…®s nep…ôt…ôn\f + \fr 17:22 \ft Jon 1:14\f* k…ôm io, k…ôn io iatawte-in k…ôl…ôh nep…ôt…ôn r…ôhak k…ôm ilat, m…ôm…ô ilat okotuwa kiti…ôh …ôm tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô kilau k…ôtioal kiti…ôh.\f + \fr 17:22 \ft Jon 14:20\f*  
\v 23 Iak…ôtat…®g e n…®kilat, k…ôn ik n…ôk…ôtat…®g lak. Tol n…ôhlan, iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô, ilat okotuwa kiti…ôh …ôm e nat…®mnat m…®n rafin m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, ilat okot…ôplan mot…®tun m…ôm…ô ik n…ômahl-ipa io, k…ôn m…ôm…ô ik n…ômolkeike r…ôham net…ômim\f + \fr 17:23 \ft Jon 16:27\f* tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inu, ik n…ômolkeike mihin io.   
\p
\v 24 ‚ÄúTata, ik n…ômos-ipa ilat u e nelm…ôk m…ôm…ô ilat r…ôhak m…®n, k…ôn io ekolkeike m…ôm…ô ilat okot…®tun nuwam…ôn ik…®n-u it…ôm io m…®n ekuw…®n ik…®n,\f + \fr 17:24 \ft Jon 12:26\f* m…ôm…ô ilat okot…ôplan nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag r…ôhak\f + \fr 17:24 \ft Net…ôm koat…ôfak koatehm nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha Iesu m…ôs…®n …ôm roiu, (Jon 1:14, 2 Kor 3:18). M…ôto kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô ot…®t…ôl…®g-pa, kitat okotahmen lan, m…ôto-inu e nian …ôh, okot…ôplan …ôsas r…ôhan nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag e n…®gan…ômt…®tat (1 Jon 3:2). Nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag r…ôha Iesu it…ôm r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n ilat okot…ôplan; inu, r…ôhan nep…ôt…ôn m…ôm…ô in Uhg…®n, nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag …ôh it…ôm in t…ômos aup…ôn n…ôtueint…ôn t…ôpanat…®g.\f* it…ôm io ekatos. Nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag u, ik n…ômos-ipa k…ôm io, m…ôto-inu ik n…ômolkeike io aup…ôn ag…®n nian n…ôtueint…ôn u t…ômat…®k…ô …ôh.\f + \fr 17:24 \ft Jon 1:1-3; 1:14; 1 Pita 1:20\f*   
\p
\v 25 ‚ÄúTata, ik nak…ôtuat…®p ag…®n.\f + \fr 17:25 \ft Sam 119:137; Rom 3:26\f* Net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, ilat kot…ôruru ik,\f + \fr 17:25 \ft Jon 15:21; 16:3\f* m…ôto io ek…®tun ik. K…ôn net…ôm m…®n u r…ôhak m…®n, ilat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô ik n…ômahl-ipa io.  
\v 26 Io emol …ôp ik k…ôm ilat, m…ôm…ô ilat okot…®tun w…®r ik,\f + \fr 17:26 \ft Jon 17:6\f* k…ônu io, oiakat…ôk…ôike matol …ôp ik n…ôhlan, m…ôm…ô nolkeike…ôn r…ôham ot…®n…®p w…®r n…®kilat,\f + \fr 17:26 \ft E ves u, n…®p…ôt…®n k…ôiu. Kiti…ôh, Iesu tat…ôfak m…ôm…ô Tata Uhg…®n otolkeike r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô in tatolkeike Iesu. M…ôto in tat…ôfak m…®n m…ôm…ô r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n okotolkeike ilat m…®n tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô Tata Uhg…®n in tatolkeike Iesu.\f* k…ôn m…ôm…ô io at…®p oiak…ôtat…®g e n…®kilat. Nolkeike…ôn u iakat…ôghat-in, in nolkeike…ôn r…ôham, tahmen m…ô inu ik nakolkeike mihin io.‚Äù\f + \fr 17:26 \ft Jon 15:9; Rom 5:5\f*   
\c 18  
\s1 T…®k…®m…®r m…®n r…ôha Iesu k…ômotuwa motask…ôl…®m in  
\r (Mat 26:7-56; Mak 14:43-50;  //  Luk 21:47-53)  
\m
\v 1 Nian Iesu t…ômaup…ôn m…ôfak, k…ômotiet e taon u, k…ôn motegu…ôf…®m…®n-p…ôn ent…ôn…®p…ôn-p…ôn e noanapinat kit, n…ôrg…®n un, Ketron. K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, k…ômahw…®nu kit ik…®n. K…ôn Iesu ne r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n k…ômotuw…®n e n…®ki n…®g m…®n …ôh.   
\p
\v 2 K…ôn Jutas u, et…ôm u uaris…®g in ot…ôpaneg…ôhan-in Iesu k…ôm r…ôhan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n, in t…®n…®tun r…ôk…®s ik…®n …ôh, m…ôto-inu nian neen, Iesu ne r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim ilat koatu…ôf…®m…®n ilat m…®n ik…®n.\f + \fr 18:2 \ft Luk 21:37; 22:39\f*  
\v 3 K…ôn pris asol m…®n ne Farisi m…®n k…ômotahl-ip…ôn mopael m…®n it…ôm koat…ôtul o Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n kotuwa motehm Jutas. K…ôn Jutas t…ômit net…ôm m…®n …ôh ilat mopael m…®n neen r…ôha net…ôm Rom, mit ilat motuw…®n e n…®ki n…®g ol…®f …ôh. Ilat koat…ôm…®k noan…®si…ô, ne lait m…®n, ne nat…®mnat r…ôha n…ôluag…®n…ôn.\f + \fr 18:3 \ft W…ôk 1:16\f*   
\p
\v 4 Iesu t…®n…ôm…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat m…®n u, in otuwa tol nulan, m…ôto in t…ômaliw…ôk muw…®n olat, k…ôn m…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?It…ômat noateg…ôs-in pah un?‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 Ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm Nasaret kit, n…ôrg…®n u Iesu.‚Äù K…ôn in t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u inu.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:5 \ft ‚ÄúIo u inu‚Äù - ∆èplan-tu futnot e Jon 4:26.\f* \f + \fr 18:5 \ft Jon 6:20; 8:24,28,58; 13:19; 8:6,8\f* (K…ôn Jutas, suah u it…ôm t…ômeg…ôhan-in-p…ôn Iesu e nelm…®lat, in tat…ôtul ilat min.)  
\v 6 K…ôn nian Iesu t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u inu,‚Äù ilat k…ômotani m…ôntaalat mot…®t…ôl…®g, moteiuaiu motorin ilat e n…®s…®p.\f + \fr 18:6 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:17\f*   
\p
\v 7 K…ôn Iesu tat…®g m…ôtap…ôh m…®n olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?It…ômat nakoteg…ôs-in pah un?‚Äù K…ôn ilat kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm Nasaret kit, n…ôrg…®n u Iesu.‚Äù   
\p
\v 8 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEn…ôn-ip…®n…ô r…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIo u inu.‚Äô\f + \fr 18:8 \ft ‚ÄúIo u inu‚Äù - ∆èplan-tu futnot e Jon 4:26.\f* \f + \fr 18:8 \ft Jon 6:20; 8:24,28,58; 13:19; 8:6,8\f* Ok…ôm…ô it…ômat nakoateg…ôs-in io, k…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nakotap…ôs net…ômim m…®n u, koatuw…®n latu…ônu.‚Äù  
\v 9 In t…ôm…ôn n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn u it…ôm in t…®n…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s in otol n…®pahrien…ôn. N…ôghat…ôn u t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúTata, net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm n…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn ilat e nelm…ôk, okol esaiiroauin…ôn kit.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:9 \ft Jon 6:39; 10:28; 17:12\f*   
\p
\v 10 Saimon Pita t…ômat…®l…ôs r…ôhan kit nisa r…ôha n…ôluag…®n…ôn. K…ôn …ômun, in t…ômiuw-iar…ôp r…ôhan nisa, m…ôte r…ôk…®s matelg…® slef kit r…ôha pris asol ag…®n, mat…ôlg…®n mat…®p. N…ôrg…® suah un, Malkas.   
\p
\v 11 M…ôto Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Pita m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúAii-p…ôn r…ôham nisa u e r…ôhan sipa. Ik on…ôk…ôike m…®tun m…ôm…ô nahm…ô…ôn u r…ôhak,\f + \fr 18:11 \ft Nian Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk on…ôk…ôike m…®tun m…ôm…ô nahm…ô…ôn u r…ôhak,‚Äù n…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Oes…ôn…®m-p…ôn…ôn e pan…®k…®n u it…ôm r…ôhak Tata otos-ipa k…ôm io?‚Äù E n…ôghat…ôn Kris, ‚Äúoek…ôn…®m e pan…®k…®n‚Äù in nimaa n…ôghat…ôn, n…®p…ôt…®n u, m…ôm…ô Iesu tateg…ôhan-in m…ôm…ô in otos nahm…ô…ôn u it…ôm otuwa ron nian Uhg…®n otol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm in o nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôha net…ômim rafin.\f* it…ôm Tata Uhg…®n in t…ômos-ipa k…ôm io, k…ôn io ek…ôike m…ôt…ôl…®g-in …ôm, mol.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:11 \ft Mat 20:22\f*   
\s1 Ilat k…ômot…®l…ôs Iesu motuw…®n t…ôtul aup…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…® Anas  
\r (Mat 26:57-58; Mak 14:53-54;  //  Luk 22:54)  
\p
\v 12 K…ôn mopael m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Rom ne et…ôm-iasol r…ôhalat, ne mopael m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, k…ômotask…ôl…®m Iesu, k…ôn mot…ôlis …ôtain nelm…®n.  
\v 13 K…ôn k…ômotaup…ôn mot…®l…ôs in motuw…®n t…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…® Anas. Anas un, in et…ômaa Kaeafas. Kaeafas un, in pris asol ag…®n e nup …ôh.\f + \fr 18:13 \ft E nian r…ôha Oltesteman, katos-ip…ôr pris asol ag…®n m…®n kot…ôtul m…ôtoarus nian ilat okoat…®m…®s. M…ôto e nian Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa u lan, net…ôm Rom k…ômot…ôuhlin n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn …ôh, motol m…ôm…ô et…ôm tatol pris asol ag…®n, ok…ôike kat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…®tain, m…ôm…ô suah kit in ot…ôs…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn nian t…ôf…ôm…ôh. E nup 6 AD, net…ôm Rom k…ômotos-ip…ôr Anas m…ôm…ô in otuwa pris asol ag…®n, k…ônu e nup 15 AD, k…ômot…®l…ôs-i…ôhau in e r…ôhan w…ôk, k…ôn mot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr Kai…ôf…ôs m…ôm…ô tatos n…ômeen. M…ôto Anas in tatos …ôh n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, k…ôn net…ôm Isrel koat…ôn …ôh m…ôm…ô in pris asol ag…®n.\f*  
\v 14 K…ôn Kaeafas u inu, in aup…ôn t…ôm…ôn k…ôm net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel m…ôm…ô t…ôw…®r p…®k m…ôm…ô et…ômim kiti…ôh …ôm ot…®m…®s o net…ômim, tapr…ôk…®s-in m…ôm…ô net…ômim rafin okot…®m…®s.\f + \fr 18:14 \ft Jon 11:49-51\f*   
\s1 Pita t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô in  //  t…ôruru Iesu  
\r (Mat 26:69-70; Mak 14:66-68;  //  Luk 22:55-57)  
\p
\v 15 K…ôn Saimon Pita ne et…ômim kit m…®n r…ôha Iesu, ilau k…ômiauaris…®g-in Iesu. Et…ômim u kit m…®n r…ôha Iesu, pris asol ag…®n in t…®tun w…®r. Tol n…ôhlan, in t…ôm…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Iesu, mian …ôp…ôh im…ô e iat r…ôha nim…ô r…ôha pris asol ag…®n un.  
\v 16 M…ôto Pita in t…ômat…ôtul …ôm e ket. K…ôn et…ômim kit m…®n u r…ôha Iesu, it…ôm pris asol ag…®n t…®tun w…®r, in t…ômiet muwa ihlu…ô, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm p…ôtan u it…ôm tat…ôtul o ket. K…ôn in t…ômit Pita mian im…ô.  
\v 17 K…ôn …ômun, p…ôtan un it…ôm tat…ôtul o ket, t…ôm…ôplan Pita k…ôn t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ei, ik m…®n un et…ômim r…ôha suah …ôh?‚Äù  
\p M…ôto Pita t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôp…ô, s…ôn…ôm…ô io r…ôhan et…ômim.‚Äù   
\p
\v 18 K…ôn e nian …ôh, in nian r…ôha n…ôt…ôp…ôn, k…ôn iolw…ôk m…®n r…ôha pris asol ag…®n, ne mopael m…®n, ilat k…ômotasiep…ôn e noan…ômk…®l…®p e n…®g…ôm, k…ôn moat…ôtul t…®t…ôlau in, moat…ôto. K…ôn Pita m…®n, in t…ômuw…®n mot…ôtul, moat…ôto n…®g…ôm.   
\s1 Pris asol ag…®n t…ôm…ôghat  //  k…ôm Iesu  
\r (Mat 26:59-66; Mak 14:55-64;  //  Luk 22:66-71)  
\p
\v 19 K…ôn pris asol ag…®n tat…ôtap…ôh-in nat…®mnat m…®n o Iesu. Tat…ôtap…ôh o net…ômim m…®n r…ôhan ne n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhan it…ôm t…ômat…ôn mat…ôg…ôtun ilat lan.\f + \fr 18:19 \ft Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô Kai…ôf…ôs in pris asol ag…®n e nup …ôh (ves 13), m…ôto Anas in tatos …ôh nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha pris asol ag…®n kit, m…ôto-inu in pris asol ag…®n aup…ôn ik…®n. K…ôn ves u tat…ôghat-in Anas. (Jon 18:24; Luk 3:2; W…ôk 4:5-6).\f*   
\p
\v 20 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo emat…ôn r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim. Nian rafin, iat…ôg…ôtun net…ômim lan, …ôp…ôh e nim…ô m…®n r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn, k…ôn …ôp…ôh e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ôm net…ôm Isrel koat…ôp…ôl…ôh ik…®n nian rafin. Io es…ôhluaig-in…ôn r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n.  
\v 21 ?T…ôhrol nak…ôtap…ôh-in nulan k…ôm io? T…ôw…®r m…ô nakuw…®n m…ôtap…ôh o net…ôm k…ômoat…ôto r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n. T…ôw…®r nakuw…®n m…ôtap…ôh o n…ôghat…ôn m…®n un em…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat. Ilat kot…®tun w…®r nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm emat…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 Nian Iesu t…ômat…ôn n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ôn mopael kit it…ôm in tat…ôtul e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, in tat…ôtul …ôh-ik…®n, t…ômem n…®kap…®n, k…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Nakat…ôn nulan e pris asol ag…®n o naka?‚Äù   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô em…ôn n…ôghat…ôn neen it…ôm t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô onak…ôn-iar…ôp. ?M…ôto ok…ôm…ô r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n kot…ôtuat…®p …ôm, t…ôhrol nakatem io?‚Äù   
\p
\v 24 K…ôn …ômun Anas tahl-ip…ôn Iesu tuw…®n o pris asol ag…®n u Kaeafas. K…ôn tat…ôm…®k m…ôtm…ôt…®g …ôm nol it…ôm k…ôm…ôlis lan.   
\s1 Pita t…®n…ôn m…®n m…ôm…ô  //  t…ôruru Iesu  
\r (Mat 26:71-75; Mak 14:69-72;  //  Luk 22:58-62)  
\p
\v 25 K…ôn Saimon Pita t…ôtul …ôh mat…ôto n…®g…ôm. K…ôn koat…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ei, ik m…®n un, ik et…ômim r…ôha suah …ôh?‚Äù M…ôto Pita t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôp…ô, s…ôn…ôm…ô io r…ôhan et…ômim.‚Äù   
\p
\v 26 K…ôn …ômun, iolw…ôk kit r…ôha pris asol ag…®n, in noanol kit r…ôha suah u Pita t…ôm…ôtat…®p mat…ôlg…®n aup…ôn, in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…®kik t…ôht m…ôm…ô em…ôplan ik it…ômat min …ôp…ôh e n…®ki nahw…®nu…ôn, o k…ôp…ô?‚Äù   
\p
\v 27 M…ôto Pita t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôp…ô. S…ôn…ôm…ô io.‚Äù  
\p K…ôn roiu ag…®n-…ôh m…®n, m…ôn…®g kit t…®mn…ôn.\f + \fr 18:27 \ft Jon 13:38\f*   
\s1 Iesu in t…ôm…ôtul aup…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…® Pailat  
\r (Mat 27:1-2, 11-14; Mak 15:1-5;  //  Luk 23:1-5)  
\p
\v 28 K…ôn laulaug…®n ag…®n-…ôh, k…ômot…®l…ôs Iesu motiet e nim…ô r…ôha Kaeafas, motuw…®n e nim…ô r…ôha Pailat. Pailat in et…ôm Rom, m…ôto in tatos n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn asol Isrel. Net…ôm Isrel koatos n…ôtuak…ôm…ôn kit r…ôhalat, ilat k…ôsotuw…®n…ôn e nim…ô r…ôha et…ôm ik p…®s…®n kit. Ok…ôm…ô okotuw…®n im…ô, k…ôn ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat kotamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn ilat okol k…ôsotun…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn.\f + \fr 18:28 \ft Jon 11:55\f*  
\v 29 O n…ôtuak…ôm…ôn u r…ôhalat, tol k…ôn Pailat in t…ômiet e r…ôhan nim…ô, muwa ihlu…ô m…ô ot…ôplan ilat. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…®p…ôgn…ômt…® naka un it…ômat noatehm-p…ôn e suah u?‚Äù   
\p
\v 30 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô suah u in t…ôs…ôtg…ôhl…ôn lou, okol esot…®l…ôs…ôn in motuwa k…ôm ik.‚Äù   
\p
\v 31 K…ôn Pailat t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúT…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkot…®l…ôs in motuw…®n, k…ôn it…ômat motakil, t…ôt…ôu-p…ôn lou m…®n r…ôhat…ômat.‚Äù  
\p M…ôto ilat kot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúM…ôto net…ôm Rom …ôm ilat koteg…ôhan-in m…ôm…ô k…®tun nohamnu…ôn et…ômim.‚Äù  
\v 32 Iesu t…ômat…ôn aup…ôn m…ôm…ô in ot…®m…®s n…ôhlan,\f + \fr 18:32 \ft Iesu t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô in ot…®m…®s e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau (Mat 20:19; 26:2; Jon 3:14; 8:28; 12:32-33). K…ôn net…ôm Rom, ilat koatohamnu net…ôm koatol n…ôrat…ôn, moat…ôtu-p…ôr ilat e n…®g k…ôluau. M…ôto net…ôm Rom k…ôsoteg…ôhan-in…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ôm Isrel, ilat kotol mihin.\f* k…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ômol m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u r…ôhan okotuwa motol n…®pahrien…ôn.   
\p
\v 33 K…ôn …ômun Pailat tuw…®n m…®n im…ô, k…ôn maun-in Iesu tuwa m…ôtul aup…ôn-in n…®gan…ômt…®n, k…ôn t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? ?Ik kig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel?‚Äù\f + \fr 18:33 \ft Mat 2:2; Luk 23:2-3\f*   
\p
\v 34 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik at…®p …ôm nakat…ôtap…ôh nulan, o ik nakat…ôtap…ôh m…ôto-inu net…ômim koat…ôn-ip…®n…ô io k…ôm ik?‚Äù   
\p
\v 35 K…ôn Pailat t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol? ?Ik n…®kim t…ôht m…ô io et…ôm Isrel kit? Net…ômim imam ik…®n …ôm ne pris asol m…®n r…ôham, ilat k…ômoteg…ôhan-in-pa ik e nelm…ôk. ?Ik n…ômol nat naka?‚Äù   
\p
\v 36 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo, esol…ôn kig r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u. Ok…ôm…ô io kig kit tahmen e kig m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, k…ôn r…ôhak net…ômim m…®n okot…ômou, motoh net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okotos-ip…ôn io e nelm…® net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. M…ôto io s…ôn…ôm…ô kig kit r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:36 \ft Luk 17:21; Jon 6:51\f*   
\p
\v 37 K…ôn Pailat t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôto n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô ik kig kit?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk n…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô io kig kit. Io emaiir-pa e n…ôtueint…ôn u o nat kiti…ôh …ôm, m…ôm…ô ekat…ôtul-ar…ôp mat…ôn-iar…ôp n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 18:37 \ft Jon 3:32\f* K…ôn et…ômim it…ôm n…®kin tagien m…ôm…ô ot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn, k…ôn in tat…ôt…ôl…®g-in r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:37 \ft Jon 8:47\f*   
\p
\v 38 M…ôto Pailat t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Naka un, n…®pahrien…ôn?‚Äù  
\s1 Pailat t…ômakil m…ôm…ô Iesu in t…ôike m…®m…®s  
\r (Mat 27:15-31; Mak 15:6-20;  //  Luk 23:13-25)  
\p K…ôn Pailat t…ômiet m…®n muw…®n mehm net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo es…ôplan…ôn nol…ôn rat kit ne e suah u, it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô suah u t…ôm…ôr…ôk…®n lou.\f + \fr 18:38 \ft Luk 23:4\f*  
\v 39 Meto e nol…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, e nian r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, nian rafin iat…®k…®s suah kit mahl-iar…ôp…ôn e kalapus. ?K…ôn t…ôhrol? ?It…ômat nakotolkeike m…ôm…ô io ekeg…ôhan-in k…ôn m…®k…®s kig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel?‚Äù   
\p
\v 40 K…ôn ilat kotag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!K…ôp…ô! !It…®mat ekotap…ôs suah un, ekototolkeike Parapas!‚Äù Parapas un, in iakl…ôh kit, k…ôn in t…ômat…ôluag…®n matohamnu it…ôm m…ôm…ô ot…ôhg-iar…ôp kapman r…ôha Rom.\f + \fr 18:40 \ft W…ôk 3:14\f*   
\c 19  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn Pailat t…ômos-ip…ôn Iesu e nelm…® r…ôhan mopael m…®n, k…ôn ilat k…ômotalis-alis.\f + \fr 19:1 \ft Aes 50:6; 53:5\f*  
\v 2 K…ôn k…ômot…ôm…®k nol it…ôm tol nihl…ôn-nihl…ôn, motol hat lan, tahmen e hat r…ôha kig, k…ôn mot…ôfauin-p…ôn e r…ôhn-kap…ô. K…ôn motuw…®n-in-p…ôn kot …ôf…ôm…ôh kit k…ôm in, tol n…ôgu…®-naris lan, tahmen e kot r…ôha kig.  
\v 3 K…ôn ilat motuwa ron, moatol m…®l…ôh lan, k…ôn moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk u inu, kig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. It…®mat ekotos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn k…ôm ik.‚Äù K…ôn ilat moatem-p…ôn …ôm n…®kap…®n.   
\p
\v 4 K…ôn Pailat tiet m…®n muw…®n ihlu…ô, k…ôn mat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEi, net…ômim. Io ekahl-iar…ôp m…®n suah u tuwa ihlu…ô, m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkot…ôplan-tu m…ôm…ô io esehm…ôn nol…ôn rat lan ne.‚Äù  
\v 5 K…ôn Iesu t…ômiet m…®n muwa ihlu…ô. In tat…ôfauin hat u it…ôm k…ômol e nol it…ôm tol nihl…ôn-nihl…ôn, tahmen e hat r…ôha kig, k…ôn matuw…®n e kot …ôf…ôm…ôh tol n…ôgu…®-naris, tahmen e kot r…ôha kig, k…ôn Pailat t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Net…ômim! !Ot…ôplan-tu! !Suah u inu!‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 M…ôto nian pris asol m…®n ne mopael m…®n it…ôm koatehm Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n k…ômot…ôplan, ilat k…ômotag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ok…ôht-ip…ôn e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau! !Ok…ôht-ip…ôn e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau!‚Äù\f + \fr 19:6 \ft W…ôk 3:13\f*  
\p K…ôn Pailat t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ôla, it…ômat p…®s…®n …ôm, ot…®l…ôs motuw…®n, mot…ôht-ip…ôn in e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau. M…ôto io es…ôplan…ôn nol…ôn rat kit ne lan.‚Äù   
\p
\v 7 M…ôto ilat kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúR…ôhat…®mat kit …ôh-ik…®n lou tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in ot…ôk…ôike m…®m…®s, m…ôto-inu in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 19:7 \ft Lev 24:16; Mat 26:63-66; Jon 5:18; 10:33\f*  
\v 8 K…ôn nian Pailat t…ôm…ôto n…ôghat…ôn u, in t…ôm…ôg…®n p…®k t…ôhm…®n m…®n.  
\v 9 K…ôn in t…ômat…®g muw…®n m…®n im…ô, m…ôtap…ôh o Iesu m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik et…ôm hi…ô?‚Äù\f + \fr 19:9 \ft Pailat t…ôm…ôtap…ôh n…ôhlan o n…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô naka Iesu in uhg…®n …ôk…ôku kit, o ok…ôm-naka n…®kin tat…ôht m…ôm…ô Iesu in et…ôm e n…ôpt…ôn p…®s…®n kit k…ôn et…ôm p…®s…®n kit in otakil nol…ôn r…ôhan (Luk 23:6-7). Iesu t…®nuhalp…®n r…ôk…®s r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn, m…ôto Pailat t…ôm…ôs…ôn…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn lan (Jon 18:36-38a; Aes 53:7).\f*  
\p M…ôto Iesu t…ôsuhalp…®n…ôn r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn.  
\v 10 K…ôn Pailat t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?T…ôhrol n…ôs…ôn-ipam…ôn k…ôm io? ?Ik n…ôs…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô io iatos n…ôsan…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô ekahl-iar…ôp ik, k…ôn matos m…®n n…ôsan…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô ok…ôht-ip…ôn ik e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau?‚Äù   
\p
\v 11 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsol…ôn nat u, okol ik on…ôsos ag…®n-…ôh…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô onakakil io.\f + \fr 19:11 \ft Rom 13:1\f* Tol n…ôhlan, nol…ôn rat r…ôha suah un it…ôm t…ômos-ip…®n…ô io e nelm…ôm, in t…ôrat mapr…ôk…®s-in r…ôham.‚Äù\f + \fr 19:11 \ft Jon 18:30; W…ôk 3:13\f*   
\p
\v 12 K…ôn t…ôtuoun e nian …ôh, Pailat t…ômolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…®k…®s Iesu. M…ôto net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel koatag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô nak…®k…®s suah u mahl-iar…ôp, k…ôn ik s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ômim r…ôha Sisa. Et…ômim u it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in kig, in t…®k…®m…®r r…ôha Sisa.‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 K…ôn nian Pailat t…ôm…ôto n…ôghat…ôn u, k…ôn t…ômit Iesu muwa m…®n ihlu…ô. K…ôn in t…ômuw…®n e ik…®n kit, n…ôrg…®n un, Lou K…ôpiel Epin-Epin, e n…ôghat…ôn Isrel, in Kapata,\f + \fr 19:13 \ft Kapata in ik…®n kit k…ôm…ôl…®n k…ôpiel it…ôm tepin-epin m…®n ik…®n, kol tahmen …ôm e s…®men it…ôm k…ôm…ôhl…ôk…®n.\f* k…ôn mat…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr jea r…ôha nakil…ôn.  
\v 14 T…®nu…ôk…®r m…®tgar t…ôtul e tina, e nian …ôtuat…®p r…ôha nol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô…ôn o nol…ôn lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn.  
\p K…ôn Pailat t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm Isrel m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei net…ôm m…®n …ôp…ô! !Ot…ôplan-tu! !Suah u in kig r…ôhat…ômat!‚Äù\f + \fr 19:14 \ft Jon 19:19,21-22\f*   
\p
\v 15 M…ôto ilat k…ômotag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh, mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ohamnu! !Ohamnu! !∆èht-ip…ôn e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau!‚Äù  
\p K…ôn Pailat t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?It…ômat nakotolkeike m…ô io ek…ôht-ip…ôn kig r…ôhat…ômat e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau?‚Äù M…ôto pris asol m…®n kot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Sisa …ôm un, in r…ôhat…®mat kig!‚Äù   
\p
\v 16 K…ôn Pailat t…ômeg…ôhan-in-p…ôn Iesu tuw…®n e nelm…®lat, m…ôm…ô mopael m…®n r…ôha Rom okotuw…®n mot…ôht-ip…ôn e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau.  
\s1 Mopael m…®n k…ômot…ôtu-p…ôr Iesu e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau  
\r (Mat 27:32-44; Mak 15:21-32;  //  Luk 23:26-43)  
\p K…ôn ilat k…ômot…®l…ôs Iesu motuw…®n.  
\v 17 In tat…®l…ôs n…®g k…ôm…ôluau r…ôhan,\f + \fr 19:17 \ft Luk 14:27\f* matiet matuw…®n ik…®n kit m…®n, n…ôrg…®n un, Kolkota e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. N…®p…ôt…®n u, ‚ÄúLouip…®l-uip…®l.‚Äù\fig |alt="three crosses with Jesus, robbers, and soldiers" src="LB00328B.TIF" size="span" loc="Jhn 19:17-27" ref="Jon 19:17" \fig*  
\v 18 K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, k…ômot…ôht-ip…ôn Iesu e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau. K…ôn k…ômotat…®g mot…ôht-ip…ôn m…®n et…ômim k…ôiu, kit e n…®kal…®n mat…®p, kit e n…®kal…®n mol, k…ôn Iesu in tat…ôkul ilug…®n elau.   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn Pailat t…ôm…ôn k…ôte r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn kit, k…®l…ôs kan k…ôht-ip…ôn e r…ôhn-kap…ô n…®g k…ôm…ôluau. N…ôghat…ôn u tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, \sc Iesu\sc*, \sc et…ôm Nasaret\sc*, \sc kig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel\sc*.\f + \fr 19:19 \ft Jon 19:14,21\f*  
\v 20 K…ôn net…ôm Isrel tep…ôt, ilat kotafin n…ôghat…ôn u, m…ôto-inu ik…®n …ôh k…ômot…ôht-ip…ôn Iesu ik…®n, in iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o taon.\f + \fr 19:20 \ft Hip 13:12\f* K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, k…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, ne n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Rom, ne n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Kris.  
\v 21 K…ôn pris asol m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, k…ômotuw…®n mot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Pailat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOn…ôk…ôs…ôte…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòKig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel.‚Äô T…ôw…®r m…ô onak…ôte il…ô m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòSuah u in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in kig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \fr 19:21 \ft Jon 19:14\f*   
\p
\v 22 M…ôto Pailat t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNat it…ôm em…ôte, em…ôte.‚Äù   
\s1 Mopael m…®n k…ômotoor nat…®mnat r…ôha Iesu  
\p
\v 23 K…ôn nian mopael m…®n k…ômot…ôht-ip…ôn r…ôk…®s Iesu e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau, k…ôn mot…ôm…®k r…ôhan nat…®mnat, k…ôn k…ômotoor ilat n…ômt…®n kuw…®t, m…ôto-inun mopael m…®n ilat kuw…®t. M…ôto kot …ôf…ôm…ôh r…ôhan, et…ômim it…ôm in t…ômol n…®m…ôhan, in t…ôm…®s…®lp…®n-…®lp…®n…ôn n…®m…ôhan lan, in t…ômol api…ôpi…ô …ôm n…®m…ôhan …ôh.  
\v 24 K…ôn mopael m…®n u k…®not…ôn-…ôn k…ôm ilat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEi, t…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô okotear…ôsin nat u. T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô okotat…®pin …ôm tais ron. K…ôn et…ôm tatol win lan, in t…®tol r…ôhan u kot.‚Äù Nat u t…ômiet m…ôm…ô otol n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn, u t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúIlat k…ômot…ômki-r…ôk…®s r…ôhak nat…®mnat. Ilat k…ômotoor elat m…®n.  
\q1 K…ôn ilat k…ômotat…®pin tais m…ôm…ô ot…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô pah otos nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh.‚Äù\f + \fr 19:24 \ft Sam 22:18\f*  
\m K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, mopael m…®n k…ômotol mihin pahrien.\f + \fr 19:24 \ft Jon 19:28,36,37\f*   
\s1 Iesu ne r…ôhan Mama  
\p
\v 25 K…ôn iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o n…®g k…ôm…ôluau r…ôha Iesu, n…®p…®tan kuw…®t k…ômoat…ôtul …ôh-ik…®n. Mama r…ôha Iesu, ne pia r…ôhan mama, ne Meri kit m…®n, p…ôtan r…ôha Klopas, k…ôn iahunin kit m…®n Meri p…ôtan Maktala.\f + \fr 19:25 \ft Luk 8:2; Jon 20:1,18\f*  
\v 26 K…ôn nian Iesu t…ôm…ôplan r…ôhan mama ne suah un it…ôm in tolkeike p…®k\f + \fr 19:26 \ft Jon tat…ôn at…®p …ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äúsuah un it…ôm in tolkeike p…®k‚Äù (Jon 13:23).\f* katu…ôtul e n…®kal…®n, k…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm r…ôhan mama m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!P…ôtan, n…ôt…®m un!‚Äù   
\p
\v 27 K…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm suah u m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk r…ôham u mama.‚Äù K…ôn t…ôtuoun e nian …ôh, suah u t…ômit p…ôtan un mian iman ik…®n, k…ôn in t…ômatehm w…®r in, tahmen e r…ôhan mama …ôtuat…®p.   
\s1 Iesu t…®n…®m…®s  
\r (Mat 27:45-56; Mak 14:33-41;  //  Luk 23:44-49)  
\p
\v 28 K…ôn uaris…®g lan, Iesu t…ôm…®tun m…ôm…ô w…ôk m…®n it…ôm in t…ômuwa m…ôm…ô otol, t…®nol namnun r…ôk…®s.\f + \fr 19:28 \ft Jon 17:4\f* K…ôn o nol…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn lan, in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEnoaoa.‚Äù\f + \fr 19:28 \ft Sam 69:21; Jon 19:29\f*   
\p
\v 29 K…ôn pes…®n …ôk…ôku kit …ôh-ik…®n tat…ôp…ôl…ôh, k…ômiuw-p…ôn wain lan u tag…®n. K…ôn ilat k…ômot…®l…ôs nat kit tame-ame tahmen e kat…ôn, k…ôn moteer-p…ôn e wain un, k…ôn motatu-p…ôn e nelm…® n…®g kat…ôn m…ô hisop, k…ôn mot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr tuw…®n iu…ôhk…®r o nohl…® Iesu, m…ôm…ô ot…®r…®m.  
\v 30 K…ôn nian in t…ôm…ôn…®m wain u m…ôs…®n, k…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Nat…®mnat rafin t…®nol namnun!‚Äù\f + \fr 19:30 \ft Luk 12:50; Jon 4:34; 17:4\f*  
\p K…ôn t…ôm…ôtag-i…ôhau, meg…ôhan-in-p…ôn r…ôhan nameg…ôn tiet, k…ôn m…®m…®s.   
\s1 Suah kit t…ômaru n…®kal…® Iesu  
\p
\v 31 Nian …ôh r…ôha nol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô…ôn, m…ôto-inu ok…ôn law…®gin un, nian r…ôha Sapat. (K…ôn Sapat u, in Sapat keike kit.)\f + \fr 19:31 \ft Sapat u, in Sapat keike kit, m…ôto-inu t…ômuwa …ôtuat…®p e nian r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn.\f* K…ôn net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel k…ôsotolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô n…®p…ôt…® suah mil…ôhal …ôh ok…ôt…ôhal…ôkul e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau m…ôtoarus-p…ôn nian …ôh. K…ôn o nat …ôh, ilat k…ômotuw…®n mot…ôtap…ôh o Pailat m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim, kotuw…®n, mot…ôtg…ôhl nelk…®l…ôhal, p…ôs il…ôhal k…ôhal…®m…®s u…ôhai …ôm. K…ônu ilat kot…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s n…®p…ôt…®l…ôhal.  
\v 32 K…ôn mopael m…®n k…ômotaup…ôn mot…ôtg…ôhl nelk…® suah mil un k…ôiu it…ôm k…ômot…ôht-ip…ôn ilau e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau il…ôhal Iesu.   
\p
\v 33 M…ôto nian k…ômotuwa o Iesu, mot…ôplan m…ôm…ô in t…®n…®m…®s r…ôk…®s. K…ôn …ômun, ilat k…ôsot…ôtg…ôhl…ôn nelk…®n.  
\v 34 K…ôn mopael kit t…ômaru …ôm n…®kal…®n e r…ôhan n…®ro,\f + \fr 19:34 \ft Sek 12:10; Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:7\f* k…ôn roiu ag…®n-…ôh, n…®ta ne n…ôhau k…ômuai…ôh ahmen-ahmen …ôm, m…ôtuatite e n…®p…ôt…®n.\f + \fr 19:34 \ft 1 Jon 5:6-8\f*  
\v 35 (K…ôn suah kit …ôh-ik…®n tat…ôtul,\f + \fr 19:35 \ft Aposol Jon it…ôm t…ôm…ôte naoa u, in tat…ôghat-in at…®p …ôm in e ves 35 (Jon 19:26; 21:24).\f* in t…ômehm nat…®mnat m…®n u e n…®gan…ômt…®n. K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôha suah u, in t…ôtuat…®p, k…ôn in t…®tun m…ôm…ô in tat…ôn pahrien. K…ôn in tat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô it…ômat m…®n on…ôkot…®tun motahat…ôt…ô lan.)  
\v 36 Nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ômotuwa m…ôm…ô okotol n…ôghat…ôn e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn lan,\f + \fr 19:36 \ft Jon 19: 24,28,37\f* u tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOkol n…®k…®l…®k…®lin kit t…ôs…®t…ôg…®t…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 19:36 \ft Iesu in tahmen e N…ôt…® Sipsip r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn k…ôn n…®tan otosmeg…ôh net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n. (Jon 1:29; 1 Kor 5:7; 1 Pita 1:19). Tahmen m…ôm…ô k…ôm…ôs…ôtg…ôhl…ôn n…®k…®lk…®li nen…ôt…® sipsip m…®n it…ôm katoh e lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn (Eks 12:46; Nam 9:12), e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, n…®k…®lk…®li Iesu kit, t…ôm…ôs…®t…ôg…®t…ôn. Sam 34:20.\f*  
\v 37 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit m…®n e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIlat okot…ôplan suah u it…ôm k…ômotaru.‚Äù\f + \fr 19:37 \ft Sek 12:10; Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:7\f*   
\s1 Josep ne Nikotimas, ilau k…ômiat…ôn…®m Iesu  
\p
\v 38 K…ôn uaris…®g e nat…®mnat m…®n u, et…ôm Aramatia kit, n…ôrg…®n u, Josep. Josep u, in et…ômim kit r…ôha Iesu, m…ôto tat…ôhluaig-in nat u, m…ôto-inun tat…ôgin net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel.\f + \fr 19:38 \ft Jon 7:13\f* In t…ômuw…®n m…ôplan Pailat, k…ôn t…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô oteg…ôhan-in p…ôs t…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s n…®p…ôt…® Iesu. K…ôn …ômun, Pailat t…ômeg…ôhan-in, k…ôn in t…ômuw…®n m…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s.  
\v 39 K…ôn Nikotimas, u aup…ôn in t…ômuw…®n m…ôplan Iesu lap…®n,\f + \fr 19:39 \ft Jon 3:1-2; 7:50\f* in t…ômuw…®n ilau Josep. In tat…®tol k…ôt…®m kit, t…ôm…ôrioah e nat pien-pien m…®n u m…®r ne alos. K…ôt…®m u t…ôf…®g…ôm tahmen e tate kilo.   
\p
\v 40 K…ôn ilau k…ômial…ôs-ir…ôk…®s n…®p…ôt…® Iesu, mualpin e n…®m…ôhan w…®r kit, n…ôrg…®n u linen. K…ôn ilau k…ômioal-p…ôn m…®r ne alos e n…®m…ôhan u, tahmen …ôtuat…®p …ôm m…ô inun net…ôm Isrel kotalpin mihin n…®p…ôt…® et…ômim, moat…®t…ôn…®m.  
\v 41 K…ôn ik…®n …ôh k…ôm…ôht-ip…ôn Iesu ik…®n e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau, k…ômahw…®nu ik…®n, k…ôn e ik…®n …ôh, n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel kit …ôh-ik…®n, it…ôm kat…®t…ôn…®m it…ôm ik…®n. K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, k…ôs…®t…ôn…®m-p…ôn…ôn …ôh suah kit ik…®n.  
\v 42 K…ôn ilau k…ômu…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn n…®p…ôt…® Iesu e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel u, m…ôto-inu nian …ôh in nian r…ôha net…ôm Isrel koatol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô lan o Sapat,\f + \fr 19:42 \ft ∆èplan-tu futnot e 19:31.\f* k…ôn n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel it…ôm kat…®t…ôn…®m it…ôm ik…®n, in iu…ôhk…®r …ôm.   
\c 20  
\s1 Iesu t…®n…ômeg…ôh m…®n  
\r (Mat 28:1-10; Mak 16:1-8;  //  Luk 24:1-12)  
\m
\v 1 E Sante, laulaug…®n ag…®n, t…®tapin…ôp-apin…ôp …ôh, Meri u p…ôtan Maktala,\f + \fr 20:1 \ft Luk 8:2; Jon 19:25\f* t…ômuw…®n e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel, k…ôn m…ôplan m…ôm…ô k…ôpiel asol it…ôm k…ômahtos…®g-in n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel lan, in k…ômahwin r…ôk…®s.  
\v 2 Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn in t…ômaiu m…®t…ôl…®g muw…®n o Saimon Pita ne et…ômim u kit m…®n r…ôha Iesu, u Iesu tolkeike p…®k, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilau m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIlat k…ômot…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s n…®p…ôt…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô …ôp…ôh e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel. K…ôn ekot…ôruru m…ôm…ô k…ômot…ôl…ôh…ôu hi…ô n…®p…ôt…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 3 K…ôn Pita ne et…ômim kit m…®n u r…ôha Iesu, k…ômiaiet m…ôtian m…ôm…ô oku…ôplan n…®p…ôg …ôh.  
\v 4 K…ômuaiu …ôsan…ôn mian, m…ôto suah u kit in t…ômaiu maup…ôn mapr…ôk…®s-in Pita, maup…ôn muw…®n …ôp…ôh n…®p…ôg u ik…®n.  
\v 5 K…ôn in t…ôm…ôm…ôhl-…ôm…ôhl m…ôtag-p…ôn …ôp…ôh im…ô, k…ôn m…ôplan n…®m…ôhan w…®r u linen tat…ôm…ôhl, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôsuw…®n…ôn im…ô.\fig |alt="man peering in tomb after resurrection" src="LB00329B.TIF" size="col" loc="Jhn 20:5-9" ref="Jon 20:5" \fig*  
\v 6 K…ôn Saimon Pita in t…ômiet-ar…ôpa m…®n, k…ôn megup…ôn u…ôhai …ôm im…ô e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel u, k…ôn t…ôm…ôplan n…®m…ôhan u koat…ôm…ôhl,  
\v 7 k…ôn m…ôplan m…®n n…®m…ôhan u k…ômotalpin r…ôhn-kap…ô Iesu lan aup…ôn. N…®m…ôhan u, in t…ôs…ôm…ôhl-p…ôn…ôn ilat n…®m…ôhan m…®n un neen, m…ôto in k…ômaiu-aiu w…®r k…ôl…ôh…ôu p…®s…®n.  
\v 8 Et…ômim u r…ôha Iesu it…ôm t…ômaup…ôn, in m…®n t…ômuw…®n im…ô e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôplan nat…®mnat m…®n u, k…ôn in t…ômatahat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô Iesu t…®n…ômeg…ôh m…®n.  
\v 9 (Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô Iesu ot…ôk…ôike m…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn, m…ôto ilat k…ôsot…®tun w…®r…ôn …ôh n…ôghat…ôn …ôh.)\f + \fr 20:9 \ft Sam 16:10; Aes 53:11; Luk 24:25-27,46; Jon 2:22; W…ôk 2:24-28\f*   
\s1 Meri u p…ôtan Maktala in t…ôm…ôplan Iesu  
\r (Mak 16:9-11)  
\p
\v 10 K…ôn et…ômim mil un r…ôha Iesu k…ômiat…ôl…®g m…ôtian im…ôlau ik…®n,  
\v 11 m…ôto Meri in tat…ôtul iu…ôhk…®r e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel u m…ôtas…ôk. K…ôn nian in t…ôm…ôtas…ôk …ôh, k…ôn m…ôm…ôhl-…ôm…ôhl m…ôtuag-p…ôn …ôp…ôh e n…®p…ôg.  
\v 12 K…ôn …ômun t…ôm…ôplan nagelo k…ôiu …ôp…ôh im…ô. Nat…®mnat r…ôhalau in t…ôru…ôn t…ôru…ôn. Ilau katu…ôp…ôl…ôh u ik…®n-u k…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn Iesu ik…®n. Kiti…ôh tat…ôp…ôl…ôh e n…ôme r…ôhn-kap…ô, k…ôn kiti…ôh e n…ôme nelk…®n.   
\p
\v 13 K…ôn ilau k…ômu…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôtan. ?Ik natas…ôk o naka?‚Äù K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilau m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIlat k…ômot…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s n…®p…ôt…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhak, k…ôn ek…ôruru m…ôm…ô k…ômot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn hi…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 14 Nian in t…®n…ôn r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn u, k…ôn meirair, k…ôn t…ôm…ôplan Iesu tat…ôtul …ôm u ik…®n-un, m…ôto in t…ôruru m…ôm…ô Iesu.  
\v 15 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôtan. ?Nak…ôtas…ôk o naka? ?Ik nateg…ôs-in pah?‚Äù M…ôto p…ôtan u, n…®kin t…ôht m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô naka suah u it…ôm tat…®tas…®lin nahw…®nu…ôn, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol, ok…ôm…ô ik n…ôm…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s n…®p…ôt…®n, k…ôn m…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn …ôh kit, awi, …ôn-ipa-tu k…ôm io, p…ôs io ekuw…®n m…®l…ôs.‚Äù   
\p
\v 16 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúMeri.‚Äù K…ôn Meri t…ômeirair, m…ôtag-p…ôn m…ôplan, k…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Raponi!‚Äù (Inu n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel u, n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúR…ôhak I…ôg…ôtun.‚Äù)   
\p
\v 17 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSask…ôl…®m…ôn io, m…ôto-inu io esuw…®n…ôn …ôh …ôp…ôh il…®s o r…ôhak Tata. M…ôto ik, uw…®n, mehm piak m…®n k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô io enat…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn il…®s o r…ôhak Tata, k…ôn in m…®n r…ôhat…ômat Tata. In Uhg…®n r…ôhak, k…ôn in Uhg…®n m…®n r…ôhat…ômat.‚Äù   
\p
\v 18 K…ôn Meri Maktala t…ômuw…®n m…ôplan net…ômim m…®n r…ôha Iesu, k…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Suah m…®n …ôp…ô! !Io em…ôplan I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô!‚Äù K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm Iesu in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in.   
\s1 Net…ômim m…®n r…ôha Iesu k…ômot…ôplan Iesu  
\r (Mat 28:16-20; Mak 16:14-18;  //  Luk 24:36-49)  
\p
\v 19 E Santei ehnaip…ôn, net…ômim m…®n r…ôha Iesu k…ômotarg…ôf…®m…®n ilat m…®n …ôp…ôh e nim…ô kit, k…ôn motahtos…®g e toa motol lok lan, m…ôto-inu ilat koat…ôgin net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. K…ôn …ômun, Iesu t…ômuwa m…ôtul ilug…®n elat, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôs n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn t…ôtat…®g ot…ômat.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:19 \ft Jon 20:21,26; Jon 14:27; 16:33\f*  
\v 20 K…ôn in t…ômurap…®k nelm…®n k…ôn mol-p…ôn n…®kal…®n k…ôm ilat, k…ôn n…®kilat t…ômagien p…®k m…ôto-inu k…®not…ôplan I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.\f + \fr 20:20 \ft Jon 16:19-22\f*   
\p
\v 21 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn m…®n k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôs n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn t…ôtat…®g ot…ômat.\f + \fr 20:21 \ft Jon 20:19,26\f* Tol m…ô r…ôhak Tata t…ômahl-ipa io,\f + \fr 20:21 \ft Jon 3:17\f* e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm io etahl-ip…ôn it…ômat nakoatuw…®n e n…ôtueint…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:21 \ft Mat 28:19; Jon 17:18\f*  
\v 22 K…ôn nian in t…®n…ôn r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn u, k…ôn in t…ômehag-p…ôn elat, k…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat, otos Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 20:22 \ft Esik 37:9; Jon 7:39; W…ôk 2:38; 8:15-17; 19:2; Kal 3:2\f*  
\v 23 Ok…ôm…ô n…ôkotaluin nol…ôn rat r…ôha et…ômim, k…ôn Uhg…®n m…®n in otaf…ôl r…ôk…®s nol…ôn rat r…ôhan. M…ôto ok…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôsotaluin…ôn nol…ôn rat r…ôha et…ômim, k…ôn Uhg…®n ot…ôsaluin…ôn k…ôn m…ôsaf…ôl r…ôk…®s…ôn.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:23 \ft Mat 16:19; 18:18\f*   
\s1 Iesu ne Tomas  
\p
\v 24 K…ôn et…ôm tuelef u kit r…ôha Iesu, n…ôrg…®n u Tomas, u k…ôtaun-in m…ôm…ô, Mil Mil, in t…ôm…®k…ô e nian Iesu t…ômiet-ar…ôpa olat.  
\v 25 K…ôn in m…®n neen, ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei, emot…ôplan r…ôhatat I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô!‚Äù  
\p M…ôto Tomas t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô ek…ôplan n…ôme nil e nelm…®n mil, k…ônu ekek e noanelm…®k, k…ônu mea-p…ôn e n…ôme n…®ro e n…®kal…®n, k…ônu panahat…ôt…ô lan. M…ôto ok…ôm…ô es…ôplan…ôn, okol esahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:25 \ft Mak 16:11\f*   
\p
\v 26 K…ôn t…®nos wik kiti…ôh r…ôk…®s, net…ômim m…®n r…ôha Iesu koat…ôp…ôl…ôh m…®n …ôp…ôh im…ô, e nim…ô kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn motahtos…®g e toa, motol lok. K…ôn Tomas …ôh-ik…®n ilat min. Nat …ôpnap…®n k…ômol lok e toa, m…ôto Iesu tat…®g muwa m…®n m…ôtul ilug…®n elat m…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôs n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn t…ôtat…®g ot…ômat.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:26 \ft Jon 14:27; 20:19,21\f*  
\v 27 K…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Tomas m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èplan-tu nelm…ôk. Wa mek e noanelm…ôm. K…ôn m…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in nelm…ôm k…ôn mea-p…ôn e n…ôme n…®ro u e n…®kal…®k. S…ôm…®k m…ôtm…ôt…®g…ôn r…ôham nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôun, m…ôto ik on…ôk…ôike m…ôtahat…ôt…ô lak.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:27 \ft Luk 24:40\f*   
\p
\v 28 K…ôn Tomas t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk r…ôhak I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ôn ik r…ôhak Uhg…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:28 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 4:11\f*   
\p
\v 29 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk n…ômahat…ôt…ô lak, m…ôto-inu n…ôm…ôplan io.\f + \fr 20:29 \ft Jon 3:15\f* M…ôto net…ôm m…®n un k…ôsot…ôplan…ôn io, k…ôn ilat kotahat…ôt…ô lak, ilat okotos n…ôw…®r…ôn pahrien, n…®kilat tagien pahrien.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:29 \ft 1 Pita 1:8-9\f*   
\s1 Naoa u, k…ôm…ôte m…ôm…ô net…ômim okotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu  
\p
\v 30 Iesu t…ômol n…ômt…ôtin m…®n tep…ôt e n…®gan…ômt…® r…ôhan net…ômim, it…ôm k…ôs…ôte r…ôk…®s…ôn e naoa u.\f + \fr 20:30 \ft Jon 21:25\f*  
\v 31 M…ôto k…ôm…ôte n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotahat…ôt…ô\f + \fr 20:31 \ft Jon 3:15\f* m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, inu N…ôt…® Uhg…®n. K…ôm…ôte n…ôhlan, m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn e n…ôrg…®n, m…ôto-inu it…ômat noatahat…ôt…ô lan.\f + \fr 20:31 \ft Jon 19:35\f*   
\c 21  
\s1 Iesu t…ômol …ôp in k…ôm r…ôhan net…ômim ilat sep…®n  
\m
\v 1 Uaris…®g e nat…®mnat m…®n u, Iesu t…ômol …ôp m…®n in o r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim,\f + \fr 21:1 \ft Jon 21:14; Jon 20:19,26\f* …ôp…ôh e n…®m…ôkl…ôk…®l e n…®kal…® lek asol, kat…ôn m…ô Lek Kalili.\f + \fr 21:1 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô Lek Taepirias, in n…ôrg…® Lek Kalili kit m…®n.\f* K…ôn t…ômol …ôp in nulan.  
\v 2 E nian …ôh, net…ômim m…®n u r…ôha Iesu k…ômotaliw…ôk kiti…ôh: Saimon Pita, ne Tomas u k…ôtaun-in m…ôm…ô Mil Mil, ne Nataniel u, et…ôm Kalili iman latu…ônu Kena, ne n…ôt…® Sepeti mil,\f + \fr 21:2 \ft N…ôt…® Sepeti mil k…ôiu, ilau u Jemes ne Jon. Jon u inu in t…ôm…ôte naoa u.\f* ne et…ômim mil k…ôiu m…®n r…ôha Iesu.  
\v 3 Saimon Pita t…ôn-ip…ôn olat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo enatuw…®n ekat…®pin net.‚Äù  
\p K…ôn ilat kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ôla, p…ôs kitat rafin kotuw…®n.‚Äù K…ôn ilat rafin k…ômotatite, motuw…®n e pot kit. K…ôn Pita t…ômapeg r…ôhan nat…®mnat o w…ôk. K…ôn ilat k…ômotuw…®n, motat…®pin net, mot…ôtoarus tian. M…ôto k…ôsotos…ôn n…ôm kit ne.\f + \fr 21:3 \ft Luk 5:5\f*   
\p
\v 4 K…ôn t…®natian, k…ôn Iesu tuwa mat…ôtul ipar, m…ôto r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim, ilat kot…ôruru m…ôm…ô Iesu.\f + \fr 21:4 \ft Luk 24:16; Jon 20:14\f*   
\p
\v 5 In t…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!N…ôman! ?N…ôsotos…ôn n…ôm kit, o?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn ilat kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôp…ô, n…ôm t…®k…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 K…ôn in t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ôla, otat…®pin-p…ôn-tu net e mat…®p ik…®n e n…®kal…® pot u, k…ôn on…ôkotiuw n…ôm neen.‚Äù K…ôn …ômun, kotat…®pin-iar…ôp net, …ômun, m…®not…ôruru niuw-p…ôr…ôn, m…ôto-inu net t…®n…ôr m…®n…ôr m…®n…ôrioah e n…ôm.\f + \fr 21:6 \ft Luk 5:4-7\f*   
\p
\v 7 K…ôn suah u it…ôm Iesu tolkeike p…®k, in t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Pita m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! !I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô …ôtuat…®p …ôh!‚Äù K…ôn nian Pita t…ôm…ôto n…ôghat…ôn u, t…ôm…ôt…ôut u…ôhai …ôm, k…ôn m…ôt…®p…ôn it…ôh…ôi, meai muw…®n ipar.  
\v 8 K…ôn net…ômim m…®n u neen r…ôha Iesu, ilat k…ômotuwar e pot, moatiuw net apon t…ôm…ôrioah e n…ôm, m…ôto-inu bot in iu…ôhk…®r …ôm m…ôs…®n o n…®m…ôkl…ôk…®l, tahmen …ôm hanr…®t mita.  
\v 9 K…ôn nian ilat k…ômotuw…®n ipar, mot…ôplan n…®g…ôm …ôk…ôku kit …ôh-ik…®n, n…ômtahl…®n tatu…ôp …ôh, k…ôn n…ôm neen …ôh-ik…®n, katuwan e n…®g…ôm, ne p…®ret …ôh-ik…®n.\fig |alt="Jesus serving breakfast to disciples on seashore" src="LB00330B.TIF" size="span" loc="Jhn 21:9-14" ref="Jon 21:9" \fig*  
\v 10 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOt…ôm…®k n…ôm m…®n un neen it…ôm n…ômotos motuwa.‚Äù   
\p
\v 11 K…ôn Saimon Pita t…ômuw…®n m…®n e pot, k…ôn mewk…ôkan net muw…®n …ôp…ôh ipar. Net u t…ôrioah e n…ôm asol m…®n, ilat rafin wan-hanr…®t-fifti-tri. K…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô net u t…ôm…ôrioah pap e n…ôm, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôs…ôhap…ôn.  
\v 12 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOtuwa motagw…ôn.‚Äù K…ôn ilat kit n…®kin t…ôs…ôht…ôn m…ôm…ô ot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik pah un?‚Äù m…ôto-inu ilat k…®not…®tun …ôsas m…ôm…ô in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.  
\v 13 K…ôn Iesu t…ômos p…®ret muwa mos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn m…®n n…ôm.   
\p
\v 14 K…ôn inu, nian tatol k…®s…®l lan, it…ôm Iesu t…ômol …ôp in o r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim uaris…®g e nian in t…ôm…®m…®s, k…ôn m…ômeg…ôh m…®n.\f + \fr 21:14 \ft Jon 20:1,19,26\f*   
\s1 Iesu ne Pita  
\p
\v 15 Nian ilat k…®notagw…ôn r…ôk…®s, Iesu t…ôm…ôtap…ôh o Saimon Pita, m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSaimon, n…ôt…® Jon. ?Ik nakolkeike io tapr…ôk…®s-in net…ôm m…®n un?‚Äù Pita t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èw…ôh, I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ik n…ôk…®tun m…ôm…ô io ekolkeike p…®k ik.‚Äù\f + \fr 21:15 \ft Mat 26:33-35; Jon 13:37-38\f*  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ôla, ik onakatagw…ôn r…ôhak nen…ôt…® sipsip m…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 16 K…ôn Iesu tat…®g m…ôtap…ôh m…®n ron m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSaimon, n…ôt…® Jon. ?Ik nakolkeike io?‚Äù  
\p In t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Iesu m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èw…ôh I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ik n…ôk…®tun m…ôm…ô iakolkeike ik.‚Äù  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ôla, ik onakatehm w…®r r…ôhak sipsip m…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 21:16 \ft Esik 34:2; Mat 2:6; Jon 10:11; W…ôk 20:28; 1 Pita 5:2-3\f*   
\p
\v 17 K…ôn m…ôtau k…®s…®l lan, Iesu tat…®g m…ôtap…ôh m…®n ron m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSaimon, n…ôt…® Jon. ?Ik nakolkeike io?‚Äù\f + \fr 21:17 \ft Jon 13:38\f*  
\p K…ôn Pita, n…®kin t…ômahm…ô, m…ôto-inu Iesu t…ôm…ôtap…ôh ron mau k…®s…®l, m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik nakolkeike io?‚Äù K…ôn in t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ik n…ôk…®tun nat…®mnat rafin.\f + \fr 21:17 \ft Jon 16:30\f* Ik n…ôk…®tun m…ôm…ô io ekolkeike ik.‚Äù  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ôla, ik atagw…ôn r…ôhak sipsip m…®n.   
\p
\v 18 ‚ÄúN…®pahrien…ôn ag…®n u iat…ôn k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô, aup…ôn, e r…ôham net…ôm-alu…ô…ôn, n…ômatiargin at…®p r…ôham k…ôt…ôut, k…ôn m…ôtaliw…ôk matuw…®n ik…®n m…®n rafin it…ôm nakolkeike m…ôm…ô nakuw…®n ik…®n. M…ôto nian ik onakagu…®hl, onak…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in nelm…ôm, k…ôn et…ôm p…®s…®n kit ot…ôlis …ôtain r…ôham k…ôt…ôut, k…ôn mit ik nakian ik…®n ik n…ôsolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô nakuw…®n ik…®n.‚Äù  
\v 19 E n…ôghat…ôn u, Iesu t…ômaup…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s …ôm, nol…ôn it…ôm Pita ot…®m…®s, k…ôn r…ôhan n…®m…®s…ôn,\f + \fr 21:19 \ft Kat…ôn m…ôm…ô e nup tate m…®n tatuwa, k…ôn k…ôpan…ôtu-p…ôr Pita e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau.\f* in ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 21:19 \ft Jon 13:36; 2 Pita 1:14\f*  
\p K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ôla, uaris…®g-in io.‚Äù\f + \fr 21:19 \ft Mat 4:19; 16:24\f*   
\s1 Iesu ne suah un it…ôm Iesu t…ômolkeike p…®k  
\p
\v 20 K…ôn Pita teirair m…ôplan et…ômim kit r…ôha Iesu u, Iesu tolkeike p…®k, tatuaris…®g-in ilau. Suah …ôh in…ôh, it…ôm t…ômi…ôu-i…ôu muwa iu…ôhk…®r o Iesu e nian k…ômotagw…ôn e lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, k…ôn mat…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, pah un oteg…ôhan-in-p…ôn ik e nelm…® r…ôham t…®k…®m…®r m…®n?‚Äù\f + \fr 21:20 \ft Jon 13:23,25\f*   
\p
\v 21 Nian Pita t…ôm…ôplan in, k…ôn t…ôtap…ôh o Iesu m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, m…ôto tahro e suah …ôh?‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn Iesu t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ok…ôm…ô io ekolkeike m…ôm…ô in otat…ômeg…ôh muw…®n m…ôtoarus nian iak…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n, ik on…ôk…®tun o naka? Ik un, ik on…ôk…ôike muaris…®g-in io.‚Äù\f + \fr 21:22 \ft Jon 21:19; Mat 4:19; 16:24\f*   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan o nat u Iesu t…ôm…ôn, n…ôghat…ôn kit …ôh-ik…®n kat…ôn t…®t…ôlau-…®t…ôlau e piatat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ômim u r…ôha Iesu ot…ôs…®m…®s…ôn,‚Äù m…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ôs…ôn…ôn k…ôm Pita m…ôm…ô suah u ot…ôs…®m…®s…ôn. In t…ôm…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ok…ôm…ô, io ekolkeike m…ôm…ô in otat…ômeg…ôh, m…ôtoarus-p…ôn iak…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n, ik on…ôk…®tun o naka?‚Äù   
\p
\v 24 Et…ômim u r…ôha Iesu in et…ômim kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm tat…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat m…®n u,\f + \fr 21:24 \ft Jon 15:27\f* k…ôn in m…ôte r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u. K…ôn it…®mat ekot…®tun m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u tat…ôn, in n…®pahrien…ôn …ôm.\f + \fr 21:24 \ft Nian neen, Jon tat…ôghat n…ôhlan, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äúit…®mat,‚Äù m…ôto in tat…ôn …ôm in p…®s…®n …ôm (19:35; …ôplan-tu 1 Jon 1:1-4).\f*   
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn  
\p
\v 25 K…ôn nat…®mnat tep…ôt m…®n …ôp…ôh ik…®n it…ôm Iesu t…ômol\f + \fr 21:25 \ft Jon 20:30\f* k…ôn ok…ôm…ô net…ômim k…ôpoat…ôte r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat m…®n u ilat rafin e naoa m…®n, io, n…®kik t…ôht m…ôm…ô rum ot…®k…ô e n…ôtueint…ôn rafin o n…ôl…®n…ôn naoa m…®n u.   